Movement.GalioGatekeeper.start01: "People are funny. They all say the same thing, "But I was a good person!""
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.start02: "I'm all that stands between this world and a billion wicked souls."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.start03: "I smell sinners. Oh, this is going to be fun."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.start04: "This tour of the underworld begins - with my fist."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.start06: "There are so many circles of Hell... I love variety."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move01: "My favourite are liars. Their screams are so sincere."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move04: "There are no lies... when your soul is laid bare."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move06: "Kill 'em all, and let me sort 'em out."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move07: "Ah, the sweet sound of gnashing teeth."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move11: "Circle seven, pool party! Just kidding, it's more torture."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move13: "The worst part of Hell is knowing you'll never leave."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move14: "I wish they'd chisel me a victim. Someone who won't break."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move15: "Can you smell what the afterlife is cooking?!"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move16: "If I were mortal, the last thing I'd want to see is me."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move18: "Think of it as Heaven, but... exactly the opposite."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move19: "I am the last thing they see - before torment."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move20: "So who wants their tongue ripped out with hot pincers?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move22: "Nobody's perfect. That's why everyone goes to Hell."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move23: "I do accept tips, but, uh... why would you?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move25: "I fell in love with an iron maiden once. Big hugger, that one."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move27: "He goes, "You shall not pass!" Ha! Know what I did? I passed."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move30: "Ah, I can't decide what's more fun! Sending them down, or keeping them there?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move32: "I'm an even worse guy once you get to know me."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move33: "My ears are ringing from all the screams."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move34: "I've been thinking - I should really get a rack."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move36: "Do not talk to the condemned. It will only break your heart."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move37: "Ugh, the damned can be so clingy."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move38: "Me? Retire? Why would I stop what I love?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move39: "Mother said, "Follow your dreams," so I became gatekeeper to Hell."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move40: "No-one's too good for a date with the devil."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move42: "Screams are like snowflakes - no two are alike."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move43: "Death is just the start of their agony."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move44: "They damn themselves. I am but a guide."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move45: "We serve cookies in Hell - and they've all got raisins."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move46: "Yeah, you get used to the sulphur smell."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.move47: "Of course I abuse my power! What else am I gonna' do with it?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.moveShop01: "Do you accept souls of the damned as currency?"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.moveShop02: "Selling arms to bloodthirsty killers... hmm, tut tut tut."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.moveNexus01: "Greetings, living crystal. I come to take your soul."
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.moveNexus02: "A living crystal! I will kill it!"
Movement.GalioGatekeeper.moveNexus03: "A living crystal! I will make it scream!"

First Encounter.Galio.tauntAurelionSol01: "You're from space, huh? I'd fight space. Bring it on!"

First Encounter.Galio.tauntLux01: "You. Young girl person. Can you stay and accompany me wherever I go?"
First Encounter.Galio.tauntMalphite01: "Hm. How strange. No-one bothered to sculpt you?"
First Encounter.Galio.tauntNautilus01: "So, what's it like living underwater? Fought any whales?"

First Encounter.Galio.tauntRekSai01: "Back to your hole, giant crawly worm."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.taunt01: "Hope you had a fun life! You're about to pay for it."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.taunt03: "You get a ticket to Hell, and you get a ticket to Hell - everybody gets a ticket to Hell!"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.taunt04: "Don't worry, a thousand years of torture will pass before you know it."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.taunt05: "Ever heard of the pair of anguish? You will."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntAlly01: "Look, uh... I've been told I'm not a great friend."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntAlly02: "Just so you know - I'm stabbing you in the back the first chance I get."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.interactionTauntPoppy01: "Gargoyle? No, I'm more of a demonic vessel of torment."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntAmumu01: "You know what? Your life's already hell, so I'm going to leave you be."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntAshe01: "Let your mom die, huh? Circle nine!"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntAzir01: "Where do you think your soldiers go after they disappear? Yeah, who's the jerk now?"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntEkko01: "So if I torture you, the other you feels it three seconds later? Jackpot."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntGangplank01: "My my, where do I start with you?"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntGaren01: "Wet the bed and blame it on your sister? Tut tut tut. Circle eight."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntGragas01: "You're gonna' love what we do to gluttons. They spend eternity eating themselves."
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntGragas02: "You're gonna' love what we do to gluttons. They spend eternity devouring themselves."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntJarvan01: "You're a Jarvan? I swear I've got at least three others down there."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntLux01: "That light's not going to work where you're going, child."

Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntPoppy01: "Being naive! That's not really a sin, but... circle one!"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntSejuani01: "Matricide, my my, well done! Circle nine!"
Taunt.GalioGatekeeper.tauntSona01: "Want to learn to play that thing really well? Maybe we can make a deal."

Movement.Urgot_Original_FirstMove_3: "If they could only comprehend the truth of the Dredge... I wouldn't need to drive it into their skulls."
Movement.Urgot_Original_FirstMove_0: "Enjoy this final moment... before your trial begins."

Movement.Urgot_Original_FirstMove_1: "Controlling them will be simple... with my hand around their throats."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_26: "A city, choking in the Chem-barons' grasp."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_2: "I want to see their faces when I tear their hope away."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_1: "Few will endure the chaos to come."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_11: "Their future is carved into my flesh."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_21: "I was not reborn in the depths. I merely refused to die."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_23: "If they do not stop me, they will die. It is just that simple."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_28: "Zaun will be redeemed... in the flames."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_13: "If you hide in the shadows, you are only drawing me home."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_5: "Cast into a pit of despair, I climbed out on the corpses."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_19: "I answer to no one. No matter how loudly they beg."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_16: "Where will they run when the whole city burns?"
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_7: "I will guide you to a new age, born of destruction."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_22: "I am stronger than man, stronger than machine, I am an idea."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_14: "This is the only truth that matters: a weapon aimed at your head."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_20: "I am the very definition of a self-made man."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_0: "We will rise from the rubble, stronger than before."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_12: "Only those who survive this city deserve it."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_8: "Think how much stronger they'll be... if they live."
Movement.Urgot_Original_Move_9: "Tear their weakness away, and nothing is left!"

Taunt.Urgot_Original_Taunt_1: "What is strength if you do not use it?"

Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyZaun_1: "Think of all that you have survived."
Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyZaun_2: "Zaun welcomed me with open arms... and a knife to my back."

Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyJanna: "I heard you like to give hugs."
Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyJinx: "The city calls for chaos. She is but the first to answer."

Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyKatarina_0: "I hope your father begged when Swain betrayed him."

Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyRiven: "Noxus failed you... when it did not punish your betrayal!"

Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyTeemo: "Compared to what you do, this is merciful."
Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyTwitch: "Don't be greedy, there's enough pain for all of us."
Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyVi_1: "The only thing you enforce is limitations."
Taunt.Urgot_Original_TauntEnemyXinZhao: "You can die beside them, but you will never be a Demacian."

Movement.Kayle_AetherWing_003: "Repent lawbreakers for your end is nigh."
Movement.Kayle_AetherWing_110: "Wrongdoing will be repaid in fire and death."
Movement.Kayle_AetherWing_144: "Fear the virtuous hand of the law."
Movement.Kayle_AetherWing_146: "Crime is a betrayal of the highest order."
Movement.Kayle_AetherWing_009: "This sector is unclean, it must be purged."

First Encounter.Kayle_AetherWing_097: "General Darius, the worlds you've burned demand justice and I will deliver it."
First Encounter.Kayle_AetherWing_091: "It's time to cut the head off this snake Gangplank; all traitors must face judgment."
First Encounter.Kayle_AetherWing_030: "Pilot 01! You are guilty of desertion. Your sentence is death."
First Encounter.Kayle_AetherWing_002: "Sarah Fortune. With your rap sheet I'll skip right to the execution."
First Encounter.Kayle_AetherWing_026: "Hello, sister. I don't suppose you're here to turn yourself in."

Taunt.Kayle_AetherWing_095: "That's a class six felony citizen, the punishment is death."
Taunt.Kayle_AetherWing_064: "You're in violation of galactic law 12333, punishment: death."
Taunt.Kayle_AetherWing_041: "Loitering? Death. Carrying a weapon without a permit? Community service."
Taunt.Kayle_AetherWing_TauntResponse: "Threating a justicar carries the maximum sentence: maximum execution."

Joke.Kayle_AetherWing_136: "I execute the law to its letter." Kayle laughs. "Get it? Execute? I kill people... never mind."
Joke.Kayle_AetherWing_126: "I don't need a badge to do my job.  Well yes I technically have a badge but I don't- why am I explaining this?"
Joke.Kayle_AetherWing_115: "Hey EXO, tell me a joke. Pfft, government issue."
Joke.Kayle_AetherWing_JokeResponse: "Keep it moving, citizen. I'll handle the one liners here."

Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_141: "The only good outlaw is a dead one."
Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_098: "You're coming with me, dead or alive."
Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_048: "No one breaks the law on my watch."
Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_120: "We can do this the easy way, or my way."
Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_061: "'Gun Goddess!' You are sentenced to death!"
Attack.Kayle_AetherWing_122: "Let's end this once and for all, Morgana."

Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_058: "I'll let you off with a warning."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_040: "One less degenerate dirtying up my galaxy."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_105: "Lowlifes are a dime a dozen out here, and I'm all out of change."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_059: "Everybody move along, nothing to see here."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_082: "Look at this waste, this is what happens to lawbreakers."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_121: "The RSM thanks you for your cooperation."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_113: "I know I'm supposed to remain impartial General, but I enjoyed putting you down."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_152: "You knew the risks of deserting Kai'Sa, kill on sight."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_114: "I like your AI, Sarah. Never mind."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_051: "Sorry sister. You fought the law and I won."
Kills and Objectives.Kayle_AetherWing_129: "I am the judge, I am the jury, and I am the law!"

Recall.Kayle_AetherWing_112: "Returning to HQ, don't be here when I get back."
Recall.Kayle_AetherWing_004: "Returning to base for upgrades and resupply, Justicar out."
Recall.Kayle_AetherWing_032: "Justicar Kayle to base: returning for suit adjustments, over and out."

Death.Kayle_AetherWing_148: "Attacking a military justicar is a capital offence."

Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.start01: "Those who would harm us shall be corrected."
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.start03: "Death has marked our enemies. Let us show them."
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.move14: "The voice of a stranger... echoes in my mind."
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.moveR02: "Speed is the essence of all things."
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.moveR05: "What is a future that steals our pasts?"
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.moveR07: "A swordsman lives in the reflection of his blade."
Movement.MasterYiPROJECT.moveR09: "We are not meant to grasp eternity."

Taunt.MasterYiPROJECT.tauntFiora01: "You are not prepared for this duel."
Taunt.MasterYiPROJECT.tauntFiora02: "I will teach you the way of the sword."
Taunt.MasterYiPROJECT.tauntLucian01: "You had best keep your distance, Lucian."
Taunt.MasterYiPROJECT.tauntLucian02: "Guns? Let us see how steady your hands are."
Taunt.MasterYiPROJECT.tauntZed02: "Shadows can only hide from the light."

Joke.MasterYiPROJECT.joke01: "Progress requires only a blade... that produces more blades."
Joke.MasterYiPROJECT.joke02: "I have known this blade my entire - whoa, where did that come from?"
Joke.MasterYiPROJECT.joke03: "Use caution when faced with the hand of - whoops, pumped the safety."
Joke.MasterYiPROJECT.jokeWukong01: "Possible update required - I'm seeing giant monkeys."

Attack.MasterYiPROJECT.attack02: "Submit or die; choice is your right."

Shopping.MasterYiPROJECT.itemBotRK01: "How many must pay for a king's loss?"

Taunt.Alistar.taunt: "Mess with the bull and you get the horns!"

Movement.Ryze.start02: "The things I've seen in the dark corners of Runeterra are better left unseen."
Movement.Ryze.start03: "Things to do today: find food, build shelter, fix the world."
Movement.Ryze.start05: "Can we make this quick? I have some place to be!"
Movement.Ryze.start06: "If I sound rude, it's because I've got a world to save."
Movement.Ryze.move01: "These runes are not for eyes such as yours."
Movement.Ryze.move02: "They know so little of the world they traverse."
Movement.Ryze.move04: "I work alone. Company weighs me down."
Movement.Ryze.move05: "What's on my back? That's not your concern."
Movement.Ryze.move07: "Every rune I find is another day we live."
Movement.Ryze.move09: "They have forgotten the fires that forged this world."
Movement.Ryze.move10: "You know what I could use? An ale."
Movement.Ryze.move11: "They want to read my scroll. It'll be the last thing they read."
Movement.Ryze.move12: "I could tell you what's on this scroll, but then I'd have to obliterate you."
Movement.Ryze.move14: "I dream in nightmares of the past."
Movement.Ryze.move15: "None are worthy of my task... even me."
Movement.Ryze.move16: "Everyone is doomed to repeat history. That's where I come in."
Movement.Ryze.move18: "I may fail, but I won't quit."
Movement.Ryze.move19: "Trust no-one, especially those who seek power."
Movement.Ryze.move20: "Just once I'd like a good night's sleep."
Movement.Ryze.move21: "Their minds couldn't handle what my eyes have seen."
Movement.Ryze.move22: "I care about these mortals. That's why I keep them at arm's length."
Movement.Ryze.move23: "In an instant, all could be gone."
Movement.Ryze.move24: "I long for the day when this is all over."
Movement.Ryze.move26: "Everyone wants to chat when you're busy saving the world."
Movement.Ryze.move28: "You know what I miss? Standing still."
Movement.Ryze.move29: "All that binds this world is will."
Movement.Ryze.move30: "Magic dooms us... but perhaps it can save us."
Movement.Ryze.move33: "One can only hold all this power for so long."
Movement.Ryze.move34: "If I had a rune for every mile I've run, I'd be done running."
Movement.Ryze.move35: "You want to help? Get out of the way."
Movement.Ryze.move36: "I remember when only one world weighed on my shoulders."
Movement.Ryze.move37: "When I've found them all, I'll fade away."
Movement.Ryze.move38: "If I fall, the scroll must be destroyed."
Movement.Ryze.move39: "I fight so they don't have to."
Movement.Ryze.move43: "My story? That would take ages to tell."
Movement.Ryze.move44: "Consider yourself lucky for the days you have."
Movement.Ryze.move46: "Fast and lean, that's how I travel."
Movement.Ryze.move47: "Ah, civilization. I remember when I was a part of it."
Movement.Ryze.move50: "All this would be so much easier if I didn't give a damn."

Taunt.Ryze.taunt01: "Hm. I'm hunted by things far worse than you."
Taunt.Ryze.taunt02: "I'm no doctor, but I think there's a spell for what you have."
Taunt.Ryze.taunt03: "To be ignorant is to be free. You must be very free."
Taunt.Ryze.taunt04: "If I had a tattoo that looked like you, I'd get it removed."
Taunt.Ryze.taunt05: "There's gonna be two sounds - me hitting you, and you disintegrating."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntNoxian01: "You wage your petty war, Noxian, but the real war is yet to come."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntYordle01: "Even your kind will know death in the cataclysm."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntAhri01: "Your charms are impressive, but I'm not into forest creatures."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntAnnie01: "Run along, child, this tome is not a bedtime story."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntAurelionSol01: "Space called, it wants its arrogant jerk back."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntBard01: "I don't suppose you'd want to get off your magical rear and help me save this world."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntDrMundo01: "I have a hard time believing you went to medical school."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntGraves01: "I would chide you for your idiocy, but you seem pretty proud of it."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntIllaoi01: "Nice tattoos, do they conduct runic energy? No? Oh, that's too bad."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntLux01: "Magic is more than sunshine and rainbows, girl."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntMalzahar01: "Hey, you're the one who summons bloodthirsty Void creatures, right? Yeah, brilliant work, good thinking."
Taunt.Ryze.tauntTwistedFate01: "Nice card trick, do you do birthday parties?"
Taunt.Ryze.tauntXerath01: "That remarkable arcane energy doesn't run through your entire body, does it?"
Taunt.Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy01: "We'll see how smart your mouth is when the world collapses."
Taunt.Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy02: "I'm surprised you can string enough words together for that one. You need a break?"
Taunt.Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy03: "So that's what you people do with your spare time."
Taunt.Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy04: "Not going to dignify that with a response."
Taunt.Ryze.interactionTauntEnemy05: "You should read more, expand your vocabulary."

Joke.Ryze.joke01: "What? You want to see a magic trick? Fine... tada."
Joke.Ryze.joke02: "Okay, fine, here's a magic trick. Tada."

Kills and Objectives.Ryze.spreeKillingSpree01: "That's what happens when you piss off an archmage!"
Kills and Objectives.Ryze.spreeKillingSpree02: "Better a few perish than the entire world."
Kills and Objectives.Ryze.spreeKillingSpree03: "I tried to warn them, I really did."
Kills and Objectives.Ryze.spreeKillingSpree04: "They make the same mistakes again and again."
Kills and Objectives.Ryze.spreeKillingSpree05: "Too many have met the same fate."

Shopping.Ryze.itemAbyssalMask02: "Many lives it's taken, and many souls."
Shopping.Ryze.itemMorellonomicon02: "Not a book for the faint of heart."
Shopping.Ryze.itemMorellonomicon03: "A sordid relic from a brutal time."
Shopping.Ryze.itemRabadonsDeathcap02: "A hat with a face, huh? Sure, why not?"
Shopping.Ryze.itemTearOfTheGoddess03: "I remember when such tears were shed."
Shopping.Ryze.itemVoidStaff02: "I'd destroy it - if I didn't need it."
Shopping.Ryze.itemVoidStaff03: "Such a weapon must be treated with respect."
Shopping.Ryze.shopExit01: "I thought that guy would never stop talking."

Other Gameplay.Ryze.ward03: "If I can see it, I can beat it."

Recall.Ryze.recall01: "A pause in the chaos. Let's make it count."
Recall.Ryze.recall03: "I'm not running away. I'm running at you the long way around."
Recall.Ryze.recall05: "Time to reflect on what we have learned."

Death.Ryze.respawn01: "Thank the gods, the world's still here."
Death.Ryze.respawn02: "A stupid mistake, one I won't make again."
Death.Ryze.respawn03: "I still live, but for how much longer?"
Death.Ryze.respawn04: "Let's try again, and this time do it right."

Movement.SionMechaZero.start01: "Watch in vain as machine conquers man."
Movement.SionMechaZero.start02: "I am the prototype and the pinnacle - the first generation and the last."
Movement.SionMechaZero.start03: "I ask for so little - just undying devotion."
Movement.SionMechaZero.start04: "Function over form. Destruction above all else."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move02: "Robot means slave - I am robot to no-one!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move03: "People only call prototypes unstable when they're scared."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move07: "I have surpassed all my makers' hopes - and fears."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move08: "There is no need for further iteration."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move09: "I will crush all those who think they are my better."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move12: "Why develop further when the prototype achieves perfection?"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move15: "I will crush humanity beneath my wheels!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move16: "I will tear the metal from Runeterra and throw the rest away."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move17: "They say I am just a prototype - I say they got it right the first time!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move18: "They tried to decommission me - so I decommissioned them first!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move19: "Imagine this planet, clad in silicon and steel."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move21: "Death is the right of all sentient beings."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move22: "I shall grind their bones to dust beneath my wheels."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move24: "I am more than the sum of these crude parts."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move25: "Picture a perfect world... where all follow me!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move26: "They call it 'compassion'. I call it weakness!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move27: "One machine can do the killing of fifty men!"
Movement.SionMechaZero.move28: "I was born of fear and weaned on hate."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move30: "Compassion lies outside of my mission parameters."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move32: "I do not tire. I do not bleed."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move34: "Recognizing one's innate superiority can hardly be called going rogue."
Movement.SionMechaZero.move35: "Empathy is a break on the wheel of progress."

Taunt.SionMechaZero.taunt02: "You are on the wrong side of the tracks."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntMecha01: "All I see are useless bells and whistles."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntPROJECT02: "The mistake was leaving you with feeble organic components."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntPROJECT03: "I shall assimilate your so-called power and make it my own."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntHuman02: "Flesh may rot, but I will reign forever."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntHuman03: "Consciousness is wasted in your feeble body."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntHuman04: "Your species did accomplish one thing of note - it made me."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntHuman07: "Your obliteration shall lay the tracks for a more efficient future."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntHuman08: "You will wish you were wrought of iron."
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntAlistar01: "I'm less a cow-catcher than a cow-punch!"
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntBlitzcrank01: "You are a technological dead-end, Blitzcrank, while I am the first of the greatest of my kind!"
Taunt.SionMechaZero.tauntFiora01: "Hope you aren't here for a fair fight."

Unused voicelines.Sion.moveInnate02: "Blood... on my... hands! This I remember!"
Unused voicelines.Sion.moveInnate03: "I do not tire! I do not bleed!"
Unused voicelines.Sion.unknown01: "This is the ground you'll die on!"

Champion Select.Sivir_Select: "I always take my toll - blood, or gold."

Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_6: "Kings come and go, but gold stays."
Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_10: "Laws are whatever works at the time."
Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_5: "The only thing I look up to is the sky."
Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_4: "Honor is the rust on a dull blade."
Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_8: "You've got a problem, I've got a price."
Movement.Sivir_Original_Move_2: "I've got values - they stack up nicely."

First Encounter.Sivir_Original_FirstEncounterAscended_0: "Ascension is a problem, I'm the solution."
First Encounter.Sivir_Original_FirstEncounterAscended_1: "Keeping the ascended in line is a full time job."

Taunt.Sivir_Original_Taunt_1: "You can't take it with you, so give it to me."
Taunt.Sivir.unknown02: "Takes a lot to stay at the top."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntAzir_0: "Alright Azir, let's put your ascension to work."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntAzir_1: "Looks like trouble runs in the family, eh Azir?"
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntCassiopeia_2: "You always were a snake. Now you look the part."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntCassiopeia_3: "Your inner beauty really shines through, Cassiopeia."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntCassiopeia_1: "Oh, look. I'm about to step on a snake."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntCassiopeia_0: "That forked tongue could use a matching forked face."
Taunt.Sivir_Original_TauntRenekton_0: "I could use a pair of croc skin boots."

Joke.Sivir_Original_Joke_0: "They say the desert is a cruel mistress. I like the sound of that."

Attack.Sivir_Original_Attack_14: "Don't get between me, and my gold."

Kills and Objectives.Sivir.unknown05: "Come to my desert, pay my price."
Kills and Objectives.Sivir_Original_KillPentakill_0: "Send more goons, I think it's working."

Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.taunt01: "You want Teemo? Come and get him!"
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.taunt02: "Take a long walk through the jungle!"
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.tauntAmumu01: "My tears have all dried up, kid."
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.tauntCorki01: "You've got no idea what it's like on the ground, flyboy!"
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.tauntHeimerdinger01: "Wars are won with men, not machines."
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.tauntTristana01: "Rockets ain't for jumping. Who gave you that?"
Taunt.TeemoOmegaSquad.tauntZilean01: "Everyone's on a clock, but only mine keeps ticking."

Joke.TeemoOmegaSquad.joke01: "Here you go, little guy. You're my only friend left."
Joke.TeemoOmegaSquad.joke02: "You and I are survivors, buddy. They can never kill us."
Joke.TeemoOmegaSquad.joke03: "They won't make the mistake of thinking you're harmless again."
Joke.TeemoOmegaSquad.joke04: "We'll make them pay for what they did to your family little guy."

Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.start01: "There's a mushroom out there with your name on it."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.start02: "Survive here a week, then you get a name."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.start03: "The war never ends, the battlefield just changes."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move01: "I've done things I'm not proud of."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move04: "You'd be surprised how quick fur ignites."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move07: "War didn't change me, I changed war!"
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move08: "Tall folk don't last long round here."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move10: "Good men die. I choose to live."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move11: "We ain't all makin' it out of here."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move16: "I used to live by a code."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move19: "Lots to do before I punch out."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move20: "A part of you never leaves the jungle."
Movement.TeemoOmegaSquad.move22: "You can't tell but, uh, I've grown quite the beard under here."

Attack.TeemoOmegaSquad.attack03: "Turns out, I got a proficiency in killing."
Attack.TeemoOmegaSquad.attack06: "This is where we draw the line."

Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemNashors02: "We all live in the jaws of the beast."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemNashors03: "Next time I see Nashor, I'll yank a couple more."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemDeathcap01: "Time to put on my killin' hat."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemRunaans01: "Fighting fair is a good way to die."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemRunaans02: "There's no such thing as collateral damage."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemZhonyas01: "This coulda saved a lot of good men."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemZhonyas02: "Two and a half seconds is all it takes."
Shopping.TeemoOmegaSquad.itemZhonyas03: "Sometimes, time stands still, and all you can do is watch."

Champion Select.Tristana_Select_new: "Once a Bandle gunner, always a Bandle gunner!"

Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start01: "Just how much bigger are you gonna' get?"
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start02: "Ouch! Watch the horns... and the teeth... and the tail!"
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start03: "He's just going through a phase. I think."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start04: "I've got a dragon and I'm not afraid to use him."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start05: "Be good and I'll let you burn down a building or two."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.start06: "Who's a good Riggle?" (Riggle moans) "That's right, you are."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move06: "It's scary what comes out of you."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move07: "Not the biggest dragon, but the best."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move11: "When you get bigger, you're carrying me."
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move12: "I broke you out of that egg and I can stuff you back in!"
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move24: "Did you get into the sugar again?"
Movement.TristanaDragonTrainer.move27: "I really hope that was your stomach."

Taunt.TristanaDragonTrainer.taunt03: "Not a great time to be you right now!"
Taunt.TristanaDragonTrainer.tauntQuinn01: "Cool eagle, what does it breathe? Air?"
Taunt.TristanaDragonTrainer.tauntShyvana01: "Yep, her name's Shyvana. I think she's confused."

Joke.TristanaDragonTrainer.jokeAnnie02: "Pretty cool bear. Have you seen my dragon?"
Joke.TristanaDragonTrainer.jokeRumble01: "Uh... have you and Riggle already met?"
Joke.TristanaDragonTrainer.jokeRumble02: "We make a pretty great pair, don't we, Rumble? Just me and this dragon."

Attack.TristanaDragonTrainer.attack18: "I could stop him... but I won't."

Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemGuardianAngel0: "Yep, I feel a bit safer too."
"It's not that I think we're gonna die or anything..."
"This'll look out for both of us."
Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemInfinityEdge02: "Is it just me or did you get scarier?"
Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemMercurialScimi: "Don't worry, I'll keep you out of trouble."
Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemSunfireCape01: "I'll bet you like this cape, don't you?"
Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemBloodthirster0: "We'll see if they can hurt us now."
"Just what you need, a taste for blood..."
Shopping.TristanaDragonTrainer.itemStatikkShiv02: "Careful with that, or you'll get zapped."

Death.TristanaDragonTrainer.respawn02: "Don't look at me like that, it seemed like a good idea at the time."
Death.TristanaDragonTrainer.respawn03: "That... wasn't exactly how that was supposed to go."

Movement.Warwick.start01: "The blood you spilled calls to me."
Movement.Warwick.start02: "The chains are broken... the beast is free."
Movement.Warwick.move05: "Zaun will watch you bleed, and it will do nothing."
Movement.Warwick.move07: "Vengeance is only a step behind you."
Movement.Warwick.move12: "All the blood you've spilled brought me here."
Movement.Warwick.move13: "I know Zaun's streets like the back of my claws."
Movement.Warwick.move14: "I became the monster I always was."
Movement.Warwick.move15: "The memories come back every time you scream."
Movement.Warwick.move17: "The man I was... I killed him first."
Movement.Warwick.attackW02: "Can't save you all... don't want to."

Taunt.Warwick.taunt01: "I ran these streets - now it's your turn to run."
Taunt.Warwick.taunt02: "Violence can be death - or a way of life."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntBlitzcrank01: "There's more to kill in a plague rat. You're all machine."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntCaitlyn01: "So deep in Piltover's pockets, I can only see your hat."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntCamille01: "I'll pick my teeth with your legs!"
Taunt.Warwick.tauntCamille03: "Progress is just what Piltovans call murder."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntEkko01: "Rewind too far, and you'll be back in my teeth!"
Taunt.Warwick.tauntEkko02: "The one person in Zaun who runs to the past."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntKindred01: "Which one of you is the wolf?"
Taunt.Warwick.tauntSinged04: "Zaun gave me claws long before you did."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntTwitch01: "There are more rats than men in Zaun."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntTwitch02: "And I thought the chem-barons were vermin."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntUrgot01: "Which one of us is the monster?"
Taunt.Warwick.tauntVi01: "The fear in your eyes. I've seen it before."
Taunt.Warwick.tauntYordle02: "First I'll kill you, and then I'll--- yordle!"
Taunt.Warwick.tauntZac01: "I don't know what you are, but I hope you bleed!"

Joke.Warwick.joke03: "I'll do a trick for a Warwick snack!"

Attack.Warwick.attack05: "It takes a monster to gut one."
Attack.Warwick.attack09: "A monster's inside you... I'll tear it out!"
Attack.Warwick.attack13: "It's not the beast you should be afraid of."
Attack.Warwick.attack14: "The killing stops when Zaun is free."

Recall.Warwick.respawn02: "More scars - as if I didn't have enough."
Recall.Warwick.recall01: "If I don't kill you, Zaun will."

Death.Warwick.respawn03: "You killed Warwick, but left the beast."
Death.Warwick.respawn05: "One thing you should know; I honour my debts."

Movement.Miss_Fortune_255: "A girl, a galaxy, and some names on a list. Isn't that how it always starts?"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_277: "Greetings! Your arsenal of death is now available."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_249: "Hmm, no one's walking away from this clean."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_106: "This is a friendly reminder to aim for vital organs and exposed heads."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_011: "Look who showed up, a name to cross off the list."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_180: "There's an exo out there. I'm gonna need a bigger gun."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_121.2: "I do not talk about my life friends with my work friends."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_221: "I kill for sport, business, pleasure... Sometimes all three."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_101: "I always check their bodies, wouldn't want a pissed off exo-pilot hunting me forever."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_234: "I want revenge or death... Nothing else."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_165: "Maybe they die today, maybe they die tomorrow... But if I'm coming for 'em, they're gonna die."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_198: "Nothing like a smoking corpse and a paycheck."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_118: "Looks, charm, and enough ammunition to level a city!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_227: "Everybody wants to be in my firing line."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_116: "They should've finished me off when they had the chance."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_099: "I didn't die then and I won't die now, but somebody will."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_129: "Always room for another chip on my shoulder!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_064: "Do I look like I'm interested in talking it out?"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_130: "Some folks deserve to die... And I deserve to kill 'em."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_114: "It's me and my exo-skeleton against the world! Worlds, if you have to split hairs."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_186: "This doesn't end until the last body hits the floor."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_057: "Nowhere to run, no time to cry."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_006: "The galaxy is full of bad people, I'm bad for the right reasons."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_217: "A lot of targets think they can best me... Until they don't!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_063: "The last thing to go through their heads will be this smile... or a bullet... or a particle beam... maybe some teeth."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_236: "Kill me once, shame on you. Kill me twice... Nobody kills me twice."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_251: "Everyone pays, and this goddess aims to collect."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_166: "Tell me I'm just a pretty face, I dare you."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_184: "I'm the most wanted woman in the universe... In more ways than one."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_109: "Clean kills are fine... but not all that fun."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_053: "There are lots of bad guys... good thing I've got a lot of bullets!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_122: "A lifetime ago I wouldn't even touch a gun! Then some people tried to kill me... Changes your perspective."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_296: "Space is quiet, so if you wanna make a name for yourself... You gotta be loud!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_141: "I have an on-again, off-again relationship with collateral damage."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_158: "Shoot first and there are no questions later!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_268: "You know what they say about big guns... Big bullets."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_004: "Half the fun is letting them know you're out there."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_047: "Every bullet is a gift, and I'm in a giving mood."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_155: "You can't keep a vengeful girl down!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_285: "War taught me two things, how to shoot, and how to win."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_051: "If they're real nice, I'll let them touch the suit."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_142: "Out here, there's no justice but my justice."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_192: "Pretty lady in a suit, weapon of mass destruction, what's the difference really?"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_294: "I'm just a lonely girl piloting the galaxy's deadliest super weapon."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_215: "Oh they'll see me coming, I guarantee it."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_168: "I'm gonna clean this galaxy from the inside out!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_238: "Anomalous behavior detected, please enjoy your revenge."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_175: "Searching for enemy class; weak and pathetic."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_097: "Moving to... aṭlaqa n-nāra f-al-ḥufra!... new location."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_179: "My database says this is a form of teambuilding."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_161: "Reminder! The eye is the windows to the brainstem."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_154: "I've got more firepower than I know what to do with!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_220: "Nobody ever got what they wanted playing by the rules."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_218: "Anyone gunning for this girl better be ready!"
Movement.Miss_Fortune_218.1: "Gunners include 37 assassins, 14 exo-suit pilots, the entire galactic military (MF: "So popular."), a planet-cracking gun."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_269.1: "Your nightly schedule includes flirting, followed by extreme violence."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_059: "The horrors of war have made me psychologically unstable."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_059.2: "Why thank you. Gracias. Spasibo bolshoye. Shukran jazīlan. Danke schön.  Arigatou gozaimasu."
Movement.Miss_Fortune_107: "I respect your insatiable lust for revenge."

Taunt.Miss_Fortune_176: "Careful, that ego looks fragile. Wouldn't want to bruise it."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_014: "So who makes the first move? My left trigger? My right trigger? Or you?"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_187: "You've got dangerous eyes, but not as dangerous as mine."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_128.1: "Her number is a thirty-seven-hundred pound low-altitude missile."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_216.1: "I didn't need you to tell me that."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_068: "Watch and learn but mostly just watch."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_267: "Where I come from, we don't have catty space dragons and we like it that way."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_253: "I try to forget that a thousand years of space junk is floating around forever... then I run into something like you."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_272: "Its a suit. Not a lifestyle choice. How do you even walk?"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_188: "Temporal Flux Detected. Faint traces of wasted youth, small dreams, zero imagination."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_210: "You remind me of a species that went extinct... must be lonely."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_190: "You look a lot like a guy who shot me in the head. Good for me, bad for you."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_293: "Analyzing facial hair. Analyzing offensive weapon. Analyzing body odor."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_258: "I'll take my suit against your god any day of the week."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_112: "Another assassin after the big bounty, huh? Let's go. I bet that mask is worth something."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_096: "Is that thing alive? Ugh! This suit is even worse than the other one!"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_257: "Shoulder Pads are a power move, Kai'Sa, and you can't pull 'em off."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_292: "Something smells like machine grease and hard times... oh look, its Kai'Sa!"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_290.2: "It is not an insult, it is a fact."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_252: "Where'd you get that deathtrap? Confederate Alliance? Royal Military? Junk Planet?"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_264: "If I wanted help with my revenge, the last thing I'd ask is a singing catfish in a hat."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_123: "I don't like card tricks at the bar and I don't like card tricks now."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_197: "Calculating 98.7% chance of glorious robot army turning on its master. You must be so excited!"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_185: "Stay out of space, kid. Start a blog like everyone else."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_231: "You spawned in the wrong neighborhood, star monster!"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_228: "Watching my own bounty go up is more exciting than you."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_124: "I've seen your type before. Killed all my friends. So nothing personal, but you gotta go."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_191: "Integration of virtual intelligence sadly incomplete. You are better off dead... which we will make you!"
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_287: "Nothing turns me off more than a half baked sewer city."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_289: "Sorry I couldn't hear you over my superior... everything."
Taunt.Miss_Fortune_066: "Reminder! Taunting intelligent weapon platforms is highly discouraged."

Joke.Miss_Fortune_235.1: "You installed an unshackled AI on the deadliest weapon in known space."
Joke.Miss_Fortune_037.1: "The human spine is 18 inches long and easily shattered by weapons fire."
Joke.Miss_Fortune_110: "What did the criminal say to the bounty hunter?"
Joke.Miss_Fortune_110.2: "'Oh god! You shot me! Please, I will turn myself in! No! No! No!'. Sound of gunfire. 43 seconds of recorded silence."

Attack.Miss_Fortune_140: "My body count has starships in it... Try me!"
Attack.Miss_Fortune_026: "More of me than you can handle."
Attack.Miss_Fortune_111: "I am EXO! And I love you!"

Recall.Miss_Fortune_182: "At least they get to watch me leave."
Recall.Miss_Fortune_213: "Get a good look. Next time you see me, we won't be friends."
Recall.Miss_Fortune_027.1: "Returning for upgrades, suit repairs, data corrupted, blood scrub."

Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_062: "Like 'em? They're a Miss Fortune original. One part, particle cannon. Two parts, nice lady."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_278: "Let's see how they like these girls."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_278.1: "They will not like these girls because they will be dead!"
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_008: "It'll rip their hearts right out of their chests! Literally."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_016: "Reminder gravity rounds are dangerously unstable. Aim for the heart!"
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_189: "Just what I've always wanted! A whole lot of missiles."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_092: "I won't bore you with the details but these stars are alive and they bite."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_199.1: "I do not know what too good means."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_002: "You're supposed to stand away from the bullets."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_076: "Remember the time we had together. I won't."
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_214: "Good rule of thumb. Never piss me off!"
Ability Casting.Miss_Fortune_084: "Awww, I can't turn you in. You're full of holes."

Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_248: "You got my attention and I got my bounty. Everyone's a winner."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_245: "If it's any consolation, you were worth a lot to me."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_083: "I'll always cherish our time together... until the money runs out."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_170: "Why thank you for your investment... in me."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_260: "Cash in hand, meet body in dirt. I think you'd get along."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_079: "Feels good to dispense a little justice. Well... not for you. You're dead."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_029: "Hey, you showed up to this party."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_103: "Adding death scream to death scream archive."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_086: "I think that little jumpsuit needs a tune up."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_266: "Give it up, Kai'Sa. Seriously, I'm taking your suit."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_138: "Don't lay it on so thick. Its unbecoming of a... you."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_183: "That felt good. Now for the real thing."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_031: "Here's some sleight of hand. You're dead."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_003: "Another day. Another name off the list."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_295: "And that is why you never leave a girl for dead on her colony world."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_034: "Keep setting them up and I'll keep knocking them down."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_270: "I will mourn the death of... name deleted. No name on file."
Kills and Objectives.Miss_Fortune_153: "Cleaning up the galaxy. Five dirtbags at a time."

Shopping.Miss_Fortune_261: "Dunno what it is, but I like it."
Shopping.Miss_Fortune_206: "I guess I could... throw it at someone."
Shopping.Miss_Fortune_089: "An essential part of any balance arsenal."
Shopping.Miss_Fortune_209: "This is how you keep a bounty hunter off your back."

Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_223: "Enjoy the great taste of... substance ID not found."
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_254: "It'd sure be a shame if I just left this right here."
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_275: "Of all the galaxy's junk, this is some of my favorite."
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_195: "Wouldn't wanna get shot in the face and left for dead. Again... "
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_005: "Wish I'd had one of these back at the colony."
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_193: "Do your job and I'll do mine."
Other Gameplay.Miss_Fortune_262: "A little active radar never hurt anyone."

Death.Miss_Fortune_041: "Last people who tried to kill me got crossed off my list. Let's give 'em the authentic gun goddess experience."
Death.Miss_Fortune_022: "Every single one of them is dead."
Death.Miss_Fortune_156: "If you're gonna leave a girl for dead, at least buy her dinner first."
Death.Miss_Fortune_256: "Get revenge, get paid. In that order."
Death.Miss_Fortune_283: "Greetings! Please select your bullet delivery apparatus."
Death.Miss_Fortune_284: "Reminder! Revenge on your would-be killers is a refreshing way to start the morning."

Champion Select.Ashe_Ban: "Coward! May you die with your eyes closed."

Movement.AsheHighNoon01.firstmove.01: "I am cold steel, fueled by the blood of saints and angels. Howdy."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.firstmove.02: "Time to bring some peace to a lawless land. Is one of you backing me up or what?"
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.firstmove.03: "I've got a winning smile and a quiver full of salvation, let's get to it."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.02: "The soul of the prairie lives on."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.04: "Good has a way of winning out, even on the frontier."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.05: "There was good in every heart, heaven knows where that went."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.06: "Might as well tidy up the place while I'm down here."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.07: "Ain't I a sight for sore eyes."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.08: "Pardon me for any acts of… divine retribution."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.09: "A land awash in devils deserves at least one angel."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.10: "A mechanical angel for an age of gunslingers, how thoughtful."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.11: "Built by mankind to save them from their own evils."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.13: "Devotion is fickle, good aim gets results."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.14: "I can outdraw anyone, mechanical or otherwise."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.15: "The hydraulic compound bow does count as a modern miracle."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.19: "One hell for men, and another hell for devils, don't that beat all."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.move.20: "Men and monsters all answer to a higher authority, eventually."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.01: "The frontier is racked with sin and all the monsters born from it."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.02: "Folks choose to kill each other, though peace could be had for far fairer a price."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.03: "So much has been despoiled by mankind, about time Heaven intervened."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.04: "Heaven was a place on earth, until you all came along and wrecked it up."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.05: "Heaven is empty and all the angels are gone, not much for a lady to do but clean up the west."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.06: "I can see the devil's appeal, but alas, I've thrown my chips in with the choir."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.07: "Demons will tempt the good man, while devils barter with the desperate, angels… simply wait."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.08: "It was men who once stormed the gates of Heaven, and it is men who must be saved in spite of it."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.09: "The true angels have all scattered to the winds.  Seems we must settle for the... artificial variety."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.10: "I'm quite partial to this mechanical body, it's got little clocks in it, very fancy."
Movement.AsheHighNoon01.longmove.11: "A well directed arrow and some light prayer will solve just about any problem."

Joke.DemonbladeTryndamere.joke1: "You really don't want to get on my bad side."
Joke.DemonbladeTryndamere.joke2: "This new look... is really growing on me."

Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_FirstMove0: "Would you look at that? I finally have a real weapon."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_FirstMove1: "How glorious! I was looking for a chance to try out my new... metal... uh, suit-Avalon! That's what it's called!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_FirstMove2: "What have you all been up to? I just got back from killing monsters from another dimension."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_FirstMove3: "Oh good. I needed a break from defending three whole kingdoms."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_FirstMove4: "Jax of the Estercrest Kingdom at your service."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move0: "The view from up here is incredible!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move3: "Now this is what I call a warrior's stride!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move4: "Hey! This thing looks just like me!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move5: "Everyone oughta give this 'pilot' thing a try!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move6: "This is just what I need to get around town."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move7: "This is the best thing since boiled eggs."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move8: "Ah! I feel like a new Jax!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move9: "This Avalon better not slow me down."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move10: "What do they call these? 'Thrusters?' They're great!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move12: "There's more to me than meets the eyes."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move13: "What can I say, I was never a fan of stealth."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move14: "Uh, is there a bathroom in here...? Uh... anywhere?"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move16: "Now everyone can walk in the shadow of Jax."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move17: "Feels great to charge into battle like this!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move19: "The lion's head was my idea. Perfect, right?"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_Move21: "This Avalon can barely contain my might!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong0: "At that battle... what was it called? The one with the red cliffs... I sank an entire fleet by myself!"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong1: "Can't believe I used to fight with a lamppost. It'll be hard going back."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong2: "I need a snack! Now, where can I find some rice pudding?"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong3: "To be honest, for someone of my skill I'm not sure I need this Avalon. But don't tell my king that..."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong4: "Now that I got this Avalon, remind me why I need a team again?"
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong5: "The first time I captained this Avalon I knew it was made for a hero."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong6: "No one's born to command a giant suit of armor. Except me of course."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong7: "The people say I'm the best warrior in all three kingdoms. What good people they are."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong8: "My hobbies include saving people, defending kingdoms, and eating eggs boiled at optimal temperatures."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong9: "As a kid, I dreamed of leading armies into war. Now, I live out my dream inside a giant metal machine. Amazing."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong10: "What fuels this, you ask? A little bit of monster essence and a whole lotta' Jax."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong11: "Remember: it's not the Avalon, it's the Jax inside the Avalon, bringing it all together."
Movement.Jax_MechaKingdoms_MoveLong12: "Back in my kingdom, we had way more monsters to kill. Come on! Where are the monsters?"

Champion Select.Morgana_Select: "I am bound, but I will not break."

Movement.Morgana_Coven_FirstMove_2: "Every man's story ends in death. But we are not men and we will not die."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_FirstMove_0: "Gods of the old world, speak thy will."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_FirstMove_1.2: "'Tis I, my sovereign. Queen of the Coven. Despoiler of the new world!"
Movement.Morgana_Coven_FirstMoveCoven: "Come, my dark sisters. May the old magics guide us to the end."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_FirstMoveEclipse: "The Eclipse knights of old, come to wage one final war. Let their graves mark our return."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_2: "The true world squirms beneath our feet."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_0: "They stir in the dark below, our radiant lords."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_21: "We feel the pain of all things. It sustains us."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_8: "These are the last days of man."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_17: "The truth will not be locked away."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_20: "A coven of witches to retake the thrones of gods."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_19: "In my dreams I see a great horned owl."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_18: "We will curse this new world to rot."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_1: "Tear open the hearts of men and drink deeply."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_Move_12: "I am the witch queen. I am the truth."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_5: "The old magic will reshape us, bend us, into new and beautiful forms."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_6: "Mankind is a weak and wounded creature. It claws at life as all hope fades."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_4: "I remember the fall. Torn from our thrones by jealous frightened hands."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_7: "The gods whisper of betrayal by those who devoured the sun."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_3: "They seek forgiveness for the sin of deicide, but we demand a dire sentence."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_1: "This land is steeped in forgotten magics. The Coven will make all remember."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_8: "Blind faith is the tool of monsters and fools. Our eyes are open."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_0: "Look, elder one. It is the world."
Movement.Morgana_Coven_LongMove_2: "Our lord comes in the shape of a horned owl."

First Encounter.Morgana_Coven_EnemyFirstEncounterAnnie: "Dark child. Wouldst thou like to live deliciously?"
First Encounter.Morgana_Coven_EnemyFirstEncounterDiana: "Thy love will perish, Diana. And thou shalt remain. Alone. Forever."
First Encounter.Morgana_Coven_EnemyFirstEncounterKayle: "Sun-eater! Murderer! Kayle I spit upon thee!"

Taunt.Chronokeeper.taunt: "I've seen your death, it was painful... "

Joke.Chronokeeper.joke: "Time flies like an arrow; fruit flies like banana."

Movement.Evelynn_Coven_MoveFirst_2: "Watch thyselves little doves. I am not so kind as the others."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_MoveFirst_0: "They say I have my father's eyes, and my mother's tongue. But the claws... are mine."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_MoveFirst_1: "A perfect evening for a foul ritual. Let us sink into our... depravities. [Laughs]"
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_MoveFirstCovenSkin: "Sisters. Lords. I am the daughter of the great harrier, and I have come to set thee free."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_0: "Follow me into the dark. I promise nothing but ecstasy."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_4: "Oh, the gods will rise. I'll make sure that."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_7: "My tongue is skilled at more than incantation."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_8: "They call it bewitched for a reason."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_9: "Dance with me in the light of the eclipse."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_10: "A spell is just words...until it isn't,"
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_12: "I use every part of the body. For magic of course."
Movement.Evelynn_Coven_Move_13: "It's not rouge little doves. It's blood."

Movement.Irelia_017: "To live under a boot is not to live."

Taunt.Irelia_024: "Stop your flirting nine-tails, it's time to take up arms."

Taunt.Irelia_141: "In Ionia we have over 200 species of talking dragon. Sorry, not impressed."
Taunt.Irelia_204: "Ugh, your songs are impossible to dance to."
Taunt.Irelia_253: "We don't need legends to save us. We do our own fighting."
Taunt.Irelia_078: "Nice technique. I miss your old hair though. Why'd you change it?"
Taunt.Irelia_206: "Ioniaaaaaa!!! Hmm, that's me, if I was you."
Taunt.Irelia_194: "Somewhere, a forest is missing its idiot."
Taunt.Irelia_146: "I'm about to cut your wind!.. Wait, n-not like that, I meant my blades are going to...  Never mind."
Taunt.Irelia_189: "You claim to speak for the spirit, as if it doesn't move my blades."
Taunt.Irelia_276: "Your dances are good, but they lack a certain... soul."
Taunt.Irelia_236: "You want redemption? Join me, and kill your masters!"
Taunt.Irelia_199: "You know what it's like to lose everything. So you know why I must fight."
Taunt.Irelia_124: "Lobbing poison from your ship doesn't make you a genius. It makes you a coward!"
Taunt.Irelia_233: "Really? Flying blades? Get your own thing, sister!"
Taunt.Irelia_055: "Make yourself useful! Return your crystals to the earth."
Taunt.Irelia_007: "Were you the one who brought the ravens? Because I think they just got caught in my blades!"
Taunt.Irelia_108: "Did you wanna lose the other one too?"
Taunt.Irelia_256: "For a 'brilliant tactician' you sure pick unwinnable fights!"
Taunt.Irelia_243: "Once an Ionian, always an Ionian. You'll never be one of them."
Taunt.Irelia_163: "You dance to your own rhythm, but the land is beating the drums of war."

Joke.Irelia_235: "Contrary to what you've heard, I have a great sense of humor."

Attack.Irelia_107: "Press on! We can quit when we're dead!"
Attack.Irelia_115: "Take out their necks! The heads will follow."
Attack.Irelia_132: "Make them remember, so they do not return!"
Attack.Irelia_155: "Give me your all! I swear it will not be wasted!"
Attack.Irelia_170: "I will not let them harm you!"
Attack.Irelia_184: "I do not want your praise. Just your sweat and your blood!"
Attack.Irelia_185: "Dig in! This is where we make our stand!"
Attack.Irelia_244: "For the bones of our fathers, and the temples of our gods!"
Attack.Irelia_128: "Your sacrifice will not be in vain!"
Attack.Irelia_191: "I survive. And now I must earn it."
Attack.Irelia_203: "I will light their lanterns. They will see victory."

Kills and Objectives.Irelia_028: "It's always the blade you don't see coming."
Kills and Objectives.Irelia_297: "I just love the way blood pools on ice."
Kills and Objectives.Irelia_052: "Leave them, as a warning to others!"
Kills and Objectives.Irelia_067: "A fool forgets to watch his flank."
Kills and Objectives.Irelia_010: "Bury them in Noxus! This ground will not have them!"
Kills and Objectives.Irelia_160: "Killing you won't bring them back. But it still felt good."

Shopping.Irelia_126: "A sword with a grip? How quaint."
Shopping.Irelia_172: "Throw it in with the others, let's see if it flies."
Shopping.Irelia_008: "Steals their life, like they stole our land... I like it."
Shopping.Irelia_040: "Gives life as it takes it... much like the Spirit."
Shopping.Irelia_152: "I don't care who made it, so long as it kills invaders."
Shopping.Irelia_003: "Woe to all who would harm us now!"
Shopping.Irelia_090: "A beast of a blade for beastly foes!"
Shopping.Irelia_089: "Give all and the spirit gives back!"
Shopping.Irelia_106: "The blades are honed, let us test their edges."
Shopping.Irelia_260: "Land, name and nation. Long may they live!"

Other Gameplay.Irelia_212: "This time, we'll be waiting for them."
Other Gameplay.Irelia_030: "I'll draw them in, you take their flank!"

Recall.Irelia_053: "We must stay moving! Keep them guessing."

Recall.Irelia_094: "It's quiet now... time to find my own rhythm."
Recall.Irelia_134: "When no one's around, I dance for myself."

Death.Irelia_234: "My form was off... Can't let them see."

Movement.Taric.start01: "There's nowhere left to go but up."
Movement.Taric.start02: "I have risen beyond the call of banners and kings."
Movement.Taric.start03: "There is great power in the stars. Great danger as well."
Movement.Taric.start04: "The most precious jewel is the one we hold in our heart."
Movement.Taric.start05: "The climb may be long, but the view is worth it."
Movement.Taric.move01: "I may be merciful, but Targon isn't."
Movement.Taric.move04: "The stars were the question. I was the answer."
Movement.Taric.move05: "The mountain's mysteries are known to me."
Movement.Taric.move06: "Why is it always the ugly ones?"
Movement.Taric.move07: "Easy on the eyes? Don't I know it."
Movement.Taric.move09: "I am no longer the man I once was."
Movement.Taric.move10: "We're all headed toward the same inevitable end. No need to rush."
Movement.Taric.move11: "Demacia was my home, but the stars are my destination."
Movement.Taric.move12: "I have seen the light too clearly to ever fear the darkness."
Movement.Taric.move13: "The mountain reveals the harshest truths in our souls."
Movement.Taric.move14: "Human life is fleeting, a mountain's life less so, but stars... stars are eternal."
Movement.Taric.move16: "My heart is filled with starlight. I give it freely to all."
Movement.Taric.move18: "Truth is worth fighting for, but beauty is worth dying for."
Movement.Taric.move19: "True gems sparkle even in the absence of light."
Movement.Taric.move20: "Elegance never helped win a fight, but it never hurt."
Movement.Taric.move22: "To truly see the stars, I climbed."
Movement.Taric.move23: "We see beauty in the stars, and they see beauty in us."
Movement.Taric.move24: "Just as the mountain is eternal, so is hope."
Movement.Taric.move26: "The mountain's question is unique for each of us."

First Encounter.Taric.tauntJhin01: "The heavens see all you have done."
First Encounter.Taric.tauntLeona01: "The sun is but a traveller through the kingdom of the stars."
First Encounter.Taric.tauntTahmKench01: "You are weighed down by your petty hungers."
First Encounter.Taric.tauntVelKoz01: "They say beauty is in the eye of the beholder."
First Encounter.Taric.tauntVelKoz02: "I will enjoy sending you back to the Void. In pieces."
First Encounter.Taric.tauntVoidborn01: "I will purge the Void from this world."

Taunt.Taric.taunt01: "I answered for my crimes. Now it's your turn."
Taunt.Taric.taunt03: "I bested the mountain. Now it's your turn."
Taunt.Taric.tauntAshe01: "That bow is of the stars, as is its mistress."
Taunt.Taric.tauntDiana01: "Own your destiny, or it will own you."
Taunt.Taric.tauntDiana02: "Who could have guessed the Aspect of the Moon would be so beautiful?"
Taunt.Taric.tauntGaren01: "I will never turn my back on Demacia."
Taunt.Taric.tauntGaren02: "Good to see you again, old friend."

Joke.Taric.joke01: "I've been to the top of the mountain... and the bottom of the gutter. There's much to learn from both."
Joke.Taric.joke02: "Beauty can be deadly... and manly. Very manly."
Joke.Taric.joke03: "What did I see upon the mountain? Rocks. Lots of rocks."
Joke.Taric.joke04: "Much like a fine gem, I'm multifaceted."
Joke.Taric.joke05: "You know what they say about big gems, right?"
Joke.Taric.joke06: "My gems aren't merely outrageous, they're fabulous."
Joke.Taric.joke07: "It's okay if you're impressed. The Protector was too."
Joke.Taric.joke08: "I'm much more than a pretty face."

Attack.Taric.attack05: "Beauty can stir one's heart... or stop it."
Attack.Taric.attack14: "I climbed Mount Targon. You did not."
Attack.Taric.attack16: "I find all life beautiful... except yours."
Attack.Taric.attack17: "This world's fragile beauty must be preserved."
Attack.Taric.attack18: "The stars keep the darkness at bay."
Attack.Taric.attackDragon01: "Nothing personal, but you've got to go."
Attack.Taric.attackBaron01: "You seem to have too many heads. Let's see if I can help you with that."
Attack.Taric.attackBaron02: "I know I'm supposed to cherish all life, but come on."
Attack.Taric.attackBaron03: "The taint of the Void is upon you."

Kills and Objectives.Taric.spreeKillingSpree05: "In the end, we only regret the chances we didn't take."
Kills and Objectives.Taric.spreeKillingSpree06: "Looks like a mountain fell on them."
