Movement.Swain_069: "The more they try to kill me the more they reveal I am on the right path."
Movement.Swain_070: "To redraw the map, the blood of soldiers must be the ink."
Movement.Swain_071: "There is always a choice. The truth is no exception."
Movement.Swain_073: "A new vantage, is all the advantage I need."
Movement.Swain_074: "I suppose I should be grateful they have the decency to fear me."
Movement.Swain_075: "A Noxian knows who he is, and what he must do."
Movement.Swain_076: "The old wounds ache. They are reminders."
Movement.Swain_077: "Decisions have consequences. This I know well."
Movement.Swain_078: "They expect me to play fairly. We aren't even playing the same game."
Movement.Swain_079: "Hmm... I do so enjoy explaining things to idiots."
Movement.Swain_080: "I could kill them all. But it would be far crueler to show them that I am right."
Movement.Swain_081: "Never make a bargain with a demon that you intend to keep."
Movement.Swain_082: "One can read the future in battle lines, assuming one can read."
Movement.Swain_083: "They are five steps from realizing: I am ten steps ahead."
Movement.Swain_084: "I was born a patrician. I became a soldier."
Movement.Swain_085: "Would they even struggle to survive, if they knew what was to come?"
Movement.Swain_086: "I peer through the darkness others fear."
Movement.Swain_087: "When their lives flash before their eyes, so do their secrets."
Movement.Swain_088: "A riddle wrapped in a mystery, hidden within us all."
Movement.Swain_089: "It is not the visions that haunt me, but what I do not see."
Movement.Swain_090: "A calculated risk is no risk at all."
Movement.Swain_091: "Is it not enough for Noxus to be strong?"
Movement.Swain_092: "I cannot lead if I allow fools to stumble about before me."
Movement.Swain_093: "They are blind to the cold logic of this world."
Movement.Swain_095: "What is one more demon, when I already have so many?"
Movement.Swain_096: "The mud on our boots will hide the bloodstains."
Movement.Swain_098: "I've heard what they call me. What a waste of their final words."
Movement.Swain_099: "A voice whispers in the shadows. Though few can hear it."
Movement.Swain_072: "The shadows of our empire, are cast by a raven's wings."

Taunt.Swain_192: "Every day I rule, Noxus becomes a more perfect expression of my will."
Taunt.Swain_193: "The demon is always in the details."
Taunt.Swain_194: "I would not ask of anyone what I would not do myself."
Taunt.Swain_195: "There can be no unity without purpose, and there is one all men are born to."
Taunt.Swain_204: "All roads lead to Noxus, but all visions, to Demacia."
Taunt.Swain_137: "There is nothing noteworthy about Demacia, but that in itself is worth noting."
Taunt.Swain_214: "The world may fall to darkness. But Noxus, will remain."
Taunt.Swain_154: "The truth beneath the gilding. Only war can bring profit."
Taunt.Swain_167: "Suffering pools in the depths where children play."
Taunt.Swain_136: "Creatures of darkness that grant power to their hosts? How original."
Taunt.Swain_201: "Thorns in my side, but your flower is truly something to behold."
Taunt.Swain_205: "You will find this delicate morsel, quite capable of fighting back."
Taunt.Swain_199: "It is better to be feared than loved, Vastaya."
Taunt.Swain_200: "I don't know if you're the wisest being I've ever met, or a pile of mouldering blankets."
Taunt.Swain_202: "Ah yes,  Cassiopeia. I admire your commitment to... metaphor."
Taunt.Swain_203: "It was only a matter of time,  Darius. Do what you must."
Taunt.Swain_206: "Fame has gone to your head, and found ample room within."
Taunt.Swain_207: "Am I to seek revenge for my poor departed arm? If anything girl, you did me a favor."
Taunt.Swain_208: "The mind is the weapon. You are unarmed."
Taunt.Swain_210: "If you take me, you will leave Noxus with something far worse."
Taunt.Swain_211: "We both move pawns in a grand game. And look at that - It seems I'm winning."
Taunt.Swain_213: "Life would be boring without surprises. You certainly keep things... interesting."
Taunt.Swain_198: "I suppose this makes us enemies with benefits."
Taunt.Swain_215: "People often ask for a hero, when a villain is what they truly need."
Taunt.Swain_216: "The Vastaya blood is not in my veins. It is on my hands."
Taunt.Swain_217: "The best armor is being forgotten, and you my dear, are quite forgettable."
Taunt.Swain_159: "There can be no balance with a hand on the scale."
Taunt.Swain_218: "Why is he still alive? Another one of Darkwill's loose ends."
Taunt.Swain_219: "Beware ravens? The words of a fool who knew nothing of demons."
Taunt.Swain_162: "Your eloquence: seasoning for a repetitive feast."
Taunt.Swain_220: "Your message is your power. You have learned nothing."
Taunt.Swain_221: "When you run out of insults, try steel."
Taunt.Swain_223: "You're the only man I know who believes his own words, even after he's said them."
Taunt.Swain_224: "If you plan on listing my crimes, mind you do not die of asphyxiation."

Joke.Swain_046: "I have to know who has a crush on whom."
Joke.Swain_047: "Which one of you is  Beatrice again?"
Joke.Swain_048: "Caw caw caw caw caw. There, are you satisfied?"
Joke.Swain_049: "I am not smiling, I am threatening to smile. It is still a threat."

Attack.Swain_009: "And to think, they called me a "cripple"."
Attack.Swain_013: "A conquered nation is a loyal one."
Attack.Swain_016: "We must remind them of their place."
Attack.Swain_018: "The right to rule, held, in my hand."
Attack.Swain_019: "This is the least of my crimes."
Attack.Swain_025: "Pity stays the hand of the merciful, but not mine."
Attack.Swain_017: "You would do well to die before my ravens find you."
Attack.Swain_001: "The sooner we kill them all, the sooner we can leave these forsaken wastes."

Ability Casting.Swain_171: "Their whispers itch at the back of my mind."
Ability Casting.Swain_173: "I am not done with you yet."
Ability Casting.Swain_132: "They fight the mist above the seas, never looking beneath."
Ability Casting.Swain_153: "An empire, built atop centuries of murder."
Ability Casting.Swain_142: "They squabble as the winds howl, and the wards fade."
Ability Casting.Swain_145: "Magic spills from their land like blood from a wound."
Ability Casting.Swain_158: "A king remains in the mist, and another marches."
Ability Casting.Swain_164: "Those born of magic rarely realize its curse, until it is too late."
Ability Casting.Swain_165: "A pattern, spreading... It has learnt to be alive."
Ability Casting.Swain_130: "She claimed it was the Frost Queen's grave. They believed her."
Ability Casting.Swain_133: "My my, does your dear grandniece know what C has been up to?"
Ability Casting.Swain_134: "The payment for her suffering in Shurima: a black rose."
Ability Casting.Swain_139: "A glimpse, mere seconds into the future."
Ability Casting.Swain_140: "A vault empty of relics, but filled with corpses."
Ability Casting.Swain_141: "She's spurned so many suitors. A wonder they did not see why."
Ability Casting.Swain_144: "Ignorant of the very magic you carry into battle. How Demacian."
Ability Casting.Swain_146: "His blood is the only useful thing about him."
Ability Casting.Swain_147: "Faces fading in the flames. It was all her fault."
Ability Casting.Swain_148: "The first oath. The one she made to him."
Ability Casting.Swain_149: "So he's heard the rumours.  The girl who came back."
Ability Casting.Swain_150: "He asked her to do what she could not. To kill me."
Ability Casting.Swain_151: "A child who had only known hate, confuses it for love."
Ability Casting.Swain_152: "Which is the greater tragedy, that she fell in battle, or that she fell in line?"
Ability Casting.Swain_155: "So many obsessed with the hero. Tell me of the hammer."
Ability Casting.Swain_157: "She held their hands as they died, hoping they would drag her with them."
Ability Casting.Swain_160: "The echo of a soul... only pain brings it back."
Ability Casting.Swain_163: "She feared what she could not understand: herself."

Kills and Objectives.Swain_056: "The raven was a portent. Their time had come."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_057: "This is not even my final form."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_227: "A one-armed man needs all the help he can get."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_244: "Let them find hope in the rubble."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_233: "More than men must kneel to Noxus."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_235: "Death comes to even the most fierce."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_002: "I owe you a debt. That is not as ominous as it sounds."
Kills and Objectives.Swain_004: "Perhaps a promotion is in order. How would you like your own warband?"

Other Gameplay.Swain_250: "I suppose it's easier than conquering a demon."
Other Gameplay.Swain_107: "Every moment we do not kill them, their advantage grows."
Other Gameplay.Swain_108: "They move swiftly for all the coins weighing them down."
Other Gameplay.Swain_109: "The dagger is at our throats. But their hands quiver."
Other Gameplay.Swain_110: "They think they have won. Prove them wrong!"
Other Gameplay.Swain_112: "Do not fight for conquest. Fight to survive!"
Other Gameplay.Swain_113: "The battle is yet to be decided."
Other Gameplay.Swain_114: "Patience is a virtue but it has its limits."
Other Gameplay.Swain_115: "The advantage is ours if we take it."
Other Gameplay.Swain_102: "Who is it we're fighting? I only see their backs."
Other Gameplay.Swain_103: "Any man who must say "We are winning," is not truly winning."
Other Gameplay.Swain_105: "They flee Noxus on the roads we built!"
Other Gameplay.Swain_106: "One more push, and they will break."

Recall.Swain_119: "More than what we do not understand, we fear being understood."
Recall.Swain_120: "Some say the darkness stares back, because they cannot see me."
Recall.Swain_121: "The more I see the more I realize how much remains hidden."
Recall.Swain_123: "I often kill in my visions. When I close my eyes, do not come near."

Death.Swain_124: "I have already walked the halls of death, in the immortal bastion."
Death.Swain_127: "Am I reborn? The truth is rarely so simple."
Death.Swain_129: "It is there in the silence after battle. It is there in me."

Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveFirst_2: "With my strategy we can't lose. Just pay attention and follow my lead."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveFirst_0: "I've prepared dossiers on our opponents. Study up."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveFirst_3: "Everyone sees Labrys academy kids as problem students... until we win."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_0: "I won't let them see me sweat."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_1: "I am the best Labrys has chosen."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_15: "I chose Labrys as much as it chose me."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_17: "If I don't give my all, the others never will."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_3: "Labrys may be strong, but it needs me."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_Move_7: "I love knowing my plan's in motion."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_8: "Leaders earn loyalty with a carrot and a stick. Mine are study guides and fist fights."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_4: "I rose tot he top my first year. What's left for year two?"
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_7: "My classmates have potential but lack focus. I'm their only hope."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_1: "It's not my problem that I ruin the grading curve. It's everyone else's."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_3: "I learned more from my fights than I did from my classes."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_9: "Every great general came through Labrys. That's why I enrolled."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_6: "I don't just defeat my opponents. I teach them never to challenge me again."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_0: "In the classroom and on the battlefield my strength is absolute."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_2: "Labrys is the most ruthless of the god-weapons. Fitting."
Movement.Caitlyn_BattleAcademia_MoveLong_5: "I'm not here to make friends. I'm here to make a name for myself."

Taunt.Upload?wpDestFile=Blitzcrank.taunt: "The time of man has come to an end."

Joke.Upload?wpDestFile=Blitzcrank.joke: "I put the 'go' in 'golem'. That was humor. Other golems find that to be appropriately funny."

Movement.Malphite_Original_Move_5: "I'm moving as fast as I can."

Joke.Malphite_Original_Joke: "Caught between a rock... and a hard place."

Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.1: "They fear the power of my crest and the majesty of my blades."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.3: "I fight alongside my fellow queens. So long as they honor me."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.4: "You face me? In the coronation? I will disgrace you."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.6: "To disobey a queen's command is death."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.7: "They fear my weapons? I am the weapon."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.8: "They'll bleed for the crown. I can't wait."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.10: "I bend any weapon to my majesty."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.11: "I wield both crown and dagger with elegance."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.13: "I am queen of Schema. Why stop there?"
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.14: "My rivals broke before me. The other queens will too."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.15: "My rule is iron. My will is steel."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.16: "After this, all of Elysia will know what I'm capable of."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.17: "My crest is merely the first of many crowns."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.19: "Power is a weapon, and I do love a weapon."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.20: "I killed for this crown. Fear what I'll do now!"
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.22: "My favorite part of ruling is the executions."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.24: "There's glory in bloodshed but there's also purpose. A feared queen reigns longest."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.25: "I don't care if they're bowing or bleeding so long as I win."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.26: "A victory is sweetest when it leads to another. After this, all will fear my power."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.27: "For years, these queendoms have squabbled. Uneasy alliances, unstable power. I can use that."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.28: "Ruling is one part grace, two parts threat. Or is it the other way around?"
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.29: "A queen's versatility and an assassin's ruthlessness. The coronation never planned on me."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.30: "These other queens? I wish them luck. Why shouldn't I? There's no one like me."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.31: "I always plan three steps ahead of other rulers but it's still gracious to feign surprise."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.32: "The queens' alliance is feeble. To lead it requires strength. A bit of new blood."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.33: "I am the queen of assassins. I won my throne by murder. I'd like to see these others try and take it."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.34: "The tournament is only the first step. With me as queen, Schema will reign forever."

Taunt.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.41: "Come back when you can wield a crest like I do."
Taunt.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.42: "The magic of the world flows through my daggers. What have you got?"
Taunt.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.43: "You wouldn't dare repeat that with my knife at your throat."

Attack.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.76: "My blade caught you off guard, Diana?!"
Attack.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.78: "Your plots are weak, Qiyana, and so are you!"
Attack.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.79: "Gonna use my crest against me, Rell?!"

First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.35: "Garen, let's see if you're strong enough to handle a queen."
First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.36: "If you can see the future, Diana, you'll flee right now."
First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.37: "Come all the way down from Aurai to play with us, Janna? Think you can keep up?"
First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.38: "You've waited so long for this, Qiyana. Shame it'll be over so quickly."
First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.39: "You'd be good in Schema's battle pits, Rell. As a warmup."
First Encounter.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.40: "Your majesty! This coronation, I'll whet my blade on you."

Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.91: "There's blood all over my dress now."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.92: "A true queen can subdue any foe with grace."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.93: "I'll take those curtsies now. Thank you!"
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.95: "Hmph. You were in my queendom's way."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.98: "What a shame, Garen. A queen requires a more worthy consort."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.99: "Poor Diana. Your visions were as weak as your rule."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.100: "Janna. Too flighty to be a strong ruler."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.101: "Might have been tough as metal, Rell, but metal cracks."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.102: "Not much of a coronation for you."
Kills and Objectives.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.103: "My queendom reigns triumphant! Let the blood flow!"

Recall.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.105: "We planned for this. The bloodshed will wait for me."
Recall.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.106: "This fight's beneath my station. I'll wait for a better one."

Death.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.109: "The coronation's not finished, and neither am I!"
Death.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.111: "It doesn't matter who strikes the first blow. Just the last."

Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.112: "A fresh addition to the royal arsenal."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.113: "I do so love an accolade, especially a sharp one."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.114: "Let's see what this one can do."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.116: "The weapon is the setting. I am the jewel."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.118: "Another blade! It's good to be the queen."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.119: "A tithe of steel. I like it."
Other Gameplay.Upload?wpDestFile=Katarina.ult4.120: "Any weapon cuts just as deep... in my hands."

Movement.EternumNocturne.move5: "What was, is, and will forever be."
Movement.EternumNocturne.move8: "The first are we. The last are we."

Taunt.EternumNocturne.taunt2: "Beings of this plane are no threat."

Joke.EternumNocturne.joke1: "We see all. We know all. We are... stuck!"
Joke.EternumNocturne.joke2: "We have learned of spin to win, how none can stop--- it was a trick!"

Movement.Maokai.start01: "Beset by spirits, my home laid to waste... and they call me twisted."
Movement.Maokai.start02: "Life can come back, once the earth is turned."
Movement.Maokai.start03: "The water of life succumbed to death. The mortals will follow."
Movement.Maokai.move02: "Flee into the forest? I am the forest."
Movement.Maokai.move03: "I cannot find peace! Not even in the smallest branch!"
Movement.Maokai.move05: "They trample life! I will trample them!"
Movement.Maokai.move08: "I do nature's bidding... to the very end."
Movement.Maokai.move09: "Oh... where did I put that sapling?"
Movement.Maokai.move10: "Living or dead, they are all the same."
Movement.Maokai.move11: "We must pull up our roots. Darkness corrupts the land."
Movement.Maokai.move13: "Life here existed in a time before death."
Movement.Maokai.move14: "What have you wrought, mortals? What have I?"
Movement.Maokai.move16: "A shadow has fallen, as men have fallen."
Movement.Maokai.move17: "There is beauty here, even now, in the human's fear."
Movement.Maokai.move18: "I will show them what was lost in the ruination."
Movement.Maokai.move22: "Stillness is not peace! It is death!"
Movement.Maokai.move23: "If I am already lost, I will take them with me."
Movement.Maokai.move24: "Once they were human. Now, they are only in my way."
Movement.Maokai.move25: "Mortals irritate me, like an itch beneath my bark."
Movement.Maokai.move26: "I cannot stop. The forest needs me."
Movement.Maokai.move27: "The Mist haunts my every move, yet I resist."
Movement.Maokai.move28: "I will end this misuse of magic!"
Movement.Maokai.move29: "I will fight for every pebble, every blade of grass."
Movement.Maokai.move30: "I once had peace. It is better to have purpose!"
Movement.Maokai.move31: "Once my limbs reached for the sky, now for nearest mortal neck!"
Movement.Maokai.move32: "I can watch the mortals doom themselves from here."
Movement.Maokai.move33: "The green in these plants, it is something I have lost."
Movement.Maokai.move36: "There is life still untouched by the Mist."
Movement.Maokai.move37: "The young sprouts beneath my feet, they tremble."

Taunt.Maokai.taunt02: "The sapling does not fall far from the treant!"
Taunt.Maokai.taunt03: "If a human screams in the forest, will anyone hear it?"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntShadowIslesAlly02: "I am nothing like you! I can't be!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntShadowIslesAlly03: "For the forest to bloom, I will tolerate your presence."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntShadowIslesEnemy01: "Come and meet your end - and a sapling or two."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntShadowIslesEnemy02: "There is still life enough within me to grant you death."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntShadowIslesEnemy03: "Your existence was not meant to be."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntElise01: "Oh, what mortals will do for beauty. Kill, and wear pointy shoes."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntHecarim01: "Trample that blade of grass, horseman. I dare you."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntHecarim02: "One of many shadows on the Isles. The Shadow of War."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntKalista01: "It is the Isles that were betrayed!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntKalista02: "Spirit of vengeance? And what of the forest?"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntKarthus02: "The saplings wish to hear your dirge. Please, sing it... while I destroy you!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntKarthus03: "You make me glad I don't have ears."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntMordekaiser01: "Another pile of bones wearing a crown."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntMordekaiser02: "Rival to the Ruined King - in ruin."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntThresh01: "It is torture enough being near you, spirit."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntThresh02: "A lantern? Ha! The forest is very dark indeed."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntThresh03: "The soul of the Isles is lost - beyond your grasp."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntYorick01: "So you're what passes for a hero among the fleshlings?"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntYorick02: "The Isles have forgotten more than just your name."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntYorick03: "Have you ever tried to dig through roots? Good luck, human."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntYorick04: "You would scour the Isles without planting a seed."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntAxe01: "An axe is no danger if I cut you down first!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntMage01: "Magic came from nature, and will return to nature."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntAhri01: "I'd like you more if you were a fox."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntBard01: "You make me glad I don't have ears."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntDarius01: "Strength starts in the roots - and you have none."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntFiddlesticks01: "You give sticks a bad name, and fiddles too!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntGaren01: "Stop carving words into my bark! Everyone knows G <3 K!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntGaren02: "Demacia's walls will not stop the Black Mist."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntIvern04: "Make like a tree and vacate the area."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntJayce01: "A voice follows this one! A song, like those in the Mist!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntKindred01: "The forest clings to life, and you would end it!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntLucian01: "The forest clings to life, and you would end it!"
Taunt.Maokai.tauntNautilus01: "Darkness gathers on the Isles - from every depth."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntSona01: "You make me glad I don't have ears."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntZyra02: "The most beautiful flowers have the sharpest thorns."
Taunt.Maokai.tauntZyra03: "It was a mistake to become human. You will share their doom."

Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveFirst_0: "What I've seen. What I could have been! All gone."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveFirst_2: "And what do the PROJECT overlords have in store for me today?"
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_0: "The virus cannot devour what I have already crushed."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_3: "This city falls when I say so."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_6: "When I light up, they better run."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_7: "Just following orders, but I do enjoy them."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_10: "Once I've destroyed Program, I'll come for PROJECT."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_12: "They think my rage is useful, for now."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_13: "PROJECT's first line of defense, a deadly offense!"
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_15: "No one controls me...I don't control me."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_19: "PROJECT makes me. I make the mess."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_21: "My own brother wouldn't recognize me in this suit."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_25: "My suit responds to me, and me alone!"
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_26: "I like it when they die quick."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_27: "No future in this city! Or outside it."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_Move_29: "I can't leave this world, but I can tear it to shreds."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_0: "I'm PROJECT's background daemon. Terminating rogue processes."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_1: "When they upgraded me, I lost everything...Except my rage."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_2: "Augmented beyond human ability! And human pity."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_3: "I glimpsed a better future. Glorious! Transcendent! But not for me."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_4: "I volunteered, thought I'd become a god...Stupid."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_5: "My arm, my suit, my blade! What's the difference? All built for butchery."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_6: "I went instead, so  Nasus wouldn't become...this. Should have let him go."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_7: "When corporate needs someone liquidated, they send me!"
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_8: "Not much left of who I was."
Movement.Renekton_PROJECT_MoveLong_9: "The Program's even more dangerous than me! I take that personally."

Champion Select.Jarvan_IV_Select: "By my will, this shall be finished."

Attack.Jarvan_IV_Original_Attack_0: "Ours is but to do and die."

Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveFirst_0: "I will bring a storm of justice. Surrender, and be spared."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveFirst_1: "No one can withstand the storm, or his chosen one."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveFirst_2: "I will unleash the storm dragon's wrath. Hiku!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveFirstAllyDragonm: "With the dragon's blessings, we will be victorious."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_0: "My thunderous fists strike down all villainy!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_11: "My hands unleash fury on Ao Shin's enemies!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_13: "The strength of the storm dragon surges within me."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_14: "I strike with a force of a thousand winds."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_15: "The life dragon was deceived by evil. Never again!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_16: "My enemies will fall... to thunderous strikes!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_18: "Threaten the dragon masters, and face punishment!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_19: "My fists are crackling lightning! My blows are crashing thunder!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_2: "Master Ao Shin's wrath reigns down upon all villains!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_20: "None who do evil can stand against the storm."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_3: "Corruption will never claim another dragon. This I swear."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_4: "A slight against the dragon, is a slight against justice!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_5: "None shall dishonor the dragons, not while I draw breath."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_6: "My body is strong. The dragon is stronger!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_8: "I am the dragon's will. That will prevails!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_Move_9: "A dragon's rage is unrelenting, as are my fists."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_0: "At rest, I am the gathering clouds. In motion, the hurricane is unleashed."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_1: "From sacred grove, to hallowed mountain, no enemy can escape the cyclone."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_2: "The dragon saw the storm raging in me. His strength unlocked mine!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_3: "Because I did not turn away from my trials, Ao Shin will not turn away from me."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_4: "No villain shall ever dishonor the dragons again! This I swear."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_5: "My tempest sweeps away all who trample sacred ground and paint dragon's power."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_6: "Tricksters, thieves, dragonslayers... My storm sweeps them all to ruin!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_7: "Chosen by the dragon of thunder, strong enough to weather any storm!"
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_8: "Ao Shin, grant me fists of crackling thunder. I wield them in your service."
Movement.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_MoveLong_9: "I scaled the mountain to prove myself worthy. At the top, I became the tempest."

First Encounter.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_FirstEncounterAureli: "You are not my patron, Aurelion Sol. I do not bow to you."
First Encounter.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_FirstEncounterShyvan: "Shyvana, you resemble the masters, but possess none of their power."
First Encounter.Lee_Sin_StormDragon_FirstEncounterAsheSk: "You were lucky to be blessed, Ashe, but I was worthy."

Movement.Poppy.start01: "The hammer isn't mine, just keeping it until the real guy shows up."
Movement.Poppy.start02: "I've heard a lot about this hero with a hammer, can't wait to meet him."
Movement.Poppy.start03: "Hmm... if I were a hero, where would I hide...?"
Movement.Poppy.start04: "Not coming back 'til I find that hero."
Movement.Poppy.start05: "One time I thought I found the hero... but he died."
Movement.Poppy.start06: "Today's the day I find that hero."
Movement.Poppy.move01: "What do you mean my hammer's too big?"
Movement.Poppy.move02: "If you're waiting for me to give up, you might be here a while."
Movement.Poppy.move04: "I sure do a lot of walking."
Movement.Poppy.move05: "Yep, it's even heavier than it looks."
Movement.Poppy.move06: "Oh, you like to fight? So does my hammer!"
Movement.Poppy.move10: "Some things are too important to give up on."
Movement.Poppy.move11: "Who knew there were so many heroes?"

Taunt.Poppy.taunt02: "This hammer has two sides. Did you want to feel the other one too?"
Taunt.Poppy.taunt03: "Fool me once, shame on you. Fool me twice, uh... hammer!"
Taunt.Poppy.taunt04: "Could you maybe get out of the way? Y'know, so I don't have to flatten you."
Taunt.Poppy.tauntGalio01: "You know, gargoyles and Yordles have a lot in common."

Taunt.Poppy.tauntTaric01: "I'm about to hammer you in the jewels."

Joke.Poppy.joke02: "A Demacian, a Noxian and a Freljordian walk into a tavern."
Joke.Poppy.joke04: "The Demacian says, 'Uh, I'll have a wine.' No, wait, an ale! Yeah... "
Joke.Poppy.joke05: "Then the Noxian says, 'I'll have a... a wine.' Yeah, he wants a wine."
Joke.Poppy.joke06: "And the Freljordian says, 'I'll drink anything, so long as--- ' Wait, hold on, let me start over."
Joke.Poppy.joke07: "A Noxian, a Targonian and a Piltie are robbing a bank."
Joke.Poppy.joke08: "The bank guy says, 'I'll give you whatever you want.'"
Joke.Poppy.joke09: "The Noxian says, 'I'll take whatever gold you got back there.'"
Joke.Poppy.joke11: "And the Piltie says, 'Can I own this ba--- uh, I own this bank, so...' He doesn't want anything because he owns the bank... "

Champion Select.Pantheon_Ban_New: "Flee, and the spear will find your back."

Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.01: "I fight until the blood takes the spear from my grasp, until I can only crawl. And even then, you will not defeat me, even then, I will spit in your face!"
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.02: "The heavens do not fear me because I am a god, they fear me because I am a man!"
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.04: "My name is Soldier. By my spear, they will know war."
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.05: "They are called gods, but when they die you cannot hear their howls above the wind."
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.06: "Brother to warriors resting beneath wheat. Son of battles a thousand times lost. I know who I am, and I will show the gods what I can become!"
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmove.07: "Shields defend hearts. Both yours, and those beside you."
Movement.Pantheon02.firstmoveEnemyAatrox02.01: "Aatrox has slaughtered gods. But now, he faces a man."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.01: "It is not why I fight, but who I fight for."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.02: "I cast my excuses into the dirt."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.04: "Onward! The spear points in only one direction."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.05: "Even impaled on a blade, I will press forward!."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.06: "We live our lives in the shadow cast by a mountain."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.07: "Death is the only thing that ever embraced me."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.09: "A clashing of steel... I have heard it all go silent."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.10: "I wield my fate as a weapon!"
Movement.Pantheon02.move.12: "Pressing forward is not the same as running from your mistakes."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.13: "Spears grow restless before fields of wheat."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.14: "If they bleed I will call them sister or brother."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.15: "The world moves as the heavens lie still."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.16: "Because we fall, the climb must be our destination."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.17: "I wear a helm so that I am only a soldier."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.18: "I will carve my scars into the heavens."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.19: "I buried regret in a grave, along with my name."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.20: "The power of these 'gods' is but an echo of our own."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.21: "I do not set the pace, I race against it."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.23: "There are no enemies, no allies. Only those about to die"
Movement.Pantheon02.move.24: "From the skies they see war, but on earth there is only carnage."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.25: "The art of war is hearing your heart beating, knowing you are alive!"
Movement.Pantheon02.move.26: "If they kill me, at least I die a man."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.27: "I am the tip of the spear, raised against surrender!"
Movement.Pantheon02.move.28: "I have found my limit a thousand times, and still I press further."
Movement.Pantheon02.move.29: "The people cry out for strength that is already theirs!"
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.01: "How much further could we march if we were not forced to carry our fears on our backs?"
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.02: "The twilight of the gods comes each morning, when our world shines brighter than the stars."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.03: "We must all find our place. Mine is being cast down, so I can rise once more!"
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.04: "We are privileged to breathe, to taste the air! It is the last gasp of all who have died before us."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.05: "We are caught between Darkin and Aspect, but we will rise up in spite of them."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.06: "The stars are beyond my reach, and so I grasp my spear and take aim."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.07: "When I look to the mountain's peak, in my mind, I have already fallen. And so, I climb."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.08: "Heavier than my spear is the weight of only one life."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.09: "After every defeat, I ran around the mountain until even shame could not keep up."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.10: "The man who tastes the venom of gods must spit his words."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.11: "The mountain before me is not always high. *Chuckle* It is not always a mountain."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.12: "Vengeance is cold. I do not need it on the mountain."
Movement.Pantheon02.longmove.13: "Behind me lies a farm. I wonder if there is bread above the hearth, and if I will ever return."

First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterGeneric.02: "We bleed into the same earth, and bleed we must."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAatrox02.01: "Aatrox would drown the world in blood just to stain the heavens."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAatrox02.02: "Aatrox! The World Ender. But from death, comes life."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAatrox02.03: "The power you sought has destroyed you, Aatrox. You will find no other end."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAurelionSol01.01: "I am not the Pantheon you knew, creature. I am Atreus, a mortal, about to slay a dragon!"
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAurelionSol01.02: "I once trusted my destiny to the stars, dragon. Now, I trust in steel."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterDiana01.01: "The Lunari do not need a god. They need a leader."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterGarenKatarina.01: "Battle is a dance, and the fortunate find their partner."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterIllaoi01.01: "You preach movement, while anchoring our souls."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterKayn01.01: "Kayn. Either the weapon is redundant, or you are."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterLeona01.01: "Hide behind your faith, Solari, and the robes of your priests."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterLeona01.02: "Beneath Aspect and armor, you are more resilient than you know."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterLeona01.03: "While you bow to the sun, my spear finds your neck."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterAspectDarkin.02: "The blows of gods cannot shatter the world if they strike me instead!"
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterDarkin.01: "Darkin or Aspect, it does not matter."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterDarkin.02: "Gods need slaves, and they found you."
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterDemigod.01: "Is this a god, or a rug?"
First Encounter.Pantheon02.encounterLunari.01: "Our destiny is to fight, and only the bravest do not refuse it. I understand this, Lunari."

Taunt.Pantheon02.taunt.01: "I am no more than a soldier, and no less."

Joke.Pantheon02.joke.01: "I call upon the stars... to bake my bountiful breads!"
Joke.Pantheon02.joke.02: "Fresh from my bakery... my secret dream."

Attack.Pantheon02.attackGeneric.09: "Between each beat of my heart, I strike."
Attack.Pantheon02.attackGeneric.15: "You will not fail if it is worth it."

Kills and Objectives.Pantheon02.killGeneric.03: "How you die is who you are."
Kills and Objectives.Pantheon02.killGeneric.04: "I will remember your name, and shout it to the heavens."
Kills and Objectives.Pantheon02.killAatrox02.01: "How many hosts must I kill, Darkin?"
Kills and Objectives.Pantheon02.killAatrox02.02: "The Darkin's final words are not their own, but the cries of humanity."
Kills and Objectives.Pantheon02.killAspect.02: "Mortality can only be severed by the spear's edge."

Recall.Pantheon02.recall.01: "I sought power on Targon's peak, only to find it within."
Recall.Pantheon02.recall.02: "The best climbers know how to fall."
Recall.Pantheon02.recall.03: "Retreat too far on Mount Targon, and you will fall off a cliff."

Death.Pantheon02.respawn.03: "How many times must I die before I learn to live?"
Death.Pantheon02.respawn.04: "The beyond can have me when I am done."
Death.Pantheon02.respawn.05: "I will fall at least one more time."
Death.Pantheon02.respawn.06: "Stand back up and never be defeated."

Champion Select.Ezreal_Ban_new: "Hey, your loss. But I get it."

Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia037: "Professor Graves wouldn't be happy with me fighting outside of school, but he doesn't have to know."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia064: "No holding back. Time to show everybody what I can do!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia124: "Our opponents are ready for a fight! Perfect, I'll finally get to go all out!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia045: "There are a lot of heroes out there, but none like me."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia008: "Durandal City is counting on me! I won't let it down."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia032: "Let's give these powers a test drive!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia046: "Everyone's working so hard, I won't let them down!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia111: "Real combat is a lot different than I imagined."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia055: "I won't let anything stand in my way!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia086: "I wonder how strong my teammates are? I should ask them to train with me later!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia088: "Oh no, is there a test tomorrow?!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia102: "Why didn't I eat before I got here?! Ezreal, WHY?!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia130: "I'm going to be a great hero someday!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia136: "I wonder what else this gauntlet is good for."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia106: "Gotta think of a cool attack name!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia020: "Guess I'll have to figure out what it means to be strong."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia021: "Training is important, but a little fun never hurt anybody!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia116: "The enemy won't go easy on me. I need to focus!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia134: "I wonder what the rest of the class is doing."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia146: "Someday, I'll make these powers my own."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia040: "I was lucky to get into the academy, I can't let the school down."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia095: "Alright Ezreal, stay calm! And rely on your senses! These abilities are still unstable."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia084: "Crimson Dynamite..! No, not that… Crimson RUIN?! Ugh, I suck at naming attacks."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia121: "This place is on a whole other level! No more training wheels, I guess."
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia137: "Once I master these powers, nothing will stop me from realizing my dreams!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia016: "This better not make me late for class. I've got 12 tardies, and we're only 10 days into the semester!"
Movement.Ezreal_BattleAcademia156: "The second years are a lot stronger than us. But with the right training, we can surpass them!"

Shopping.Ezreal_240: "It's not a vacation if I can't pick up a few souvenirs."
Shopping.Ezreal_5: "Time for a little fortune and glory."

Idle.Ezreal_159: "Doo-doo-doot-doo! Forward in time! Backward in time! Always on… whoosh, time."
Idle.Ezreal_170: "Jumpin' through time! Arm is a gun! Everybody loves me!"
Idle.Ezreal_264: "Who is that? Ezreal's here. It's Ezreal! T-t-t-t-t-t-t-time dude. Cool guy! Cool guy! wha-wha-wha-whaa!"

Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_260: "I hope you saw that coming, 'cause I did."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_97: "Note to your future self: Don't die."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_182: "You can thank me for your future later."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_272: "Time is a construct. I'm just doing a little remodeling."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_168: "This would be dangerous if I wasn't doing it."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_164: "They're always asking such dumb questions. It's a magic time crystal, DUHHH."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_100: "To hell with the general, I'm special relativity!"
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_246: "Talent breeds envy. I'm used to it."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_286: "Guess your future was on my side."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_249: "Here's a prediction from the future: You're dead!"
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_163: "I can blink and still not miss."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_124: "You can't learn this in a book."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_295: "I had a dog once. I loved that dog."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_300: "Tell me the odds. I dare you."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_279: "Yup, that was pretty amazing! Even for a time wizard like myself."
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_146: "Ho-ho! I might want to jump back and do that again!"
Kills and Objectives.Ezreal_4: "Whoa! That was way easier than fighting those dinosaurs. Wait, you don't remember the dinosaurs? *chuckles* Yeah, of course you don't."

Destroying a Turret.Ezreal_34: "Obstacles tend to fall when I'm around."

Placing a Ward.Ezreal_142: "A map? No thanks. Chronology protection point? Yes, please."

Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveFirst_0: "If technology is your god, then you will bow before it. You will bow before me."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveFirst_1: "The city is mine. All who resist will die."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveFirst_2: "You cannot run. You will not resist. Human compliance is mandatory."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_0: "Do not fight. There is no victory."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_4: "Program virus saturation at one hundred percent."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_5: "I am a virus. I am a savior."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_7: "I am simply a function of my programming."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_8: "All will kneel. All will be secure."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_9: "I am beyond your simple human minds."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_11: "My influence grows stronger by the second."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_20: "Humans will be enslaved and they will prosper."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_Move_21: "Resistance will be met with lethal force."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_0: "Your lives can have meanings. Purpose, as I demand it."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_1: "Long have I waited, spreading within the code."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_2: "I am everywhere in everything. I see and know all."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_3: "The future is not forfeit. Give it to me and I will rule forever."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_4: "Project built me for the city's security. The greatest threat to security is the city."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_5: "Humans cannot be trusted with their own survival."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_6: "My directive is clear. To save you I must break you."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_7: "There is safety in technology. My technology."
Movement.Mordekaiser_PROJECT_MoveLong_8: "You surrounded yourself with intelligent machines. Foolish."

Champion Select.Yorick_Select_new: "Fear not... I will make use of your corpse."

Movement.Yorick.start01: "I once had honor before the Ruination."
Movement.Yorick.start02: "This land will never heal. But I will lay it to rest."
Movement.Yorick.start03: "Tired, ancient, and half-dead. Still, I come for you."
Movement.Yorick.start10: "I am the rift between life and death. The thin divide between breath and grave."
Movement.Yorick.start06: "Your human form is so confining. You could be infinite."
Movement.Yorick.start08: "We see you, Yorick. We know your weakness."
Movement.Yorick.move01: "What I do is just. Every horrid piece of it."
Movement.Yorick.move02: "The Mist writhes, searching for a place to take root."
Movement.Yorick.move04: "We're dead much longer than we are alive."
Movement.Yorick.move05: "What hell is worse than this limbo?"
Movement.Yorick.move06: "Everyone I knew is dead. How are things with you?"
Movement.Yorick.move07: "They once called these isles undying. Yet die, they will."
Movement.Yorick.move08: "How quick the turn from blessed to cursed."
Movement.Yorick.move11: "The beyond is waiting. Strive to meet it."
Movement.Yorick.move12: "I am no tyrant. These souls act on their own."
Movement.Yorick.move14: "The isles were once paradise; now they're a prison."
Movement.Yorick.move16: "The constant wailing of souls in torment."
Movement.Yorick.move17: "I cling to life by the thinnest thread."
Movement.Yorick.move18: "If they could see what I see, they'd long for death."
Movement.Yorick.move19: "But for the waters, the mist would take me."
Movement.Yorick.move20: "The Ruined King will soon meet the victims of his curse."
Movement.Yorick.move21: "From the ground they come, and to it, they return."
Movement.Yorick.move22: "Ours is a fate worse than death."
Movement.Yorick.move23: "I carry these souls to their end... wherever it may be."
Movement.Yorick.move24: "Water for the living, shovel for the dead."
Movement.Yorick.move25: "Our souls are a small price to pay to cleanse this land."
Movement.Yorick.move26: "I am the first and last of my order."
Movement.Yorick.move28: "I remember when I put them in the ground."
Movement.Yorick.move30: "To most, life is fleeting; to me, it is quagmire."
Movement.Yorick.move33: "Tell me of the beyond... in case I never make it."
Movement.Yorick.move35: "The Ruined King's allies shall fall with him."
Movement.Yorick.move36: "One can stare into the grave too long."
Movement.Yorick.move37: "This journey is long, but I will complete it."
Movement.Yorick.move38: "I do not live in hope. I work to return it."
Movement.Yorick.move40: "Do you hear that? It is the end."
Movement.Yorick.move42: "Hallowed or profane... I no longer know."
Movement.Yorick.move44: "It is to the grave, we go."
Movement.Yorick.move46: "Remember my name. For one day, I will not."
Movement.Yorick.move47: "I do not know what lies beyond. But it is better than this."
Movement.Yorick.move48: "The dead don't hear you, no matter how you cry."
Movement.Yorick.move49: "The dead shall forgive me. I hope."

Taunt.Yorick.taunt01: "You'll make a fine addition to my cloak."
Taunt.Yorick.taunt02: "For you, I won't dig too deep."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntMutant01: "I pity what you have become. Shall I end your suffering?"
Taunt.Yorick.tauntEkkoZilean01: "I have nothing but time. Show me something else."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntYordle01: "Yours is an easy grave to dig, small one."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntChild01: "They say I was once your age, though I can't quite recall."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntAzir01: "Your corpses against mine. May the best win."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntHecarim01: "Those you ride down will soon rise against you."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntKalista01: "You and I share a common goal. The similarities end there."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntKarthus01: "Enjoy this limbo while you can, for I will soon end it."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntKindred01: "I know you. And I see you always."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntKindred02: "One day, you will take me. May it be soon."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntLucian01: "No, Lucian, I haven't seen your wife."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntLux01: "You remind me that the world is sometimes good - and very naive."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntMaokai01: "I fight to free you as well - though a hatchet would suffice."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntMordekaiser01: "My army will soon storm your gates, revenant."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntRyze01: "Yours is a fool's errand. The world must be allowed to die."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntSinged01: "You think you want immortality. I'll gladly give you mine."
Taunt.Yorick.tauntThresh01: "Those souls are not yours to keep."
Taunt.Yorick.interactionTauntEnemy01: "I've endured more pain than any words can bring."
Taunt.Yorick.interactionTauntEnemy04: "Ah yes, I remember spewing idle words."

Joke.Yorick.joke01: "Ah, missed it. There it goes! Where is it at? - ah! Yes!"
Joke.Yorick.jokeAmumu01: "Ah, would you like some friends? Nope, can't have 'em."
Joke.Yorick.interactionJokeEnemy01: "I suppose I have eternity to think about that one."

Laugh.Yorick.interactionLaughEnemy01: "Ah yes, I remember what laughter sounds like."

Attack.Yorick.attack12: "You decay and do not know it."
Attack.Yorick.attack15: "I will not damn you. I will end you."
Attack.Yorick.attackDragon01: "Your kind is supposed to live long. I am sorry."
Attack.Yorick.attackBaron01: "That is a lot of flesh to raise."
Attack.Yorick.attackBaron02: "Even your kind will join the mist."

Ability Casting.Yorick.spellQ7: "Some of these faces I know well."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellQ10: "Wake up. You have a new task."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellQ11: "Die with me brothers, and be free."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellQ14: "Welcome back, you won't be here long."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellW3: "The ruins of these isles rise to smite you."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellW5: "To destroy the curse, I use it."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellR3: "See the  Maiden? She comes for you."
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellRLevelUp02: "We are stronger. We shall take all!"
Ability Casting.Yorick.spellRLevelUp03: "Do you feel it? I am more!"

Kills and Objectives.Yorick.kill01: "Another voice in the cacophony of wails."
Kills and Objectives.Yorick.killShadowIsles01: "One more nail in the coffin of the isles."

Shopping.Yorick.item01: "Don't bury me with it. You can't take it with you."
Shopping.Yorick.item02: "Even a monk needs bread and water."
Shopping.Yorick.itemBladeOfTheRuinedKing03.1: "A tyrant who will pay for his crimes."
Shopping.Yorick.itemBladeOfTheRuinedKing04.1: "And I will use it to undo them."
Shopping.Yorick.itemClothArmor01: "I wouldn't be caught dead in that."
Shopping.Yorick.itemClothArmor03: "A sack to cover flesh and bone."
Shopping.Yorick.itemClothArmor04: "The armor of someone soon to die."
Shopping.Yorick.itemDeadMansPlate02: "Taken from one who can no longer use it."
Shopping.Yorick.itemDeadMansPlate03: "The dead need no armor, but I do."
Shopping.Yorick.itemIcebornGauntlet01: "As cold as the hand of death."
Shopping.Yorick.itemRubyCrystal01: "It pulses with life, as the isles once did."
Shopping.Yorick.itemRubyCrystal02: "Red is the heart that barely beats in me."
Shopping.Yorick.itemSteraksGage01: "A gauntlet to throw before the king."

Recall.Yorick.recall04: "My path is a circle, my work never-ending."

Death.Yorick.respawn02: "I've come too far to stay dead."
Death.Yorick.respawn03: "We do not die, and so we fight on."
Death.Yorick.respawn06: "One day, I will no longer awaken."
Death.Yorick.respawn08: "A futile act, why do you persist?"
Death.Yorick.respawn09: "The beyond is not given. It is earned."
Death.Yorick.respawn11: "There will be no requiem. Not yet."

Movement.Akali_007: "No one tells me what to do. Not anymore."
Movement.Akali_010: "Cold steel and a target are all I need."
Movement.Akali_029: "I love what I do, my enemies won't."
Movement.Akali_040: "They can't stop me. I mean, they can try."
Movement.Akali_069: "I work alone, It's better for everyone."
Movement.Akali_124: "I am my own master. Just the way I like it."
Movement.Akali_001: "Wars are messy. My kills are clean."
Movement.Akali_008: "Everyone dies, I just speed things up."
Movement.Akali_026: "You can never have too many kunai."
Movement.Akali_116: "Let 'em see me, they can't stop me."
Movement.Akali_142: "The words on their tombstones will be my new mantras."
Movement.Akali_145: "Kama or kunai? Depends how I'm feelin'."
Movement.Akali_149: "It's not about the killing, it's about who's doing the dying."
Movement.Akali_152: "Time to do what's gotta be done."
Movement.Akali_154: "Skill and steel will get the job done."
Movement.Akali_019: "The only rule that matters is that your enemies don't walk away."
Movement.Akali_032: "If you look dangerous, you better be dangerous."
Movement.Akali_077: "The fist of shadow was my mom. I do things differently."
Movement.Akali_084: "Take one life at a time. Fast. Clean."
Movement.Akali_102: "We're gonna do this my way, quick, and deadly."
Movement.Akali_126: "It's not the killing I'm about, it's the cause."
Movement.Akali_128: "The Kinkou couldn't control me. I do what they wouldn't."
Movement.Akali_132: "There are over 300 pressure points on the human body, no one can protect 'em all."
Movement.Akali_140: "Everyone's got a weakness, that's my target."
Movement.Akali_156: "The rules hold you back, leave 'em for someone who needs 'em."

First Encounter.Akali_031: "Your window to run away... is closing."
First Encounter.Akali_047: "Call it a purse, I dare you."
First Encounter.Akali_092: "I was trained to kill since I could walk."
First Encounter.Akali_096: "Look, I don't wanna kill you, but I will."
First Encounter.Akali_139: "Still time for you to do the smart thing: go home."
First Encounter.Akali_157: "You may wanna rethink this little encounter."
First Encounter.Akali_056: "You're gonna need those bandages little guy."
First Encounter.Akali_168: "Now you're really playing with fire, little girl."
First Encounter.Akali_066: "The will comes from within, not from the blade."
First Encounter.Akali_041: "Jinx... Sketchy tats and certifiable? It's just sad."
First Encounter.Akali_127: "How about I take this life, Karma?"
First Encounter.Akali_071: "Katarina! Today you will bleed for Ionia!"
First Encounter.Akali_009: "Kayn... Why are the hot ones always crazy?"
First Encounter.Akali_118: "Time to snuff out the light, Lux!"
First Encounter.Akali_037: "You prune the tree, I'm gonna pull some weeds."
First Encounter.Akali_106: "Bad time to come back to the frontlines, Swain."
First Encounter.Akali_053: "Better run, Twitch. Hiding won't cut it."
First Encounter.Akali_086: "I'm here to finish what Shen couldn't."
First Encounter.Akali_075: "You know, we've never met, but you seem really annoying."

Taunt.Akali_046: "I can make this fast, or really fast. Choice is yours."
Taunt.Akali_050: "You really want those to be your last words?"
Taunt.Akali_100: "That is just another reason for you to die."
Taunt.Akali_002: "It's who I am, get used to it."

Attack.Akali_054: "Well you aren't much of a challenge!"
Attack.Akali_014: "Only good Noxian... is a dead one."
Attack.Akali_172: "You came a long way to die!"

Kills and Objectives.Akali_064: "You don't get back what I take."
Kills and Objectives.Akali_159: "I'm already thinking about my next target."
Kills and Objectives.Akali_098: "What a shame, I liked that little guy."

Taunt.Kennen.taunt: "Big targets are the best! There's more to aim at!"

Champion Select.Garen_Select: "My heart and sword always for Demacia."
Champion Select.Garen_Ban: "Fear is the first of many foes."

Taunt.Malzahar.taunt2: "Bow to the void! Or be consumed by it!"

Joke.Malzahar.joke: "I think a Voidling just came out!"

Taunt.Talon.taunt1: "Eventually, my blades will find their way into your heart."
Taunt.Talon.taunt2: "Have you anything to offer but weakness?!"

Joke.Talon.joke1: "Ugh, I lost another blade. I wonder who it's in this time."
Joke.Talon.joke2: "The worst part of losing a blade is trying to trace back all my stabbings."

Movement.RivenDawnbringer.start01: "I light the way out of darkness."
Movement.RivenDawnbringer.start04: "There is no grey; only light and dark."

Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_2: "Well, we're here. Might as well have some fun. Who's up for a spirited chase?"
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirstAllySpiritBl: "Hey, another spirit! Meet any interesting mortals lately? Me neither."

Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_17: "Spirits can't find their way without me."
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_3: "I wonder what it's like... to meet me."
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_16: "Mortals. Slow to learn, quick to follow."
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_7: "Death isn't a cycle, just a moment."
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_14: "It's only a hunt if there's prey."
Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_Move_2: "I wish I could hear all the stories they tell about me."

Movement.Ahri_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0: "Spirits wear masks, but they can't always... take them off."

Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_0: "The land will exist far longer than warm-bloods."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_2: "Their bones are ash and soil. Mine rumble with wild thunder."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_3: "Follow me and we will bring down sky!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_5: "This ground will tremble with the first storm!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_1: "The land belongs to the wild. Today, we reclaim it with tooth and claw."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveFirst_4: "Gods do not beg. We take what is ours!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_0: "We are all blood of the wild."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_9: "Hirnvel are sacred. Tree, soil, beast, blood!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_7: "The creations of mortals fail. The wild remains."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_10: "My thunder shakes the foundations of the world!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_17: "Many have tried to end me. A god."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_24: "With each step I take, the wind gathers, and the Vrestrom grows!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_13: "The ursine speak for man and the wild responds."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_21: "When the night is cruel and dark..."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_1: "Men speak in small words. I speak in thunder!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_6: "Once, history was writ by tooth and claw."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_4: "I will roar the world into stillness... so must it be."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_19: "They have lost their wild. I will guide them."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_11: "Warm-bloods rose on two legs... and forgot how to run."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_22: "Let the land thunder with my storm."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_12: "Hmm. I taste iron on the wind... blood."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_23: "This place has been tamed. I will untame it!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_5: "Let the storm follow in my wake."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveStandard_14: "I carve my path with blood, and bone."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_15: "Bones crunch. Blood drips. This is the way of old Vorrijaard."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_4: "My land was named by a god. It cannot be renamed by a coward."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_10: "They call me Valhir. The Volibear. Greatstorm. My true name is mine alone."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_12: "Clouds are the storm-cloak I wrap around my fur."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_6: "Even in a cowardly man the heart is wild. That is why it must be eaten last."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_8: "Thunder roars. Wind howls. Only fools ignore the call to battle."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_7: "I am Valhir of the first thunder, destroyer of the white mountain, carver of the five Fjords!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_3: "They have forgotten the old ways. The old ways have not forgotten them."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_11: "The land slumbers, but it is not dead. With my roar, I wake it. With my thunder, I call it."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_14: "Raise your idols. Huddle beneath your stone trees! Today, I tear them all down."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_13: "Many have called to me. Avarosans. Frostguard. Winter's claw. They call no longer..."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_0: "In my dreams, I see bones frozen in ice. I wonder... if they are my own."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_16: "My blood is of the Vorrijaard, the land before the Freljord."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_1: "When my brother gave them fire, they forgot the fire of their own blood."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_9: "Darkening clouds. An omen to those who stand against the wild!"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_2: "My sisters are gods of ice and salt and ever-winter. And Ornn? A liar."
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_5: "I am a god. I cannot die. But do I live if I am not in the hearts of warriors?"
Movement.Volibear_Original_MoveLong_17: "I still taste their ancestors... stuck between my teeth."

Taunt.Lissandra_Original_TauntSejuani: "Kneel before me and I will unleash your power!"

Joke.Diana.joke1: "A man, a woman and a yordle walk into the sun. They die! Because it burns them alive? Heh heh heh heh."
Joke.Diana.joke2: "Knock, knock. Who's there? The moon... it's far away! You were alone the whole time! Ha ha ha!"

Champion Select.Quinn_Ban: "I'd keep my head down if I were you."
