Movement.Syndra.move6: "More! I can be so much more!"

Taunt.Syndra.taunt1: "Immense power is fun! You should try it sometime."
Taunt.Syndra.taunt2: "A legion couldn't stop me. What chance do you have?"

Joke.Syndra.joke1: "And they said I lacked balance. Ha!"

Movement.AurelionSol.start01: "They call me a comet. They call me a dragon. They have no words for my true form."
Movement.AurelionSol.start02: "Cower, worship, beg, they're all valid reactions."
Movement.AurelionSol.start03: "In a constantly shifting cosmos, a world this static is... refreshing."
Movement.AurelionSol.start04: "There simply are no other dragons like me."
Movement.AurelionSol.start06: "Hope. Wonder. Insignificance. Imagine what they'll feel when I complete the stars."
Movement.AurelionSol.move01: "This world holds the key to Targon's undoing."
Movement.AurelionSol.move02: "Targon has used me as its weapon for far too long."
Movement.AurelionSol.move04: "I would burn the cosmos to catch Targon in the flames."
Movement.AurelionSol.move05: "The depths of space crawl with terrible entities. Pray they ignore this world."
Movement.AurelionSol.move06: "There are countless colors, but I suppose a single rainbow is a good start."
Movement.AurelionSol.move07: "This sun is off its axis - it's been driving me crazy for eons now."
Movement.AurelionSol.move08: "Planetary life... the insufferable byproduct of dim stars."
Movement.AurelionSol.move10: "Nothing kindles wonder like the beauty of stars."
Movement.AurelionSol.move11: "Celestial dragons live and die by our own beautiful rules."
Movement.AurelionSol.move12: "Love is as real a force as gravity. Try it once in a while."
Movement.AurelionSol.move13: "Stars are not born, they are made... by me."
Movement.AurelionSol.move14: "A star's birth is as violent as it is breathtaking."
Movement.AurelionSol.move15: "I've waited millennia to watch Targon fall."
Movement.AurelionSol.move16: "All beings are made of the same stardust."
Movement.AurelionSol.move17: "With a few more basic elements I could really make this place shimmer."
Movement.AurelionSol.move18: "The stars are not to thank for any good luck one may experience."
Movement.AurelionSol.move19: "This sun could do with a new core."
Movement.AurelionSol.move20: "Any relevant species has been knocked back into the Stone Age once or twice."
Movement.AurelionSol.move21: "I wouldn't navigate by the stars. They are a work in progress."
Movement.AurelionSol.move22: "Each star is one of my hearts."
Movement.AurelionSol.move23: "My works are revered by worlds I have never even visited."
Movement.AurelionSol.move24: "Wherever I am is the fashionable part of the universe. Even here."
Movement.AurelionSol.move27: "A star is so much more than a luminous sphere of wonder."
Movement.AurelionSol.move28: "If you ask me, we have set the bar too low for sentience."
Movement.AurelionSol.move29: "My home is in the cosmos, amongst my stars."
Movement.AurelionSol.move30: "The stories they tell about me? They're probably true."
Movement.AurelionSol.move31: "All terrestrial dragons are but pale imitations of my kind."
Movement.AurelionSol.move32: "Perhaps there is more to this world than I thought - not much, but enough."
Movement.AurelionSol.move34: "Why does anyone wish upon a star?"
Movement.AurelionSol.move35: "Stars never align for anyone - except me, of course."
Movement.AurelionSol.move38: "Only when darkness overwhelms the heavens will Targon realise its folly."
Movement.AurelionSol.move40: "Targon will be the pyre from which I forge a new heaven."
Movement.AurelionSol.move41: "I see a universe drained of light and heat, where not even a story will survive."
Movement.AurelionSol.move42: "I grieve for every star never born."
Movement.AurelionSol.move44: "Whenever I think my work is complete, I end up back here, under this sun."
Movement.AurelionSol.moveEnemyBase01: "May I enter? Just joking - star dragons don't need permission."

Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt01: "Your demise will be sung about for ages to come - only thanks to its proximity to me, of course."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt02: "Your survival is not impossible, only very... very... very unlikely."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt03: "I shall be the last thing you see. Lucky you."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt04: "Make a wish. See if the stars answer. I'll wait."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt05: "What is the definition of underwhelming? Oh, right! You."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt06: "I used to wander the stars. Now I'm stuck down here, with you."
Taunt.AurelionSol.taunt07: "On other worlds, there is emerging life more complex than you."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntAhri01: "You aspire to be human? Oh, darling, there are so many other variants on mediocrity!"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntAmumu01: "I am... overwhelmed by an emotion when you are not around. It is called... happiness."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntAnnie01: "Mages are infants grasping at the machinery behind reality. At least you have a plausible excuse."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntAzir01: "You Ascended certainly know how to pick an animal totem."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntAzir02: "Your immortality is but a grain of sand in time's vast desert."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntBard01: "Pick a dimension, Bard, you're confusing them!"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntBard02: "Were you born this flat, or did you work at it?"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntCaitlyn01: "The funnier the hat, the greater the prestige, right?"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntDiana01: "You and Leona embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntDiana02: "It is always a moon's role to envy the stars."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntEkko01: "Made a mistake? Better rewind and repeat until you achieve mediocrity."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi02: "I've seen the main act. You're only a third-rate cover band."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntIllaoi01: "You do not understand your god, Illaoi."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntJhin: "Imagine what you could do with a larger canvas."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntJinx01: "Life is short, go crazy once in a while, I get it."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntLeona02: "You and Diana embody the same light. Typical Targon redundancy."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntMalphite01: "There is a saying on this planet - "Dumb as a rock". It's not a compliment."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntMissFortune01: "You are going to kill me? Dressed like that?"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntNasus01: "Bravo, Nasus, you've ascended yourself into a dog! Now fetch me something more interesting."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntNasus02: "I could teach an old dog millions of new tricks, but I simply don't like you, Nasus."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntPantheon01: "Your fate was sealed the moment you picked up Targon's spear."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntRammus01: "Are you burdened by your own monotony? Because I am."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntRenekton01: "That whole practice of Ascension is adorably amusing, like a kitten trying to walk upright."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntRyze01: "Ah, Ryze, I see you've brought paper to take notes."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntRyze02: "True magic is beyond language. Writing merely butchers the intent."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntRyze03: "Magic tattoos? Where did you get those, magic prison?... oh."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntShyvana02: "A dragon's loyalty is a priceless gift. Do not waste it in the service of fools."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntShyvana03: "Medium flame, and that is me being generous."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntSoraka01: "Twinkle, twinkle, little star, do you wonder what you are?"
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntTahmKench01: "The heavens drag on endlessly... much like a conversation with you."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntTaric01: "You're an Aspect? Let me guess - tackiness."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntTryndamere01: "Galaxies exist by my will - but, yes, that is certainly an impressive sword."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntVi02: "You are going to punch a star dragon. Good luck with that."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntZac01: "I empathize with your life as a weapon, but have a little backbone."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntZilean01: "You bend time the way a child folds origami - cute, but nothing special."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntHuman01: "Ah, mankind. Ever fumbling from one brink of cataclysm to the next."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntHuman02: "Humanity, surprisingly adept in the art of wrestling survival from the clutches of extinction."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntHuman03: "As far as fauna goes, humans strike a firm... middle."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntTargon01: "The Aspect of Targon? Sparks masquerading as lightning."
Taunt.AurelionSol.tauntTargon02: "I will cauterize Targon with star fire."

Joke.AurelionSol.joke01: "Few can impress me. That is a compliment."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke02: "Which star is your favorite? I made that one."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke03: "I made the stars... but you inspire me to make more."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke04: "First you start with some matter, then add star fire and voila! It basically does the rest itself."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke05: "Runeterra? I mean the name of this world literally means 'magic earth'."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke06: "I made the stars to illuminate the perpetual nothing, and mortals use them for... relationship advice."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke07: "A sun is unimaginable celestial power - and thrilled mortals use theirs to coordinate this 'lunch time'."
Joke.AurelionSol.joke09: "Of course I love Runeterra! You have buildings and... more buildings."

Dance.AurelionSol.dance01: "Hello, Runeterra! Are you ready to rock?"

Attack.AurelionSol.attack11: "Lighten up, destruction needn't be a maudlin affair."
Attack.AurelionSol.attack12: "Suns never burn for the benefit of dust."
Attack.AurelionSol.attack19: "I'm going to throw a star at you now. Good luck."
Attack.AurelionSol.attack23: "Nothing a little star fire cannot fix."
Attack.AurelionSol.attackDragon01: "Terrestrial dragons - a study of flawed constitutions."
Attack.AurelionSol.attackDragon03: "You call yourself a dragon? You're low-flame at best."
Attack.AurelionSol.attackDragon04: "A dragon that still needs wings to fly? Keep trying, you'll get there."
Attack.AurelionSol.attackDragon05: "I did mean to call you back, but stars needed forging."

Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellIkill03: "The stars weep for you. Just kidding - I already forgot your name."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellIkill04: "My wish upon a star came true."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellImultikill02: "Stars are best viewed from a distance."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellImultikill03: "The stars were not in their favor."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellImultikill04: "I guess their fate was written in the stars."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellQ7: "A little dim - but it still works."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.spellQ9: "This will be quite the deadly spectacle."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.attack03: "Let's end this on a high note!"
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.attack05: "Never stand in the path of a star."
Ability Casting.AurelionSol.attack07: "It's beyond too late to seek cover."

Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.tower01: "All towers fall - it's just what they do when I'm around."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.tower02: "Nothing they build can endure like the celestial firmament."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.tower03: "Towers tend to crumble when I am in the vicinity."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.tower04: "Topple, like all things crafted by mortals."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.tower05: "The architects of these towers misunderstand object permanence."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.towerKill01: "How many must I knock down before they learn?"
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.firstblood01: "You may look forward to more of this."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.ace01: "Never stop when you're on a roll."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.ace02: "I shall inscribe this moment in the stars."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.pentakill01: "That ought to keep them talking for the next century or so."
Kills and Objectives.AurelionSol.pentakill02: "Cosmic dragon; five. Everyone else; zero. Please, take notes."

Shopping.AurelionSol.item01: "Put it on my tab. The name's Pantheon, with a P."
Shopping.AurelionSol.item03: "Pay? Do you know who I am?"
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRodofAges01: "Some things are simply better with age."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRodofAges02: "Ages? This thing has been around for centuries, tops."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRodofAges03: "It's been around for ages? So... almost new."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRodofAges04: "All things appreciate in value over time."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRabadonsDeathcap02: "As long as it's set at a jaunty angle I'm in."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemOrbofWinter01: "A snow globe? Perfect for my collect - to destroy you. Destroy you!"
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter01: "Time to slow things down a bit."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemRylaisCrystalScepter02: "A bit gaudy for my tastes but exceedingly useful."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment02: "Perfect for the bimillenial celestial masquerade ball."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemLiandrysTorment03: "If Bard and Kindred can pull off wearing a mask, so can I."
Shopping.AurelionSol.itemLudensEcho01: "There are no echoes where I'm from."

Recall.AurelionSol.recall04: "Always know when to make an entrance - and an exit."

Death.AurelionSol.death01: "Alas, I am simply too beautiful for this world."
Death.AurelionSol.death04: "The brightest stars shine on long after they're gone."
Death.AurelionSol.deathShyvana01: "Darling, you have but set my hearts free."
Death.AurelionSol.shutdown01: "With a lifespan as comically brief as yours, I suppose I can allow you to taste triumph at least once."
Death.AurelionSol.shutdown02: "Ah, the joys of lesser organisms rising up to slay their betters! If only they were aware of the impermanence of being... or the permanence of me."
Death.AurelionSol.respawn02: "Because I am a star dragon. That's why."
Death.AurelionSol.respawn03: "It's not a comeback if one was never truly gone."

Shopping.ShadowAssassin.purchaseItem02: "Oh yes, this is the right choice."

Other Gameplay.ShadowAssassin.placeWard01: "I live in shadow, others need light."
Other Gameplay.ShadowAssassin.placeWard02: "My enemies will have no place to hide."
Other Gameplay.ShadowAssassin.destroyWard02: "Sight, a pitiful crutch for the weak."
Other Gameplay.ShadowAssassin.destroyWard03: "Are you afraid now? You should be."

Movement.Zoe.Unknown096: "Hey guys, so, cosmic change time, possible armageddon, twilight of the gods, blah blah blah. You've been heralded."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown112: "There are so many weirdos here... It's awesome!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown106: "I bring a message for you all: a warning, a sigil. But first, I wanna see the sparkle flies."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown090: "Hello? Hey, I'm over here if you want to aim a high-velocity attack against me! Maybe you'll hit me this time!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown092: "Anyone wanna go into that ankle-deep liquid? Hello? Hellooooo!!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown111: "Here we go on an adventure, through this place! Even though we don't know the name of it! It doesn't matter!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown108: "The sky is billions of explosions burning far away! How could you not wanna see them?? I did. They were pretty cool."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown109: "This will be fine! Don't worry about it Zoe, things break all the time. Like reality, planets... y'know, stuff."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown100: "The sun and moon rise in time, to ash and mirth. The mountain takes... all. Change comes."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown099: "When the beings here look up, do they think we're looking back?! We really aren't."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown097: "Heyyyy! I'm gonna have new friends, new friends here, and it's gonna be awesome 'cause they are awesome and we'll have an awesome party with cake and stuff!" *gasp* "Should I make chocolate mooncake or strawberry mooncake?" *gasp* "CHOCOLATE STRAWBERRY CAKE!!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown093: "There's this illusion of the reality, but it's not really really real, like it's beside and inside and inside and beside, but never on top... Nevermind, just kidding, but not really.."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown098: "Ohh! I like how the atmospheric refraction is favoring intense short waves today!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown101: "The sky called to me. So I went! It was pretty cool. I like this too, though."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown102: "Psst! Hey! Can you tell me your secrets? I promise not to tell them to... everyone!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown107: "There are holes in reality. And... in donuts."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown104: "We don't try to understand the sense it doesn't make, so we're trying to share that with you. You're welcome."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown110: "There is a day we must all fulfill our destiny. ...That day is taco day!!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown105: "So, there's these, like, yinger and yangerons, and they spin in this projected pattern which intersects fourth-dimensionally. But it isn't a measurable function. It's got a whoosh, whoom, whoooooooooh!"
Movement.Zoe.FirstMoveEnemyAurelionSol01: "Aww, I can hear my favorite wittle space doggy."
Movement.Zoe.FirstMoveEnemyAurelionSol02: "I think we're gonna get to play with the cosmic space dragon. He's funny, but he needs better manners."
Movement.Zoe.FirstMoveEnemyAurelionSol03: "Space dragons are so arrogant until you train them. We're gonna train this one."
Movement.Zoe.FirstMoveEnemyEzreal02: "HEY, I'M ZOE! YOU'RE EZREAL! I KNOW THAT! I mean- uh, I found it out! I mean... ugh... kill me now."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown143: "Things totally change so they can be the same but also totally different!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown135: "Starlight is an expression of something inside bursting to get out!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown137: "Trickster never loses. Because Zoe changes the rules."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown123: "Well, this is a pretty chill reality."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown145: "Dusk and dawn are the same. So there's actually two of me. Orrr I could be totally lying."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown136: "I should figure out a new game. One that mortals can play without dying!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown117: "The wheel turns, day becomes night... time to make colors!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown127: "I wanna have fun and chat with someone besides myself! I am a good listener though."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown144: "I like all these things around me! The creatures. And... and the plants!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown139: "Are we done in this reality yet? Hello? Hellooo?"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown091: "Nobody has to grow up if they don't want to. Orrrrr maybe they do. I don't, though."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown094: "I speak of the changes coming. That is our purpose. ...It's a pretty easy job."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown095: "Dusk and dawn; the ending is the beginning."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown103: "I'm not boy-crazy! I just... don't have a boyfriend yet."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown113: "I didn't even know boys existed! Now I just want one to hold my hand and look in my eyes! ...A cute one."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown114: "Daylight is too bright, the night is too dark, I want more colors!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown115: "I should come here every millennium! I like it!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown116: "Ugh, Targon has rules, but blehh, I'm gonna hang out anyway."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown118: "If this wasn't so pretty, I wouldn't care that it's all about to change."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown119: "While I wait, I will stay happy!" Zoe laughs and snorts. "Oh..."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown121: "Time is a tide. All that it gives, it also takes."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown122: "I'm gonna dance in my superpants. Cause otherwise I would be naked!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown124: "Do not look into the eyes of a god, or fly into its ears."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown125: "I am supposed to give them a message! But I forgot the sonic pattern for it..."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown126: "I hope this world survives... I like it!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown128: "The eye that looks ahead for the safe course is closed forever."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown129: "There is mischief in the stars. Also gas clouds. They smell like farts."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown131: "I wanna wanna, go to some place, place place."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown134: "Something good is going to happen. With sparkles!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown141: "No one free is afraid of... mischief."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown142: "What's fun around here? (gasp) What about over there!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown146: "You know, I wouldn't trust me, but I would totally like me. (inhales) I do like me."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown147: "Every day, every season... ends. And begin something new!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown022: "I like this virtual reality, especially its lack of network security!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown023: "Every apparent vector is actually parallax! Here it's just waaay more so."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown024: "This virtual reality is so lifelike! I wonder if anyone's in chat. Hello? Hellooo?"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown025: "Alt reality online. Time to berf the gerf."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown026: "I thought my VR rig wasn't working, but this is pretty swank!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown027: "Ooh! These VR auto-render foliages are amaze-o!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown028: "I can't believe this whole thing is procedurally generated!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown030: "I'm called Zoe, but it's just my smurf handle."
Movement.Zoe.Unknown031: "Did I remember to run script? Oh dang!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown033: "Math is beautiful. All around us is beautiful math we can remake the world with!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown034: "I'm gonna hack the government later. But first, jump-roping!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown035: "Every system has a weakness. We're going to find it!"
Movement.Zoe.Unknown037: "Man, they totally should've put this place in hybrid encryption, but they didn't!"

Taunt.Zoe.Unknown199: "There is another reality inside all of us. Maybe not you though."
Taunt.Zoe.Unknown200: "You might emerge somewhere else in the sky, somewhen else in time. That would be better."
Taunt.Zoe.Unknown202: "Is this the best physical representation you can manifest? It completely lacks zazz!"
Taunt.Zoe.TauntEzreal01: "If you won't pay attention to me, I'll blow up your world! Probably not... but I might!"
Taunt.Zoe.TauntEzreal02: "I have a question I wanna ask, buuuuut I need you to say yes before I ask it."
Taunt.Zoe.TauntEzreal03: "I'm just saying, if you wanted to hold hands, that would be okay."
Taunt.Zoe.TauntEzreal04: "Are you from here? I walk between worlds. Well, hop, actually. You're cuuuute..."
Taunt.Zoe.TauntResponse02: "Thanks for asking! I like butterflies, unicorns, and watching the end of finite realities!"
Taunt.Zoe.TauntResponse04: "Oh. Wow. That's like, totally off the mandala."

Attack.Zoe.Unknown079: "I've got a magic present for you! Here it comes!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown045: "So this the type of game you like?"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown046: "Delightful little world you have... I like it!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown052: "I don't mean to hurt you. I just do sometimes!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown053: "Your lives are short, but I love sparkles..."
Attack.Zoe.Unknown055: "This is the precipice of a new reality!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown057: "I can't help myself in doing mean things, sorry!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown058: "You're so funny, acting like magic hurts!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown062: "Ha! Let's get vloopy! ...That's a word, right?"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown076: "Do something fun! The world might be ending... Or not!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown077: "Oh, do you wanna do something, we should do something!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown078: "Tag, you're it! Hey, I said you're it!"
Attack.Zoe.Unknown082: "I don't want to grow up. You can't make me."
Attack.Zoe.Unknown084: "This is the game you wanna play?"
Attack.Zoe.AttackAurelionSol04: "Um, I'm a space dragon! And I'm the center of the universe!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackEzreal02: "I'm not saying Lux isn't a good girlfriend buuuttt... you could do better!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackEzreal03: "Do I like you or chocolate mooncake more?! So hard to decide!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackEzreal07: "I did not say I wanna kiss you... yet.."
Attack.Zoe.AttackEzreal08: "You just haven't realized how cool I am yet!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackLux02: "You are my rival! Prepare to be destroyed!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackLux03: "Do you even know he likes you!?"
Attack.Zoe.AttackLux05: "I'm not attacking you! I'm expressing my displeasure!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale02: "I'm girly too. I'm a girl, aren't I?"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale03: "Oh! So pretty! I want you to be my friend! Pleeeaaaasee!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale05: "We are going to be best friends!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale06: "Let's like, do something together.. Oh! Do you like mooncake?!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale07: "You need more stardust, I could give you some!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale10: "Can I tell you a secret? I like you!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale12: "Like you, I will try my best! Also, chocolate mooncake!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale14: "I like your hair and clothes, so pretty!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale18: "Why won't you hang out with me?!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackHumanFemale19: "Do you have a boyfriend? Tell me! I must know!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackYordle01: "Are you made of rainbows? So cute!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackYordle05: "You're ugly, but in a cute way."
Attack.Zoe.AttackYordle06: "Oh you're precious. I could eat you up!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackYordle07: "What a wittle wovewy thing you are!"
Attack.Zoe.AttackYordle10: "I just want to hug you til you explode!"

Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEnemy01: "Sorry! Beauty always has tears. Even when we're happy."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEnemy02: "Bye bye! But isn't it better with sparkles and more colors?"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEnemy07: "We all grow up! Well, you died, but... y'know."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillAurelionSol01: "Cosmic space dragon? Kinda chatty. So arrogant."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillAurelionSol02: "I liked your stars, but you're not the big deal you thought you were."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillAurelionSol03: "Aww, space dragon should have gotten back on his leash."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillAurelionSol04: "I'm gonna miss that cosmic dragon... Oh look, butterflies!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillAurelionSol05: "Said he made all the stars, and the humans believed him?!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEzreal01: "What? No! Why isn't he moving anymore?"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEzreal02: "Oh no, I think I played too rough!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEzreal03: "But now how is he gonna be my first kiss? He's dead!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillEzreal04: "He was so cute. I mean, uh, not that I noticed. Hehe."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillLux01: "Oh, I'm Lux. I'm so tall, and all the boys liiiike meeee." How do you like THEM, sparkles?!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillLux02: "Oops, I might have gotten a little jealous. Sorry, Lux."
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillLux03: "I do not like yellow hair. And Demacia. And light magic. And everything about her!"
Kills and Objectives.Zoe.KillLux04: "You probably didn't deserve that, Lux. Sorry, but not really."

Champion Select.Kai%27Sa_Select: "Are you the hunter... or the prey?"
Champion Select.Kai%27Sa_Ban: "You wouldn't last a day in the void."

Movement.Kai%27Sa_0536: "Here is where we make our stand. Do as I say, it's the only way if we want to live."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0042: "This suit lives on me, it calls me home. We survive together."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0118: "You know that feeling when your skin crawls? Like a thousand needles poking through every pore? Blood pounding through every vein? That's just an itch compared to what lives on me."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0062: "The first time I returned from the void, it was to save me. Now it's to save them."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0079: "When memories fade and darkness surrounds you, find the strength inside."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0101: "My appearance may frighten you, but make no mistake: I am on your side, and we fight to the bitter end."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0185: "Come with me if you wanna live."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0434: "Huh, memories of my father come at the strangest moments."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0329: "These creatures seek the living, even here."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0002: "I came for the hunt, but I'll stay for the fruit."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0003: "I like it here, I just might stay."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0008: "This skin lives on me, and hunts with me."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0010: "Feed the beast, or be its meal."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0021: "Forgiveness is hard, but so very worth it."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0084: "This place is beautiful, I'm going to save it."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0089: "This skin is fashioned for survival, and honed by instinct."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0094: "It's a good day for a hunt."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0109: "I came back for the others who could not."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0116: "Hold our ground, attack them in theirs."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0177: "Survival means never stopping, the void knows that too."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0180: "This suit hunts in the manner I choose."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0200: "It's fight or flight, only now I do not run."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0465: "This world is changing... we decide into what."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0179: "Danger is real, fear is an illusion."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0036: "Imagine a place where it's always night and you're holding faith for a dawn that never comes. I don't have to imagine. I've been there."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0102: "The skin grows restless, it needs to feed. If it doesn't could I be next?"
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0154: "Anger is useless to me, a wound that will only continue to fester."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0134: "I am the antidote, for the rivers of poison flowing beneath us all."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0048: "I survived the Void, but here is where my story has its best ending."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0052: "The Void will not consume me, but I must act or the others will not be as lucky."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0114: "When I was a child I was frightened of what lurked in the dark. How silly I was. Now I call it home."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0119: "Tell yourself you will live. Believe it, Kai'Sa, and you will have a chance."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0122: "Love... Fear... Whatever it's called, it's survival that motivates everyone."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0158: "I can rid them of these monsters, but who will save them from themselves?"
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0171: "Let go of the anger. It does not serve."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0239: "This place is too beautiful to be decimated by the Void."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0279: "Only a child, and no one came to save me."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0061: "Ahh, a cold breeze. I remember these. Reminds me of home."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0063: "Maybe someday they will come to accept me, for now they will need me."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0139: "The Void consumes everything, leaving only emptiness in its wake."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0066: "My skin is crawling... the needles, the itch... time to hunt."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0295: "This skin taught me how to survive. I will show it how to live."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0319: "Look closely, and your prey will show you how to kill it."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0355: "The monsters are coming. We'll be ready. I'll make sure of it."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0372: "Survival is an instinct we all have."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0160: "The hunt is binary, kill or be killed."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0007: "The hunting ground has changed, but the hunt is the same."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0009: "Like magnets, we are drawn to each other to do battle."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0088: "So this is what was before technology won, m'okay."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0043: "This second skin gave me a second life. I will not take it for granted."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0123: "Oh, how I like a fair fight."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0035: "You realize we should be on the same side?"
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0055: "I survived the Void. I refuse to let death in. I refuse to accept it as my fate."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0068: "They need to listen to me. Then they would see that I can show them a better way."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0049: "My carbon fiber exoskeleton is invulnerable to micro-meteorites, reentry, and the vacuum of space. It has but one flaw: it can be a tad itchy."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0053: "Human or machine? Make up your mind."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0058: "Some recoil at the sight of me. Underneath the shell would they see I'm just like them."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0133: "My suit AI will continue to learn with every kill, but it still could use a little extra battery life."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0080: "Fight hard. You are a living weapon."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0175: "Life and death are separated by the smallest stumble."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0207: "They have found me here. Let's settle this."
Movement.Kai%27Sa_0205: "I've seen things you people wouldn't believe, attack ships on fire on the shoulders of Or... Are those peaches?"

Attack.Kai%27Sa_0208: "This is my purpose, learn from me."
Attack.Kai%27Sa_0334: "A lamp's not gonna do it, Jax."

Ability Casting.Kai%27Sa_0592: "They can run, but they can't hide."

Kills and Objectives.Kai%27Sa_0284: "I forgive you, Malzahar, but I do not forget."
Kills and Objectives.Kai%27Sa_0337: "You're now dead prophet, that is the truth that will be told."
Kills and Objectives.Kai%27Sa_0685: "Goodbye Malzahar, now I will tell this tale."
Kills and Objectives.Kai%27Sa_0707: "Will they now see? I can do this."

Other Gameplay.Kai%27Sa_0243: "Sometimes you have to stop and taste the fruit."
Other Gameplay.Kai%27Sa_0622: "Sometimes you have to stop and taste the... Honeyfruit?"
Other Gameplay.Kai%27Sa_0703: "Don't worry, I will fight alone ‒ I've done it before."
Other Gameplay.Kai%27Sa_0354: "I'll stand our ground while you're away."

Recall.Kai%27Sa_0647: "That's enough for the moment, the hunt will resume."

Death.Kai%27Sa_0518: "In the void I had no one. I was a doomed outsider. Here, people are everywhere, and they are all mine."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0517: "Some call me 'Monster', they have no idea what lurks just below us all."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0324: "The void-spawn offer a thousand ways to die, and one way to live: Become like them."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0333: "The things we carry should lift us up, not weigh us down. Memories, love, and hope are the lightest necessities."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0224: "The yoke of fear is a heavy burden. Hunters must be nimble, and walk lightly."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0357: "I grew up deep inside a vast emptiness, I do not wish to grow old in one. That is why we must fight."
Death.Kai%27Sa_0141: "Down there I was surrounded by nothingness, but I was never alone. Memories comfort like the closest companion."

Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveFirst_0: "Remember. You've dreamed of performing live. You've got this!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveFirst_3: "First test run of this stage. Hope it all goes well!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveFirst_1: "The music here sounds so... magical! I'm sure I'll get lots of inspiration."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveFirst_2: "Whoa, is this a huge open forest? I wonder how my voice will sound!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_RisingStar_MoveFirst: "This is more than a solo debut. It's one step closer to my dream come true."
"Look out, world! I'm here to show you what I can do!"
"C'mon! We gotta give the performance of a lifetime."
"I made some touchups to my stage. Let's give it a whirl!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_MoveFirst_: "Remember Ahri's advice. Stars shine with their own light. I've got this!"
"I've practiced this choreography a million times. I can't disappoint Kai'Sa. I won't!"
"Evelynn will kill me if I screw this up. So let's sparkle and win!"
"Gonna earn my custom mic just like Akali."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_17: "Everything has beauty. You just need to know where to listen."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_13: "People haven't always been there for me. But music has."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_7: "Delightful emotions all around me. Each one, a note!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_5: "I like my songs salty and sweet."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_23: "Too bad I couldn't bring my cat Bao. He would love dancing in the grass."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_19: "Can't stand still when the beat's kicking!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_10: "Ah, sunlight! Don't get much of that in the studio."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_18: "What a magical place. I'm bound to find inspiration."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_21: "I never walk alone. Hearts beat with me."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_9: "My fans are the reason I sing."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_0: "I once saw dancers jumping and popping at the same time. So cool!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_1: "It's not stage control. It's stage presence."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_12: "Life's not about surviving in the storm. It's about dancing in the rain!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_22: "Singing in over twenty languages. Scary and exciting."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_14: "When the Lunar New Year comes around, I'm inviting everyone to perform."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_16: "Words make me think. Songs make me feel."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_4: "Don't compare yourself to other artists. Connect!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_20: "Someday, I wanna fly in the water... like a little manta."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_Move_11: "After every show, I go where music meets the ocean."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_RisingStar_Move_9: "Take it one song at a time."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_Move_3: "I felt the rush. And now I wear the crown!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_10: "Don't worry, starry eyes. Look up towards the sky, see yourself, and shine."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_7: "Little voices, never fear. Around the corner is your big premiere."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_0: "Toes in the sand by the setting sun. I saw you, wide eyes, soft hair, and my heart was done."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_1: "She's just a girl with a dream but nothing is as simple as it seems. A sketch on crumpled paper. Will she find her happy later?"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_6: "Every bad day makes a very good story. Every good story makes my songs less boring!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_8: "Reach higher. Take that heart off the shelf. You gotta love yourself before anybody else."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_12: "Rumors hurt more than sticks or stones. The words you say hit like bricks on bones. But like maya and the tides, still I rise."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_2: "Dark nights pass into early mornings. wake up and smile, surely adoring. The world is ready to welcome you."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_5: "Look into a mirror, see a miraculous view. There's no miracle here, without the miracle of you."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_13: "Dad always said no shoes in the house. I wonder if shoes on stage are okay?"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_9: "I love it when music sounds like rain. Is that weird?"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_4: "There's a song in every corner. Just gotta listen!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_3: "So many cute critters! All singing a different tune!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_MoveLong_11: "After high school, I wasn't sure what to do. Music kept me going!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_RisingStar_MoveLong_: "Can't believe my social media blew up! I always rated it T for terrible."
"How does K/DA dance so well? Body rolls are the worst!"
"One time, I rehearsed after eating a stinky tofu. It, uh... didn't go well."
"Does anyone else set a timer for when they should go to bed? Just me?"
"I painted all my cover art. It's a hobby of mine!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_MoveLong_1: "I can't decide who to stan. K/DA are all queens to me."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_MoveLong_2: "The hardest part about performing with K/DA isn't the pressure. It's the dancing."
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_MoveLong_5: "Our music video took days to shoot, but it felt like years. Still, I wouldn't have changed a thing!"
Movement.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Superstar_MoveLong_4: "Wonder if that third guy from the left ever came here... oh, wait, I need to focus!"

First Encounter.Seraphine_KDAALLOUT_Indie_FirstEncounter: "Wow, Sona! Your sound is beautiful. Could you produce my next song?"

Movement.Zac_Original_Move_2: "I may bend, but I don't break."
Movement.Zac_Original_Move_4: "I could really use a snack right now."
Movement.Zac_Original_Move_6: "Fighting is in my blood... I mean... my goo."
Movement.Zac_Original_Move_8: "Mom always said I was big for my age."
Movement.Zac_Original_Move_10: "I'm not as squishy as I look."
Movement.Zac_Original_Move_12: "There's plenty of me to go around."

Taunt.Zac_Original_Taunt_0: "It's not how much you can lift. It's how good you look!"

Attack.Zac_Original_Attack_0: "Beat up, or beat down? I'm flexible."
Attack.Zac_Original_Attack_8: "These jerks don't know when to quit!"

Champion Select.Yasuo_Select: "Death is like the wind - always by my side."

Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_1: "I light the way to your darkness."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_5: "Some choose their path. Others are condemned to it."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_8: "There is no grey. Only light and dark."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_3: "Yesterday was a dream. Tomorrow is darkness."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_7: "Darkness is needed to see the Light for what it is."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_2: "Darkness above, despair beneath, around it, flame, within it, death."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMove_0: "And all that's best of dark and bright..."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_FirstMoveEnemyRivenSk: "The world waits for our blades to meet."
"From nothing, there will always come two."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_44: "Do not fear the darkness, fear the nothing after I am gone."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_7: "Harmony isn't the answer. It's the problem."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_36: "From the ashes rises a universe reborn."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_41: "Cling to harmony, and you are robbed of freedom."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_3: "True strength comes from being torn apart."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_29: "Harmony is a lie told to force obedience."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_27: "My fire does not fear the Light."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_20: "The Light does not save, it conquers."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_26: "I will burn this world to ash."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_17: "Order does not want allies, she seeks slaves."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_21: "The Light will fall. I will cut it down."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_2: "To be alive is to know suffering."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_31: "The Light cannot hold me. I will not be restrained."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_13: "I do not regret that which must be done."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_35: "Darkness is not condemnation. It is release."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_37: "Anger, hate, love. It is all chaos."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Move_43: "I hunger for discord. My thirst for battle is unquenchable."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_5: "You hide your true self behind a mask of perfection."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_6: "You are... dangerous, but I am... more."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_2: "Can your wings bear you above your denial?"
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_3: "Our conflict is the crucible of reality."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_0: "Only a coward clings to tranquil dreams."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_7: "We are not meant for perfection, angel."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_8: "You and I are from a time before memory."
Movement.Yasuo_Nightbringer_MoveRivenSkin16_8.1: "A memory is all you will be."

First Encounter.Yasuo_Original_FirstEncounterYone_0: "An unworthy blade meets a cursed mask."
First Encounter.Yasuo_Original_FirstEncounterYone_2: "Yone, I learned your lessons too late."

Taunt.Yasuo_Nightbringer_TauntRivenSkin16_2: "Follow your path and it will break you."
Taunt.Yasuo_Nightbringer_TauntRivenSkin16_0: "Without your wings, think what might have been."
Taunt.Yasuo_Nightbringer_TauntResponse_1: "No more words. Let the blade decide."
Taunt.Yasuo_Nightbringer_TauntResponse_0: "Coming from you, I'll take that as a compliment."
Taunt.Yasuo_Nightbringer_TauntResponseRivenSki: "What is order but a blade most dull?"

Joke.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Joke: "Join the darkness. We have sugared confections."
Joke.Yasuo_Nightbringer_JokeResponseAlly: "Levity is overrated for a brooding soul."

Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_18: "All rule is meant to be broken."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_11: "Your rules will be the first to break."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_28: "Have you really come to talk with me? Again?"
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_27: "My blade is no darker than your heart."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_44: "Another massacre in the name of peace."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_40: "We are not made to follow orders."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_38: "Seeking the Light is a selfish prayer."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Attack_25: "If you do not control me, I will end you."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_AttackRivenSkin16_6: "You are blinded by your own light."
Attack.Yasuo_Nightbringer_AttackRivenSkin16_1: "It's not wings you offer, but shackles."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_18: "My rage is as deadly as my blade."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_32: "Eternal night will cover this land forever."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_35: "There is beauty in a broken world."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_1: "Order is a shepherd calling the lambs to slaughter."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_0: "Let go, and freedom will find you."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_29: "You chose a side. It failed you."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_6: "I own my shadow, and now yours."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_21: "I will never bend to the Light."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_34: "The crucible of chaos melts even an iron will."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_17: "Fear is not real. Only an illusion of order."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Kill_13: "So do the dark in soul expire."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillDarkin_1: "The darkness within is stronger than the darkness without."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillInfernal_0: "The darkness within is stronger than the darkness without."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillShadowIsle_0: "The darkness within is stronger than the darkness without."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_1: "If you weren't made for destruction, why do you break so easily?"
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_7: "Better broken than too perfect to live."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_5: "Those who live in shadow cannot dream of light."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_8: "So writhes the mind, remorse hath riven."

Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_2: "Long, long shall I rue thee, too deeply to tell."
Kills and Objectives.Yasuo_Nightbringer_KillRivenSkin16_4: "In the end, light always succumbs to darkness."

Other Gameplay.Yasuo_Nightbringer_UseItem2003: "The only succour I require is solitude."

Other Gameplay.Yasuo_Nightbringer_UseItemWard_4: "Soon, I will plunge all into darkness."
Other Gameplay.Yasuo_Nightbringer_UseItemWard_0: "A vision of darkness is all I require."

Death.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Respawn_3: "What does not consume the fire, the fire will consume."
Death.Yasuo_Nightbringer_Respawn_0: "We only see what the Light wants us to see."
