Movement.VelKoz.move07: "There is much to learn about this world."
Movement.VelKoz.move10: "I miss the darkness of the Void."
Movement.VelKoz.move15: "Genders are more easily discerned by the pitch of their cries."
Movement.VelKoz.move16: "To date, none have survived preliminary testing."
Movement.VelKoz.move19: "Ah, the Void. I miss the darkness."

Taunt.VelKoz.taunt01: "It seems your chances of survival are... less than zero."
Taunt.VelKoz.taunt02: "Let's see... yes, infinity more samples required!"

Attack.VelKoz.attack11: "Creature appears to seek its maternal unit."
Attack.VelKoz.attack21: "Flailing appears to be a universal response."
Attack.VelKoz.attack22: "They possess a variety of internal aromas."

Movement.Taliyah.startSummonersRift02: "A bird's trust is not in the branch."
Movement.Taliyah.startSummonersRift04: "Every tapestry begins with a single stitch."
Movement.Taliyah.move04: "The great Weaver says every lesson is a gift."
Movement.Taliyah.move07: "The desert's beauty lies beneath the sand."
Movement.Taliyah.move09: "Keep your eyes on the horizon and your feet on the ground."
Movement.Taliyah.move10: "My journey is not yet at an end."
Movement.Taliyah.move11: "A tribe without tradition is a flock without a shepherd."
Movement.Taliyah.move12: "It is up to all of us to see beauty in the bare stone."
Movement.Taliyah.move13: "Distance means so little when family means so much."
Movement.Taliyah.move14: "The earth calls, and I must answer."
Movement.Taliyah.move15: "To conquer our fears, we must move forward."
Movement.Taliyah.move16: "So long as the desert blooms, there is hope."
Movement.Taliyah.move19: "True learning is just a stone's throw away."
Movement.Taliyah.move20: "Oh, look, a rock... and another... and another!"
Movement.Taliyah.move21: "I know all of this will lead me home someday."
Movement.Taliyah.move23: "This world is a tapestry of our own making."
Movement.Taliyah.move27: "I keep moving, but my feet are on solid ground."
Movement.Taliyah.move28: "If I stumble, I have the earth to catch me."
Movement.Taliyah.move29: "The world is my loom, and every stone my thread."
Movement.Taliyah.move30: "This world is frayed, and in need of mending."
Movement.Taliyah.move32: "I think I've learned what I need to here."
Movement.Taliyah.move33: "I must push myself harder next time."
Movement.Taliyah.move34: "The warmth of the desert calls me home."
Movement.Taliyah.moveIdle01: "Just when I start to appreciate the view, it is time to move on."

Taunt.Taliyah.taunt01: "Maybe I'm here to teach you something."
Taunt.Taliyah.taunt02: "You're never too old to learn something new."
Taunt.Taliyah.taunt03: "Go ahead, push me. We'll both find out what I'm made of."
Taunt.Taliyah.taunt04: "You're not a problem, you're a learning opportunity."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntIonian01: "The mountains of Ionia taught me much."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntJhin01: "You're no artist, just a hired gun!"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntJhin02: "Beauty is no excuse for so much suffering."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntYasuo03: "I've learned much since we last met."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntYasuo04: "Let me show you what I've learned."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian01: "The promises of Noxus are nothing but lies."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian02: "I will take no part in your war machine."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian03: "You are nothing but plunderers and poachers."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian04: "We will not trade the yoke of one empire for another."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian05: "The earth will rip itself apart before it falls to Noxus."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNoxian06: "Noxus promised learning, but delivered only bloodshed."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia01: "The sands have revealed your true form."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia03: "This is how the desert repays thieves."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntCassiopeia04: "Noxians... why did it have to be Noxians?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntChoGath01: "You are the scourge upon our world."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntKassadin02: "Tell us what we need to stand against those creatures."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntMalzahar01: "You have betrayed our people to chaos."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntMalzahar02: "The stone of Shurima will stand against those creatures."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntRekSai01: "You will stalk the sands no more."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntRekSai02: "You breed chaos like a rabid ralsiji!"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntVelKoz02: "Want to examine some stone up close?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntVelKoz03: "How's that for dirt in your eye?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAnnie01: "Playtime is going to get a little rocky."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAurelionSol01: "Even the smallest stone can shake the heavens."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAzir01: "Remember there is stone beneath your sand."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAzir04: "There is no empire without the people."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAzir05: "Close to the ground, the sparrow flies faster than the falcon."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAzir07: "Better to build on stone than sand."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntAzir09: "Shouldn't you be home polishing your Sun Disc?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntEkko01: "Did the earth move for you too? Did I just say that out loud?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntIllaoi01: "Don't worry. I don't stay in one place for long."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntKindred01: "Life and death are two ends of the same thread."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntMalphite03: "Even rock gives under the right pressure."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNasus01: "Our future is not yet off the loom."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNasus02: "Worry is a heavier burden than stone."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNasus03: "Do not give up before the journey is finished."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntNasus04: "Even the most barren desert blooms in time."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntRenekton02: "Stone sealed your tomb once. It will again."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntRenekton03: "I will mend what you have sundered."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntSivir01: "He may be your blood, but we are your people."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntSivir03: "Do not turn your back on what is right."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntSkarner01: "I feel your tribe sleeping below the earth."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntSkarner02: "Is it hard to be the protector of so many?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntSkarner03: "I know the power that lies beneath."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntTaric01: "Ooh, you're pretty. Guys can be pretty, right?"
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntWarwick01: "It is the shepherd's duty to drive the wolf away."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntWarwick02: "You are nothing but a sheep in wolf's clothes."
Taunt.Taliyah.tauntXerath01: "Yours is the ill wind that begat his wrath."

Joke.Taliyah.interactionJokeEnemy01: "Huh. I guess that's funny where you come from."

Attack.Taliyah.attack01: "Looks like you're stuck between me and a hard place."
Attack.Taliyah.attack02: "Our paths have woven together for a reason."
Attack.Taliyah.attack05: "I've given up too much to let you stop me."
Attack.Taliyah.attack06: "Mastery is a journey. Here's your first lesson."
Attack.Taliyah.attack07: "Okay, great, that is actually what I wanted to have happen. For once."
Attack.Taliyah.attack08: "My father always said I was a shepherd's nightmare."
Attack.Taliyah.attack09: "It will take more than you to break me."
Attack.Taliyah.attack20: "A rock in my hand is worth two in your face!"
Attack.Taliyah.attack24: "Either way, I'm going to learn something from this."
Attack.Taliyah.attack25: "Looks like you've got a thing or two to learn yourself."
Attack.Taliyah.attack29: "Every rock tells a story. This one might be painful."
Attack.Taliyah.attack36: "I am the stone beneath your feet."
Attack.Taliyah.attack38: "The best defense is a strong foundation."
Attack.Taliyah.attackRiver01: "I'm the rock the river cannot wash away!"
Attack.Taliyah.attackBaron02: "As before, we will stand against you."
Attack.Taliyah.attackDragon01: "Your fire is nothing compared to the desert heat."
Attack.Taliyah.attackDragon02: "I looked for your kind at the ends of the earth."

Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellQ1: "Problems should be broken up into little pieces."
Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellQ4: "If at first you don't succeed, throw another rock!"
Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellE1: "It's never good to run from your problems."
Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellR1: "Better to build from the ground up."
Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellR7: "You can run from a landslide, I prefer to ride it!"
Ability Casting.Taliyah.spellR10: "That may have gotten away from me."

Kills and Objectives.Taliyah.firstBloodEnemy01: "A stone can't be polished without a little friction."
Kills and Objectives.Taliyah.spreeKillingSpree01: "Great, now who am I going to learn from?"
Kills and Objectives.Taliyah.tower01: "That... was... amazing! Let us see if I can do it again!"
Kills and Objectives.Taliyah.tower02: "Some walls were meant to come down."

Shopping.Taliyah.shopClose01: "Choices. Those are my only true possessions."
Shopping.Taliyah.item08: "Learning is always faster with the right tools."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemAbyssalScepter01: "Time to fight magic with more magic."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemAncientCoin01: "This currency carries weight beyond the sands."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemBootsBasic01: "Every girl needs a good pair of boots."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemEyeOfTheOasis01: "A vision most welcome in the sands."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemHextechProtobelt01: "Rocks should really come with an instruction manual."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemMejaisSoulstealer01: "Time to go big or go home."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemMorellonomicon01: "Time to throw the book at them too."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemRabadonsDeathcap01: "Let's see what I can pull out of this hat."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemRylaisCrystalScepter01: "Diamonds really are a girl's best friend."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemVisionWard02: "This should make the pattern easier to follow."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemVisionWard03: "Time to see the pattern in the weave."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemVisionWard04: "A rock in the bush is worth five in the hand."
Shopping.Taliyah.itemVoidStaff01: "A little chaos should shake things up."

Other Gameplay.Taliyah.ward01: "Clear vision is best when there are many paths."
Other Gameplay.Taliyah.ward04: "Big dreams require a lot of vision."
Other Gameplay.Taliyah.ward05: "Girls with dreams become women with vision."
Other Gameplay.Taliyah.ward06: "You cannot be what you cannot envision."
Other Gameplay.Taliyah.interactionTimeMidGame01: "The midday toil is the most difficult."
Other Gameplay.Taliyah.interactionTimeLateGame01: "Evening is upon us. Let us finish this."

Champion Select.Camille_Select: "Precision is the difference between a butcher and a surgeon."
Champion Select.Camille_Ban: "I will wait for you to be better."

Movement.Camille.start02: "I remain human... for the most part."
Movement.Camille.startTwistedTreeline01: "An island of ruination... heh, how glamorous."
Movement.Camille.move01: "Technology and I have a... complicated relationship."
Movement.Camille.move03: "I'm what you would call a deniable asset."
Movement.Camille.move07: "The harsh memory of one's past does not soften with age."
Movement.Camille.move08: "Regret is what tempers the steel of our soul."
Movement.Camille.move09: "The right word cuts more deeply than a knife."
Movement.Camille.move11: "I don't play the game, I make the rules."
Movement.Camille.move12: "It's not lies that cut but the sharpness of the truth."
Movement.Camille.move14: "Violence is a means to an end."
Movement.Camille.move15: "Morality is a beautiful servant and a dangerous master."
Movement.Camille.move18: "We all have lines. I may have crossed mine."
Movement.Camille.move19: "Another step on the march of progress."
Movement.Camille.move20: "They pay me to find problems... and then dispose of them."
Movement.Camille.move21: "Everything has a place. Forgetting yours is dangerous."
Movement.Camille.move24: "Self-made women need to be more prevalent."
Movement.Camille.move25: "Privilege must be preserved at all costs."
Movement.Camille.move26: "It is not the weapon that defines you, but how you wield it."
Movement.Camille.move29: "Sometimes scars are the most refined attire one can wear."
Movement.Camille.move30: "Progress is served by technology, not controlled by it."
Movement.Camille.move31: "The world is not black or white, but a delicious shade of grey."
Movement.Camille.move33: "The task at hand is the only one that matters."
Movement.Camille.move39: "The luxury of mercy is one I cannot afford."
Movement.Camille.move02: "I bargained my soul for the progress of Piltover."
Movement.Camille.move06: "My skills eliminate the chaos of Piltover."
Movement.Camille.move36: "For the problems of Piltover, I am the solution."

Taunt.Camille.taunt01: "If you don't have the talent to fight, at least have the decency to die."
Taunt.Camille.tauntAlly01: "Extremes are easy, it's the balance that is difficult."
Taunt.Camille.interactionTauntEnemy02: "Find bravado where you can, while you can."
Taunt.Camille.tauntCaitlyn01: "Belts? Is dressing like a commoner fashionable now?"
Taunt.Camille.tauntCaitlyn02: "Don't go looking for something you don't want to find."
Taunt.Camille.tauntEkko01: "Hourglass kid? Was sundial brat already taken?"
Taunt.Camille.tauntEzreal01: "That little toy of yours won't help you when you're dead."
Taunt.Camille.tauntRyze01: "Shall I wait while you consult your precious runes?"
Taunt.Camille.tauntVi01: "Ever wonder how you became an orphan?"
Taunt.Camille.tauntVi02: "Mmmh... it's like looking into a crude, boorish mirror."

Joke.Camille.joke01: "A Noxian, a Zaunite and a Freljordian walk into my blade. The end."
Joke.Camille.joke02: "A joke? Hmm... What do you get when you cross me in a dark alley? Eviscerated."
Joke.Camille.interactionJokeEnemy01: "In your case, intelligence seems like an unhappy accident."
Joke.Camille.interactionJokeEnemy02: "I hope you still think that's funny when I slit your throat."
Joke.Camille.interactionJokeEnemy06: "Rudeness is a sure way to an ugly death."

Attack.Camille.attack07: "Don't engage, if you don't seek to win."
Attack.Camille.attack10: "Who are you to try and stop me?"
Attack.Camille.attack11: "I know what I am. Do you?"
Attack.Camille.attack13: "A weapon's virtue is proven in combat."
Attack.Camille.attack15: "Do nothing, if you wish to be nothing."
Attack.Camille.attack16: "Hmph. You may thank me when this is over."
Attack.Camille.attack19: "You do not want your name on my list."
Attack.Camille.attack21: "I will make you an irrelevant detail."
Attack.Camille.attack31: "Let me be clear: I will kill you."
Attack.Camille.attack34: "Mind your manners — or I'll mind them for you."
Attack.Camille.attack36: "You will be forgotten before you're dead."
Attack.Camille.attack38: "You are a means to an end."
Attack.Camille.attack42: "Either attack or run, your indecision is repulsive."
Attack.Camille.attackAurelionSol01: "The yoke of mankind looks good on you."
Attack.Camille.attackBlitzcrank01: "Oh my... can someone put a sheet over this hat rack?"
Attack.Camille.attackCaitlyn01: "The law protects when it is protected."
Attack.Camille.attackCaitlyn04: "I am not one of your blunt object enforcers."
Attack.Camille.attackEkko01: "Child, I've considered every outcome. Plan accordingly."
Attack.Camille.attackEkko02: "You are not thinking far enough ahead."
Attack.Camille.attackEzreal01: "Shush now! Leave the talking to the adults."
Attack.Camille.attackGangplank01: "It would have been better for you to stay dead."
Attack.Camille.attackHeimerdinger01: "Do you have a formula for being better?"
Attack.Camille.attackIllaoi01: "I suppose I must teach you a lesson."
Attack.Camille.attackJanna01: "I've seen bigger tempests in my teacup."
Attack.Camille.attackKled01: "You know... I don't even believe in you."
Attack.Camille.attackMaokai01: "Mediocrity is the root of all evil."
Attack.Camille.attackOrianna01: "Who let you out of your toy box?"
Attack.Camille.attackOrianna02: "Time to cut your strings, little puppet."
Attack.Camille.attackRiven01: "Run along, girl, and mind your elders."
Attack.Camille.attackSinged01: "How about a taste of your own medicine?"
Attack.Camille.attackVi01: "Watch it, girl. I am your future."
Attack.Camille.attackViktor01: "Tell me, Is it the third arm that makes you extra-glorious?"
Attack.Camille.attackViktor02: "Your revolution has ceased to be useful."
Attack.Camille.attackViktor03: "You have become an obstacle to progress. Time to remove you."
Attack.Camille.attackVolibear01: "You would look better as a rug in my foyer."
Attack.Camille.attackWarwick01: "I am the one who keeps the wolves at bay."
Attack.Camille.attackWarwick02: "We are all monsters. Now, you are just one on the outside."
Attack.Camille.attackWarwick03: "Didn't your master teach you to heel?"
Attack.Camille.attackYasuo01: "You are quick, but I am quicker."
Attack.Camille.attackYorick01: "Think ahead, or start digging your grave."
Attack.Camille.attackZac01: "I am a weapon. You're some sort of... pudding."
Attack.Camille.attackZilean01: "Oh look, it's the worst of times."

Ability Casting.Camille.spellI03: "You won't avoid the consequences of your actions."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellI05: "If life hasn't changed you, then you have failed."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellI09: "Tut-tut! A lady never dirties her hands."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellICounter06: "Are you fighting back? Ts-ch, how selfish!"
Ability Casting.Camille.spellQ11: "The trick is to be clever and quick."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellQ12: "The test of good manners is patience."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellQ14: "Patience isn't a virtue, it is the virtue."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellQ15: "Patience is what separates good hunters from dead ones."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellQ24: "Precision is the only standard that matters."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellW03: "There are two sides to every issue, my side and the wrong side."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellE03: "You will be where I want you to be."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellE06: "Second-guess yourself. You will still be wrong."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellE07: "Did you really think you could run?"
Ability Casting.Camille.spellR01: "For you, this will be over in a moment."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellR02: "You and I will end this. Now."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellR03: "You will stay where I want you to stay!"
Ability Casting.Camille.spellR05: "Always dance with the one who brought you."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellRLeave01: "Ask permission, if you want to leave."
Ability Casting.Camille.spellRLeave03: "You didn't really think I'd let you go that easily?"
Ability Casting.Camille.spellRLeave04: "You will leave when I allow it."

Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill01: "You could at least be civilised about dying."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill03: "Don't take it personally, you were simply outclassed."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill08: "Ugh, at least die with some dignity."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill09: "This is what a professional looks like."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill11: "Ugh, today just got terribly bad for you."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.kill13: "Bloodshed and the upper class have always gone hand in hand."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killCaitlyn01: "That antique of yours is quite poor at close range."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killDarius01: "Bravado is contrary to civility. Much like boys."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killEkko01: "Your affinity with time has only afforded you more mistakes."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killEkko02: "Pay attention, boy. Maybe next time you'll get it right."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killFiora01: "Looks like two blades are better than one."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killFiora02: "A nimble blade wins the fight, but the keen mind wins the war."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killGaren01: "My boy, no one cares about your silly little country."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killHeimerdinger01: "Is that the result you were looking for?"
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killIllaoi01: "I suppose dying is the ultimate lesson."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killIrelia01: "You should have relied on your weapons more."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killJayce01: "Funny thing about heroes; they all end up dead."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killOrianna01: "Better to be self-made than made to serve."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killRiven01: "And all the Noxian High Command couldn't put Riven together again."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killShen01: "Play in the shadows at your peril."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killTeemo01: "Bandle Scout rule number one: be better."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killTwistedFate01: "Living another day was not on the cards."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killVi01: "All the class and manners I expect from a Zaunite."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killVladimir01: "If blood fazed me, I wouldn't be very good at my job."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killYasuo01: "The story of your sword is over."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killYorick01: "It's a fine line between deadly and dead."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killZac01: "Ugh! I think I got some on me."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killZed01: "Was that deception or were you really that careless?"
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killDoubleHatter02: "You have made the same mistake twice."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.spreeKillingSpree01: "Were you going to stop me? I didn't think so."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.spreeKillingSpree02: "Anything worth doing is worth doing right."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.spreeKillingSpree03: "The satisfaction isn't in the killing, but in a job well done."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.spreeKillingSpree05: "They do not pay me to make mistakes."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.spreeKillingSpree06: "Remove the strong and watch the weak crumble."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.killQuadrakill01: "This is what problem solving looks like."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.towerOuter01: "Wait long enough and the cracks always show."
Kills and Objectives.Camille.towerInner01: "When the foundation's rotten, the walls give so easily."

Shopping.Camille.item02: "The right tool goes to the one with the heaviest purse."

Other Gameplay.Camille.useRanduinsOmen01: "Meekness was never a virtue of mine."
Other Gameplay.Camille.useDuskbladeOfDraktharr01: "You can run, but it won't help."

Recall.Camille.recall01: "Better to sip regret than swallow death."
Recall.Camille.recall05: "Character is revealed by when one retreats."

Champion Select..1: "Fixing the world, one scoundrel at a time!"

Movement..3: "So... this is what it's like to have friends."
Movement..4: "This cape is not up to Sentinel Code. But, neither is the grappling hook, nor the boomerang."
Movement..5: "Shadya would approve of this. I think. You could never tell with her."
Movement..6: "We are not helpless. We are the ones who shape our destinies. Now, let's go shoot these villains in the face."
Movement..7: "There is no such thing as fate. But there is such a thing as Akshan."
Movement..8: "The world won't save itself. You know."
Movement..9: "Sometimes fate just needs a little nudge."
Movement..12: "How well I know the silence of a lonely life."
Movement..13: "Some people just don't want to pay with their lives."
Movement..14: "I've got quite a few tricks up my cape."
Movement..16: "A villain will show you much when they don't know you are watching."
Movement..17: "He who takes a life bears its mark on his soul."
Movement..18: "Is it wrong to kill killers? Eh, I'll ponder that later."
Movement..19: "Death? I laugh at death! Ha! Listen to me laugh!"
Movement..20: "Huh, nice place. Lotta things to swing from."
Movement..23: "I hate shooting them in the back. I don't get to see their surprise."
Movement..24: "Who am I to decide who lives and dies? Huh. Just a guy."
Movement..25: "I do not break rules. I bend them. Ever so slightly."
Movement..26: "I live by my own code. Don't be an ass."
Movement..28: "People without grappling hooks, what are they thinking?"
Movement..29: "I once knew someone who followed the rules. She's dead."
Movement..30: "Talk is worthless. We are what we do."
Movement..32: "A scoundrel left alone will always be a scoundrel."
Movement..33: "Once they see me, it is too late for forgiveness."
Movement..34: "Ha ha! The thrill of going where you're not supposed to."
Movement..35: "Some people say I hold a grudge too long but... those people are dead."
Movement..36: "How does this boomerang return? Someday I'm going to learn its secrets."
Movement..37: "'Don't use the absolver', they said. 'No one must wield such a weapon'. Eh, I disagree."
Movement..38: "Not everything happens for a reason. Some things need to be sorted out."
Movement..39: "What else can I add to this gun? Maybe a shovel. No-a ladder!"
Movement..40: "It's important to stride into the wind so the cape flutters dramatically behind."
Movement..41: "Vengeance is not a healthy impulse. Here's to bad health!"
Movement..42: "I can feel them shaking in their armor. I love this part."
Movement..43: "Listen to them. 'Oh no, is Akshan coming to kill me?' Hahahahaha. I am!"
Movement..44: "Shadya would not approve of this act of vengeance but... she wouldn't approve of a lot of things."
Movement..45: "Here we go. Get in. Avenge fallen ally. Get out."
Movement..46: "You try to rest and some lowlife kills one of your pals. Such is life."
Movement..47: "The bad part about having friends? Always having to avenge them."
Movement..48: "A friend has gone silent. Let's wake them up shall we?"
Movement..49: "They take one of mine. I take one of theirs."
Movement..50: "I hear the dead crying out for vengeance. I am coming, friend!"
Movement..51: "Killing this person won't bring my friend back. Actually, it will! Let's go do that."

First Encounter..52: "Sorry, can't let you live. You understand."
First Encounter..53: "It's not too late to turn around you know."
First Encounter..54: "I've got something for you. It's... comeuppance."
First Encounter..55: "Well. You look very guilty of something."
First Encounter..56: "I don't know how you live with yourself, but you won't have to for long."
First Encounter..57: "I know what you're feeling. It's regret."
First Encounter..58: "Hey! Grappling hook buddies! No? Okay, suit yourself."
First Encounter..59: "I know you! You're that kid who stole the gauntlet."
First Encounter..60: "Well if it isn't sentinel serious. Look at all the rules I'm breaking."
First Encounter..61: "You're from Shurima? And have a boomerang? We should hang out!"
First Encounter..62: "Silly Viego, we can't bring back those we've lost. I mean, I can but... not you."
First Encounter..63: "Greetings, fellow sentinel! How strange that we are not friends today. Oh, well."
First Encounter..64: "You work with Viego, yes? Scoundrel by association!"

Taunt..65: "I taunt with my grappling hook. See how it taunts you? Taunt, taunt, taunt..."
Taunt..66: "That was very clever. I hope it was worth your life."

Joke..69: "That was very clever. I hope it was worth your life."

Ability Casting..95: "Sometimes, I even sneak up on myself."
Ability Casting..98: "To the shadows... where the scoundrels hide."
Ability Casting..99: "Ha ha! Their eyes cannot find me."
Ability Casting..112: "Yes, yes. You can thank me later."
Ability Casting..117: "Let's try not to do that again, hm?"
Ability Casting..118: "Dear friends. Please stop dying. - Love, Akshan."

Kills and Objectives..129: "You know you had the coming, right?"
Kills and Objectives..135: "Always hard taking a life, but I get over it."
Kills and Objectives..136: "Haha! They never except the grappling hook!"

Recall..137: "Now for my grand escape. Grappling hook!"
Recall..139: "Like the mysterious boomerang. I always return."
Recall..140: "Only one way out of this mess. Skyward!"
Recall..141: "I come and go at unpredictable times. That is Akshan's thing!"

Death..145: "So... back at square one again. Let us proceed to a better square."
Death..147: "No shame in starting over. So I tell myself, anyway."
Death..148: "Someone gave me comeuppance? Ha! Who do they think they are?"
Death..149: "Yes, yes. The guy who revives people died. I'm really going to hear about this one."
Death..150: "Shadya's frowning at me now. I should've paid more attention to her lessons."

Movement.Braum.start01: "Good times, good friends... what could be better?"
Movement.Braum.start02: "If they insist on a fight, I will oblige them."
Movement.Braum.start03: "Ah! We are about to begin the fighting!"
Movement.Braum.start04: "Now, what can we learn from fighting?"
Movement.Braum.start11: "They may have many, but you have me."
Movement.Braum.move01: "Sometimes icy heart just needs warm smile."
Movement.Braum.move07: "If you have problem, you come to me first."
Movement.Braum.move09: "The darker the night, the brighter the stars."

Taunt.Braum.taunt01: "If at first you do not succeed, please, tell me what it is like."
Taunt.Braum.taunt02: "Don't worry, Braum was trying little bit."
Taunt.Braum.tauntAlistar01: "You remind me of Agatha. Best cow back home."
Taunt.Braum.tauntAlistar02: "Alistar! I have cow you should meet."
Taunt.Braum.tauntAnnie01: "Mother gave me bear as child too, Annie."
Taunt.Braum.tauntGragas01: "After this, we share a drink! You like goat's milk?"
Taunt.Braum.tauntVi01: "Your hair... we do not see things like this in the Freljord."

Joke.Braum.joke01: "When life gives you curdled milk, be patient. You get very good cheese!"
Joke.Braum.joke02: "The goats are wise; eat everything, climb everything, and if something kicks you, kick it back!"
Joke.Braum.joke03: "Mother always said - float like iceberg, sting like thrown iceberg!"

Attack.Braum.attack01: "Why not enjoy some warm milk instead?"
Attack.Braum.attack05: "When going gets tough, you call Braum."
Attack.Braum.attack08: "You hit like baby ram! No horns yet!"
Attack.Braum.attack09: "Now I give more than harsh talking to!"
Attack.Braum.attack17: "Today we fight each other. Tomorrow, we may fight together."

Ability Casting.Braum.caitlyzreal01: "Good shot! You'll get them next time."

Shopping.Braum.coin01: "This has the smell of a faraway land. Perhaps I shall see it one day."
Shopping.Braum.frozenHeart01: "To friends, I am snowfall. To enemies, I am avalanche!"
Shopping.Braum.randuins02: "A shield for my shield? I like it!"
Shopping.Braum.sightstone01: "No sneaking up on Braum this time."
Shopping.Braum.sightstone02: "Sight is the key to victory. Also stone."

Other Gameplay.Braum.poro02: "Train hard, little poro, and one day you will be strong like... baby!"

Recall.Braum.return03: "Is very important to take time to rest."

Champion Select.Jhin_Select: "In carnage, I bloom, like a flower in the dawn."

Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstMove_2: "The curtain rises on a young and vibrant universe. An audience worthy of my talent."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_22: "All of you are my children, the children of silent gods."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_2: "Oh to create, to destroy, these alone mean nothing."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_20: "A single bullet to shatter the mirror of my own godhood."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_1: "There is beauty here, hidden beneath existence."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_11: "Why erase everything at once, when it can be savored."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_8: "The universe will end, but I will make it wondrous."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_3: "What is a God, without words to fear him?"
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_17: "I can see them all, these infinite astral workings."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_23: "I want to feel everything, and then nothing"
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_10: "I provide the gift of a dazzling...extinction"
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_13: "There is a certain elegance, in annihilation."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Move_7: "Space is not silent, it dances, and it... screams."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_2: "Oceans of formless time open before me and they whisper, Jhin, we are your true face."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_3: "The stars are my eyes, and one by one, I must blind them."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_4: "Mortals and their linear time, they appreciate my art, they have no choice."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_1: "What do I erase? Myself, in every performance"
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_0: "Destroying galaxies is a pedestrian interpretation, I paint upon the canvas of eternity."
Movement.Jhin_DarkCosmic_MoveLong_5: "What lies beneath my mask? The universe, as I, was meant to make it."

Taunt.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Taunt_1: "You are all dancing in the palm of my hand."
Taunt.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Taunt_0: "Just a snap of the wrist... and everything's gone."
Taunt.Jhin_DarkCosmic_TauntResponse: "Oh, don't worry, I'll make sure you see everything you wish to see."

Joke.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Joke_0: "Yes, no, I want you to know, stop resizing, why are these here, ugh."
Joke.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Joke_1: "Big, small, big, not that one, not that one."
Joke.Jhin_DarkCosmic_JokeResponse: "I suppose a nervous jab or 'FOUR' is apropos in these moments."

Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Attack_10: "My pattern will flow from your emptiness!"
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Attack_4: "How blessed it is to be chosen."
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Attack_31: "Do you wish to see my face?!"
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Attack_19: "I wouldn't miss this for the world."
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_AttackCosmic: "Sibling, you don't compare to me, and will not get in my way"
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_AttackThreshSkin05: "Thresh, I have suffered enough of your hackery."
Attack.Jhin_DarkCosmic_AttackKaynSkin02: "I could use some gold in this composition."

Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_PassiveAttackBuff_6: "We are alone now, the stars and I."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_PassiveAttackBuff_3: "I must erase everything, the audience demands it."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_PassiveAttackBuff_1: "You are not separate from all that is."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_PassiveAttackBuff_0: "This is but a fragment of infinity."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_PassiveAttackBuff_8: "Don't close your eyes, I want you to see."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_ETrap_1: "You fear erasure, but that's why I chose you."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_ETrap_5: "If only you could see what you'll become."
Ability Casting.Jhin_DarkCosmic_ETrap_6: "In an endless abyss, there is only you"

Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Kill_2: "You have gone, beauty is all that remains."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Kill_3: "Who are you now, what will you become."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Kill_0: "From your dust all things are possible."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillCosmic: "Cheap materials, very little artistic value, cosmic garbage all over my stage."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillAsheSkin11: "Do you like it? You're an art lover. I know you understand."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillRakanSkin01: "What could you become? A neutron star? A red giant? What does Rakan mean? Tell me."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillThreshSkin05: "You never understood the value of the work Thresh, and therein lies the real tragedy."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillVarusSkin06: "Varus, I've cut your layers away, and underneath revealed light."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillKayn: "Your pedestrian dreams of greatness are ended gentlemen."
Kills and Objectives.Jhin_DarkCosmic_KillSonaSkin09: "I liked your forebears, Sona. They're all dead but they had excellent taste."

Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3102: "I love to perform, but I hate crowds."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3006: "These were clearly designed by a caveman."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3508: "The essence of a thing is found only in its absence."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3136: "We all wear masks. Mine are just better-crafted."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3035_0: "I prefer my equipment to make a bang."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3151: "Not sure I needed another mask, but oh well."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3046: "Start the music. I will make them dance."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3094: "Rapid fire? Huh. Where's the drama in that?"
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3085: "The storm is in their hearts. I calm them."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3087_0: "It is by my will alone I set my mind in motion."
Shopping.Jhin_Original_BuyItem3087_1: "I do prefer my work to have a brisk tempo."

Recall.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Recall_1: "In darkness, I dream of a cold and silent world."
Recall.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Recall_2: "I am the black tongue, a God without his throne, my mouth opens, and the stars pour in"
Recall.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Recall_0: "The final fated moment before the curtain falls."

Death.Jhin_DarkCosmic_Respawn_2: "Even if the artist dies, his contributions persist in all things."

First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterAurelionSo: "Aurelion, it is endearing that your kind's work remains uncompromised by taste"
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterAsheSkin11: "I won't be revisiting my... previous work, Your Highness, but I do have something exquisite planned for you."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterRakanSkin0: "To work on such a small stage Rakan is, mmm, well, maybe it is fitting."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterXayahSkin0: "Every universe, every Xayah, a spark... destined only to fade."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterDarkStar: "You corruptants are all pale imitations of a true masterpiece: the absence of everything."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterKarmaSkin0: "Karma you were formed from a pacifist star system? *Jhin chuckles* ,How incredibly droll."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterThreshSkin: "You see yourself as some poetic genius, Thresh.  I know you for the hack you are!"
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterVarusSkin0: "Yes Varus, you contain multitudes, but it's quality over quantity. Quality over quantity."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterZedSkin13: "Killing galaxies Zed? How plainly derivative, allow me to make you part of something greater."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterOdyssey: "Fate holds an interest in the crew of the Morning Star, but fate ends where I begin."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterKaynSkin02: "Orphaned and alone Rhaast, a mere refraction of a refraction. Not you boy, you mean nothing."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterSonaSkin09: "That orb is tacky, Templar. I'd get rid of it."
First Encounters.Jhin_DarkCosmic_FirstEncounterShen: "Oh Shen, tsk tsk tsk, look at you. Broken composition, uninspired perspective, and a ghost sword."

Movement.Kindred.start04: "Tell me again, little Lamb, which things are mine to take?"
Movement.Kindred.move01: "Those who dread us grant us the most power."
Movement.Kindred.move02: "We are not dreams. We are the waking."
Movement.Kindred.move07: "Beauty fades. That is why it is beautiful."
Movement.Kindred.move08: "Wolf chases what does not willingly go."
Movement.Kindred.move09: "Tomorrow is a hope, never a promise."
Movement.Kindred.move14: "Bits of them stick in my claws!"
Movement.Kindred.move24: "The weft and weave of fate guides---"

Taunt.Kindred.taunt02: "Chasing is the best game in the world... and I always win!"
Taunt.Kindred.tauntEkko01: "We know your name child. Woven across countless almost-lives."
Taunt.Kindred.tauntUnknown01: "Rushing to meet us again, I see."
Taunt.Kindred.tauntRengar02: "Rengar is well-versed in the ways of the hunter."
Taunt.Kindred.tauntSion01: "Come, Sion, let us end this mockery."

Joke.Kindred.joke03: "Words, words, la la la, pew twang pew!"
Joke.Kindred.joke04: "I'm hungry, I'm hungry, I'm bored, chase chase chase!"
Joke.Kindred.joke05: "The weft and weave of fate guides... um... uh... how did that poem go again?"

Attack.Kindred.attack08: "How one dies shows how one lived."

Ability Casting.Kindred.mark01: "The masks of the Kindred seek you!"
Ability Casting.Kindred.mark20: "Their path is destined to cross ours."
Ability Casting.Kindred.mark15: "I hope this one has strong legs!"
Ability Casting.Kindred.mark16: "I will chase it until it's dead!"
Ability Casting.Kindred.markKill05: "Such befalls all who bear our mark."
Ability Casting.Kindred.markKill09: "All your life has led to this moment."
Ability Casting.Kindred.markKill18: "The weft and weave of fate guides---"
Ability Casting.Kindred.markSteal05: "What folly it is to snatch our marks."

Shopping.Kindred.itemBotRK01: "Forged in a land unwelcome to us."
Shopping.Kindred.itemInfinityEdge02: "Sharp enough to slice the veil between life and death."
Shopping.Kindred.itemInfinityEdge03: "A sharper blade makes for a cleaner death."
Shopping.Kindred.itemBloodthirster03: "They shall not ignore us so easily."

Death.Kindred.unknown02.1: "There was once a pale man with dark hair who was very lonely."
Death.Kindred.unknown02.3: "All things must meet this man, so they shunned him."
Death.Kindred.unknown02.5: "He took an axe and split himself in two right down the middle."
Death.Kindred.unknown02.6: "So he would always have a friend?"
Death.Kindred.unknown02.7: "So he would always have a friend."
Death.Kindred.unknown03.1: "We will soon awaken from this pale slumber."
Death.Kindred.unknown04: "Is this what it feels like to end?"
Death.Kindred.unknown04.1: "I do not know, for this is not our end."
Death.Kindred.unknown05.1: "Older than those whose footsteps are long vanished."
Death.Kindred.unknown06: "Have they forgotten us yet, little Lamb?"
Death.Kindred.unknown06.1: "All still know us, though they try to forget. Soon we will remind them."
Death.Kindred.unknown07: "What do all stories have in common, dear Wolf?"

Champion Select.Jinx_Select: "Rules are made to be broken... like buildings! Or people!"
Champion Select.Jinx_Ban: "Aww, c'mon, what's the worst that could happen?"

Movement.JinxStarGuardian.start02: "To infinity and - uh, oops. Wrong catchphrase!"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.start03: "You're not dreaming - I'm a Star Guardian now."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.start06: "How do you like my extreme makeover?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move01: "Protecting the universe, one bullet at a time!"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move02: "Can you believe I was chosen for this?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move04: "Being noble takes all the fun out of fighting."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move05: "What do you think? Mercy, or mayhem?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move06: "What, your guns don't talk to you?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move07: "I'm fighting for peace, and justice and... er... eh, whatever."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move08: "Jury's still out on this whole Star Guardian thing."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move09: "This is not my idea of magical."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move10: "Hate to be ruthless but - oh, wait, no I don't!"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move11: "Sometimes you have to be cruel to be kind."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move12: "Glory to the First Star... whatever that means."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move13: "Star Guardian to the rescue! Am I doing it right?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move15: "We're on a mission! Just... don't remember what."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move16: "What's next? Is it shooting? I love shooting."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move17: "Who's up for a round of Hide and Go Shoot?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move18: "Yeah, I got this Star Guardian thing down."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move19: "Does First Star have to deal with this many sparkles?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move21: "Look at me! Pandemonium with a purpose."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move22: "Ugh... why do Star Guardians have to play 'nice'?"
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move23: "Glitter and guns - now that's a winning combo."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move24: "Shiro and Kuro are ready for action."
Movement.JinxStarGuardian.move25: "First Star says this is all part of the plan."

Taunt.JinxStarGuardian.taunt02: "Believe in yourself - not that it'll help."
Taunt.JinxStarGuardian.taunt04: "I've got a fistful of glitter with your name on it!"
Taunt.JinxStarGuardian.taunt06: "Not scared of my sparkles? You should be."

Champion Select.TahmKench_Select: "Call me kinnnnnnnng, call me demonnnnnnnnn - water forgets the names of the drowned."

Movement.TahmKench.start01: "I see nothing splendiferous in this table's offerings!"
Movement.TahmKench.start02: "It is my mouth into which all travels end."
Movement.TahmKench.start04: "It is the heart from which the darkest water flows."
Movement.TahmKench.move06: "I have tastes that aren't easily... pacified."
Movement.TahmKench.move08: "All the world's a river - and I'm its king."
Movement.TahmKench.move09: "All creation is born famished and starving."
Movement.TahmKench.move12: "I refuse to succumb to culinary degradation!"
Movement.TahmKench.move13: "We all gourmandize from time to time."
Movement.TahmKench.move14: "The only real sin is to deny a craving."
Movement.TahmKench.move17: "A depth of flavor is what I covet."

Taunt.TahmKench.taunt01: "You are a malodorous offense to my palate!"
Taunt.TahmKench.taunt02: "The baseness of your appetite repulses me!"
Taunt.TahmKench.taunt03: "Your mind is as clear as mud."
Taunt.TahmKench.taunt04: "Child, you're a couple cows short of a steak!"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAatrox02: "War is a manly appetite, and your directness has my admiration."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAatrox01: "Brother, you're as cultured as a crematorium selling barbecue."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAhri02: "I am enthralled by your class and refinement - I must offer you a token of my admirations."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAhri01: "You're as modest as a freshly-paid courtesan."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAkali01: "Hiding in smoke? Young lady, you're as sharp as a bag of slugs."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAlistar02: "Any pejorative of bullheadedness is pulverized by your magnificence."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAmumu02: "Coveting friendship is barely an appetite - but one I do so sympathize with."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAmumu01: "I say, you're as 'fun' as a leaky roof."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAnivia01: "I suppose I must defrost you first."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAshe02: "If you wanna' build an empire of peace, then your mortar will be blood."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAshe01: "Girl, you got as much 'foresight' as a blindfolded mole."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAzir01: "An emperor as humble as he is beloved."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAzir02: "Son, your empire was built on sand."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAzir03: "You're the emperor - of mashed potatoes and gravy."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntAzir04: "Your empire? I look upon your works and despair."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntBlitzcrank01: "If your heart is gold and your body is steel, why's tin between your ears?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntBraum03: "The heart of the Freljord must long for something."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntBraum01: "You're strong like bull, and smart like cow."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntCaitlyn02: "If you want to clean up the city, don't you need to understand where that dirt comes from?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntCaitlyn01: "You're as elegant as an outhouse in a leper colony!"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntChoGath01: "Personally I hunger for things less literal."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDarius02: "Your strength is waning, General. 'Course, I can help you slow time's regress."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDarius01: "You're as subtle as a gold codpiece."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDiana02: "Vengeance is a thirst I could help you quench."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDiana01: "Girl, you're crazier than a mouse in moonshine."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDraven02: "Your hunger for attention deserves to be sated."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDraven03: "I wonder - how can you receive the attention you deserve... while your brother is in the way?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDraven01: "At least the rumor of your vanity isn't overrated."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDrMundo02: "I can show Mundo new places to go - if he pleases."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntDrMundo01: "Your diction is as exemplary as your intellect."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntEkko02: "Time is but another river - and I care not what water I swim in."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntEkko01: "Your youthful rebellion is as tedious as your hairstyle."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntEzreal02: "Why should a hunger for adventure ever be sated?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntEzreal01: "Youthful ignorance is unfortunately your best quality."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntFiora02: "An appetite for a challenge is a craving without liability."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntFiora01: "A duel is a fight between two imbeciles... and you are the greatest."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntFizz01: "Wouldn't you care to travel to your people's destination?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGangplank02: "You're a man with troubles. I have solutions."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGangplank01: "Your attempt to be monstrous is as successful as your dictatorship."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGaren01: "You live by a code that'll never let you get what you want. Let me take you to her."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGnar02: "Time is just a river, boy, let me take you back where you belong."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGnar01: "Your conversation makes as much sense as a fish in lingerie!"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGragas02: "I admire a man of appetites - let me help you find refreshment."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntGragas01: "Your tastes are as elegant as a broken latrine."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJanna02: "There's a storm in your heart, girl. Tell me what you hunger for."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJanna01: "Girl, you're as appealing as a cake in the rain."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJarvan02: "Only a fool wouldn't hunger for the throne. Let me help you find that seat."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJarvan01: "Anything getting through that gold helmet of yours?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJax02: "It is wonderful to be hungry for a challenge."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJax01: "Boy, you are a few candles short of a lantern."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJayce02: "A drive for innovation? It's just a hunger for something new."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJinx02: "An appetite for chaos? Let me feed that mayhem."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntJinx01: "Girl, if brains were dynamite, you'd be a dud."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntKatarina01: "Don't starve your heart, child! Let me deliver you to him."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntLeeSin01: "Truth requires a journey on blind faith."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntLissandra02: "Could I offer you a bargain to replace your previous engagement?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntLissandra01: "Good ideas fall from you like pudding from a harpy."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntLucian02: "Step closer, and I'll carry you to your prize."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntLucian01: "A fool and his love are easily parted."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntMissFortune01: "The road to vengeance requires a journey I would happily provide."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntMissFortune02: "The enormity of the hat doesn't hide the vacancy beneath it!"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntNami02: "A journey to a moonstone is one I could provide."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntNasus02: "Forgiveness is a shore like any other."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntNasus01: "You're like a roofless mansion - impressively useless."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntRenekton01: "I appreciate your mind is unsullied by the complications of reason."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntRyze02: "You are a traveler... and I provide transport."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntRyze01: "You read words and mistake that for understanding."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntSejuani02: "Let me make a meal with your ambition."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntSejuani01: "You're as witty as you are subtle."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntSivir02: "Why not travel to when you were free from these doubts?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntSivir01: "Your tastes are about as sophisticated as your wardrobe."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntTeemo02: "Every heart has its own hunger. Tell me yours."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntTeemo01: "You're as likable as a rat in a bridle shop."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntTwistedFate02: "Bilgewater is a rough town to leave - I could make it easier for you."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntTwistedFate01: "A gambler's luck is only predictable... when he's a cheat."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntVi02: "Child, why would you sublimate a hunger? Have you forgotten who you are?"
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntVi01: "A boxer who thinks with her fists must inevitably punch with her face."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntWukong01: "Do you want to reach your potential? It's a journey I could provide."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntXerath02: "Ah, nothing whets my appetite like the flames of ambition gone awry."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntXerath01: "A slave's mind is never free, but I suspect you got yours on discount."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntYasuo02: "Your destiny isn't in the wind - it's on the river."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntYasuo01: "You're as quick as a turtle on molasses."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntZed02: "Child, a shadow must run from the light eventually."
Taunt.TahmKench.tauntZed01: "So, shiny attire seem like the thing to wear? You are the most intelligent ninja in the world."
Taunt.TahmKench.unknown01: "I presume you are the waiter at this establishment."
Taunt.TahmKench.unknown02: "Are you the waiter of this establishment?"

Attack.TahmKench.unknown05: "Beast, you are a rank dish! Ill served!"

Ability Casting.TahmKench.E1: "You have succeeded only in ruffling my attire!"
Ability Casting.TahmKench.E3: "Was that an attack, or an hors d'oeuvre?"

Shopping.TahmKench.itemFrozenHeart02: "There is something sublime about holding a heart in your hand."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemLocketoftheIronSolari01: "I can provide all manner of refuge."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemLocketoftheIronSolari02: "I am sanctuary for those in my favour."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemLocketoftheIronSolari03: "How did I leave my jacket pocket unadorned for so long?"
Shopping.TahmKench.itemMercurysTreads01: "I have a hunger for... fine shoes."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemMikaelsCrucible01: "I wonder who might like to bargain for a little freedom."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemRanduinsOmen02: "A little sedation for my more noisesome neighbours."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemRanduinsOmen03: "A handy tool for the next time I'm... in between meals."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemRavenousHydra02: "I pity the hydra. So many heads intent on sharing the meal."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemRavenousHydra03: "Truly this is the best way to enjoy a buffet."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemSpiritVisage01: "My visage was already flawless, now it just has more vigor."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemSpiritVisage02: "I refuse to trouble myself with charlatans."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemSunfireCape01: "A gentleman without a cape is only half-dressed."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemSunfireCape02: "Fire warms the spirit, and charges the appetite."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemWarmogsArmor01: "War is an appetite like any other."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemWarmogsArmor02: "A hearty appetite pairs best with a robust constitution."
Shopping.TahmKench.itemWarmogsArmor03: "Say what you will - a large man can not be ignored."

Other Gameplay.TahmKench.ward01: "I prefer to know when my next meal approaches."
Other Gameplay.TahmKench.ward02: "Even when you have no bait, you can still cast a line and hope."
Other Gameplay.TahmKench.ward03: "I search for bargains wherever fools cross my domain."
Other Gameplay.TahmKench.ward04: "A true meal requires foresight to manifest."

Recall.TahmKench.recall01: "Regrettably, I must retire in order to find a digestive."
Recall.TahmKench.recall02: "I shall return to this establishment shortly."

Movement.Viego_Original_MoveFirst_0: "She waits for me beyond the mist. My queen. My love. My black and broken heart."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveFirst_1: "No price is too great. No atrocity beyond my reach. For her, I will do anything."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveFirst_2: "Submission or death for all who live. In the end, it matters not. I will see her face again."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_0: "It hurts, my heart. It hurts so much."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_1: "I want precious little, yet I am forced to kill for it."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_2: "Soon, this long cruel night will end. But not yet."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_3: "My forces scour the world. Nothing will escape."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_5: "The curve of her lips, the softness of her smile."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_6: "She was the star that lit my path. Without her... darkness."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_7: "What is a wraith but the ravenous shadow of a man?"
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_8: "Stand against me. Call me villain. Die."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_9: "I feel her calling out 'Viego, save me!'"
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_10: "I will take, and take, until there is nothing left but her."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_11: "The Shadow Isles are just the beginning."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_12: "The mist is my great unending sadness."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_13: "Her eyes were portraits of a world without my cruelty."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_14: "What is lost is never lost to me."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_15: "This mist has but one cure... and I will find her."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_16: "And so it was that love was the gravest sin of all."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_17: "It is such a small and fragile thing, love."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_18: "There is no salvation from the dark, for the dark is me."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_20: "I am already a monster suited for the horrors I must inflict."
Movement.Viego_Original_Move_21: "The world denied my happiness. Now, all will die."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_0: "Isolde was my life. Viego died when she did and the ruined king was born."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_1: "The black mist flows from me like a tide. At times, it ebbs, but now we surge forward."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_2: "I remember her sinking beneath the waters... and then... and then..."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_3: "A world that would rob me of beauty is a world that deserves destruction."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_4: "Hate me if you must. Until she returns to my arms, all will be brought to ruin."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_5: "I will rip her from the jaws of death. Fate cannot stop me. Nothing can."
Movement.Viego_Original_MoveLong_6: "A crown lost long ago, reborn in unlife, ripped away from his only love."

First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterFiddlestick: "Ur-demon. When all life ends, you will return to your slumber."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterHecarim: "For all your ambition, Hecarim, this is what you are reduced to."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterIllaoi: "Your god could not stop me before, sea priestess. Do not challenge me again."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterKalista: "You will never have your vengeance, Kalista. Never."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterKarthus: "Sing, Karthus. Sing of all that must be lost and she who must be found."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterKindred: "Answer for your crimes, death. Answer me."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterMaokai: "Go on then, tree. Defeat me if you can. It will never restore the isles."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterSenna: "Why, Isolde? Why do you hide your face from me?"
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterThresh: "Your treachery does not surprise me, Thresh. Only that you believed you'd win."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterVladimir: "Hello, uncle. I'm surprised you haven't been torn apart by an angry mob."
First Encounter.Viego_Original_FirstEncounterYorick: "Ah, the monk from the waters. And... someone else. Isolde?"

Taunt.Viego_Original_Taunt_0: "You stand in the way of my love. A mistake."
Taunt.Viego_Original_Taunt_1: "Step aside, peasant. You are nothing compared to my queen."
Taunt.Viego_Original_TauntResponse: "I cannot hear you over the tremble in your voice."

Joke.Viego_Original_Joke_1: "Mist, get out of my lungs, I command you."
Joke.Viego_Original_JokeResponse: "Humor was better a thousand years ago."

Ability Casting.Viego_Original_MoveTransformed_2: "No power in this world can stop me!"
Ability Casting.Viego_Original_MoveTransformed_7: "This body, is this what you desire?!"

Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_0: "Your pain is nothing compared to mine."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_1: "The dead will not rest until I am whole once more."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_2: "Love is cruel. Yet, it will conquer."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_3: "I will find my love again. You matter so little."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_4: "The weight of this moment is so much more than you."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_Kill_5: "You are not the hero of this tale. You are not anything."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillHecarim: "In death as in life, Hecarim. You will fight only for me."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillKalista: "You never believed in my rule, Kalista, and now, this is your fate."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillKindred: "Arise, death, and greet the king who conquered you back!"
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillSenna: "Isolde... I could not see myself in your eyes."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillThresh: "You are simply the latest to defy me, jailer."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillVladimir: "So angry, uncle. It was one unanswered letter a thousand years ago."
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillYorick: "Isolde! I know it is you! Show yourself to me!"
Kills and Objectives.Viego_Original_KillPentakill: "All this carnage. Do you see?! I do it for you!"

Recall.Viego_Original_Recall_0: "She will reign again at my side, and I shall be ruined no more."
Recall.Viego_Original_Recall_1: "The mist will consume all. My victory is simply a matter of time."
Recall.Viego_Original_Recall_2: "I cast myself upon this broken throne awaiting her return."

Death.Viego_Original_Respawn_1: "No. She remains in this world. I can feel it."
Death.Viego_Original_Respawn_2: "In a world without love, death means nothing."

Champion Select.Senna_Select: "No one fights alone in the Mist."

Movement.Senna_HighNoon_MoveFirst_2: "The angels are gone and the devils are everywhere. I swear, I can't leave y'all alone for ten minutes."
Movement.Senna_HighNoon_MoveFirst_0: "I was dead. Now I'm not. Ain't that the way o' the west."
Movement.Senna_HighNoon_MoveFirst_1: "I have been plucked from limbo and delivered into this here gun fight. So, let's gun fight!"

First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounter_1: "Only thing bigger than this gun? The mistake you made standing in its sights."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounter_3: "If you've got a problem with me, make it two. One for each barrel."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounter_2: "Don't make this personal. I'm not nice."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterElise: "Eternal beauty, Elise? Now that's a curse."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterFiddlestick: "Another nightmare? Fine. I could use the target practice while I sleep."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterHecarim: "Horsey! What? I can like horses. I can like… things."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterKaisa: "Running shouldn't be part of your plan, Kai'Sa. Survive the fight, not the fear."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterLucian_1: "You saved me, Lucian. We saved each other."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterLucian_2: "Lucian has a way of breaking down my walls."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterLucian_3: "Only a man stubborn enough to fight me would be stubborn enough to love me."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterLux: "When we run to the light, shadows are cast behind us. You need to be ready, Lux."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterMaokai: "I know where the ruination began. It flows through us both."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterMorgana: "All this time, Morgana, and you still haven't learned to let go."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterSylas: "When I hear chains I reach for my gun… Wasn't wrong."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterThresh_1: "You don't own me, Thresh. I'm not afraid of you."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterThresh_2: "Lucian may think you're the enemy. But to me, Thresh? You're only in the way."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterThresh_4: "At the center of your lantern there's a soul, wretched and afraid. I think it's you."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterThresh_3: "You wanna get my soul? You go through the mist."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterVayne: "Vayne, you can aim for my heart when you find your own."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterYorick: "I know where the ruination began. It flows through us both."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterYuumi: "Cats deserve love even if they don't need it… and they use a book to hit you in the face."
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterDemacians: "When the mist came to my island, Demacia's gates were closed. Will they be open when you need help?"
First Encounter.Senna_Original_FirstEncounterShadowIsles: "Hi, it's me, the one you've been ruthlessly hunting her whole damn life."
"Have I suffered enough yet or do you need me to be a corpse?"
"I could free you, but those you've made suffer come first."
"I know the most ancient, holy ways to kick you in the darkness."

Champion Select.Lucian_Select_New: "Everybody dies. Some just need a little help."
Champion Select.Lucian_Ban_New: "You don't have the heart for this."

Game Start.LucianHighNoon132: "Well now, looks like we got ourselves a regular posse."
Game Start.LucianHighNoon052: "Howdy, friends. Let's show these folks what the west is made of."
Game Start.LucianHighNoon118: "There's a thin line between good and evil. You ready to cross it?"
Game Start.LucianHighNoon140: "Don't get too cozy, friend. We're only allies 'til we ain't"

Other Gameplay.Senna_Original_Q_Lucian_2: "I need you alive to kiss me."
Other Gameplay.LucianOriginal_WithSennaNear_Heal03_Chat: "Can see how that would be preferable."

Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_FirstMove_3: "What we have seen... what we have done... you are all part of it."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_FirstMove_0: "We will cure the galaxy of conflict. We will cure the galaxy of ignorance."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_FirstMove_1: "We once bowed before the Templars. Now, we are the truth they deny."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_FirstMoveAllyOdyssey: "Someone here likes Ora. Shall we demonstrate its power?"
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_FirstMoveEnemyOdyssey: "Our enemy came all this way to face us? And they say we try too hard."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_24: "We will show the universe its true potential."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_0: "Some consider us evil... How naive they must be."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_15: "Let us remind the universe what we are."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_17: "If they want ora... we will give it."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_22: "No more sacred orders. No more limitations."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_10: "Harmony blooms once the weak wither away."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_21: "Listen to the cosmos. Hear the truth."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_23: "Beyond the reaches of space we evolve."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_16: "We are the gift this galaxy needs."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Move_12: "We gaze upon the stars and see no limits."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_9: "The weak crave the illusion of balance. The worthy enforce true harmony."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_16: "Someone must destroy the weak. Let it be us."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_14: "So many try to hide their worst fears. And yet, we walk free."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_17: "The galaxy... a vast expanse infested by the weak."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_12: "How we long for something simpler. Harmony..."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_2: "Templars, Demaxians, The Syndicate, all blind fools."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_15: "There is only triumph and we will claim it all."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_0: "They see us as a living weapon. We are more than that. We are life transcended!"
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_13: "These creatures waste their ora. Let us pluck it out!"
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_8: "We grow ever stronger under the living stars."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_7: "Acquire forbidden power. Defy sacred doctrine. This is just the beginning."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_4: "The Demaxians conquer planets. We enlighten galaxies."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_3: "The Templars say our deeds are extreme. They are right."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_1: "Do not challenge us. We extend beyond your understanding."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_11: "Humanity achieves so little. Grant them ora and still they wallow in mediocrity."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_10: "Before us, there was nothing. Before nothing, there were monsters."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_5: "When life grows unchecked, cleansing blades are needed."
Movement.Zed_GalaxySlayer_LongMove_6: "They mistake evolution for corruption. That is why they will fall."

Taunt.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Taunt_1: "We offer you a choice: Die now, or die later."
Taunt.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Taunt_2: "You will love the way you die. We guarantee it."
Taunt.Zed_GalaxySlayer_TauntResponse: "We pray you fight better than you talk."

Joke.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Joke_1: "Cooking is like killing. It takes skill and ours is unmatched."
Joke.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Joke_2: "Have you come to dine with us? Oh, wait... of course. You are us."
Joke.Zed_GalaxySlayer_Joke_0: "Look at us! Are we not the perfect reflection of your juvenile fantasies?"

Attacking.Zed_Original_Attack_2: "I am the blade in the darkness."

First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterCosm: "This pain urges us to kill you though we do not know why."
"You intend to destroy us. A grave mistake."
First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterJinx: "Worthy spirit, Jinx. But it cannot save you... from us."
First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterKayn: "In another life, Kayn, you might have been a half-decent pupil."
First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterMalp: "Malphite, we heard you were hard to kill. Challenge accepted."
First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterSona: "Sona, we both know the Templars lie. Join us!"
First Encounter.Zed_GalaxySlayer_EnemyFirstEncounterYasu: "Captain Yasuo. This is your crew? Your brother would be so disappointed..."
