Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Kled.start03: "What was that? Oh, I should go for the decakill? Uh, if you say so."
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Kled.start04: "It's my property! All sixty gazillion acres of it!"
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=Kled.start06: "Guess we'll have to kill our way out!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_71: "This land was made for me - and me alone."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_46: "I hate to advocate violence and insanity, but it's worked for me."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_73_1: "Were you just talking, or was it the voices again?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_56: "I do not want my lands tamed. I want them unruly and free."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_18: "I'm from all over. It's next to nowhere and shut the hell up!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_0: "I play with guns. I work with an axe."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_22: "Mushrooms are healthy! Once you get used to the madness and paranoia."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_50: "A man without a weapon ain't worth listening to."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_63: "Yeah, I like it out here. Freedom, communing with nature, killing hikers."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_20_2: "I keep hallucinating that you can talk."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_28_1: "Skaarl! This ain't no time for philosophying!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_32: "Killing a few things might loosen this up."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_15_0: "No more of that! You're upsetting the invisible badgers!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_33: "My land begins where I walk. It ends where the sun don't shine!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_6: "Damn cowards, making me ride over to kill 'em."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_72_1: "Well, maybe I am looking to start a fight!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_37: "I do prefer to ride into battle."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_69_0: "Yeah, but... then how we gonna' invade both bases at once?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_27: "No, I'm positive, I ain't delusional! ...More than usual..."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_57_1: "Of course I'm paranoid! You tried to kill me yesterday!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_48: "I came to cut off a piece of that Noxian dream... and I ain't sharing my piece!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_68_1: "Nah, them we kill them too! Ain't nobody on my team but you."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_21_0: "Don't try and understand 'em, just rope, throw and brand 'em."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_14: "I grew up mean and now I'm older than murder."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_44: "Ain't nothing more beautiful than the Noxian plains... excepting a rich corpse."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_8: "All we need is open country, but we gonna' take everything they got!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_67: "I fight better when I've had my... medicine."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_43_1: "No! Planning and strategy? That's city-folk stuff!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_1: "Don't need a plan... long as I got this axe."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_9_1: "Yeah, they just confirming our suspicions, ain't they?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_41_0: "I don't have trouble communicating. Words is just treacherous bastards."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_5: "You ready, Skaarl? This day's gonna' require some mindblowing weirdness."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_51_0: "Hey, it's Forward Admiral Major Kled! I ain't been a Mister since ever!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_34: "Shh! Them brain weasels probably listening for us."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_47: "Let's get to killing them interloping intruders!"
Movement.Upload?wpDestFile=: "I am Kled! High Major Commodore of the First Legion Third Multiplication Double Admiral Artillery Vanguard Company! You will respect my authority!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_38: "Ain't nothing like having the wind on your back and blood on your face."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_45: "It's your birthday, Skaarl! Let's bake a murder cake!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_62_1: "Well, my foot wanted to meet your ass, and I'm about to give them a shotgun wedding!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_70_0: "Shh! It's time to get violent... and weird."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_12_0: "Oh, we find 'em, tie 'em up, then they's like a piñata full of meat."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_49_1: "Damnit Skaarl, d'you hide my mushroom juice again?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_53: "After we finish murdering these folks, what do you think? Tacos? Yeah, tacos."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_65: "First, we kill 'em, then we make 'em tell us where they came from."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_10: "There ain't no land that ain't mine. Just land I ain't got around to claiming."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_4: "Just 'cause they're our team don't mean we can trust 'em."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_11_1: "They're all trespassers, we're just killing them five first."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_19_2: "Yeah, yeah, invade Ionia you said, it'll be fine you said!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_16_1: "Yeah, reminds me of the siege of Ruug. Lot of men died on its high walls. It was fun."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_24: "At the gates of Qualthala, they tried using that boiling oil on us, but you can't deep-fry courage!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_13: "I am deep-fried courage, and an apple pie of angry!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_54_1: "Would you stop bitching for one minute?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_66_0: "Because I know someone is trying to sneak up on us!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_17: "Yeah, they think they so clever! Brains don't win fights, brains is what splatter on you!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_42_1: "Well, you the only thing I trust."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_64_0: "Well, just 'cause you're a hallucination and I don't speak lizard don't mean I can't understand you!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_40_0: "You do come up with the best ideas."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_31_0: "No, it's when I don't drink mushroom juice that I have a problem!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_2: "We was having a nice conversation, then they showed up... uninvited!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_55: "Noxus was created to train the faithful."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_52_1: "What are you whining about? I already fed you half a platoon!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_26_1: "Naw, it's just like the assault on Glorft. You seen one artillery vanguard in a commando fleet action, you seen 'em all."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_3: "Noxus ends where I say it ends."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_23: "Ain't much I love. Only this big sky, and this dumb lizard."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_35: "The sky is my roof, the open plains are my bed, and this lizard is the only company I need."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_7: "This big sky, this green land. Now how could I share this with anyone?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_74: "Woo, it's darn pretty round here. Glad it's mine."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_59: "You can't be lonely when the land is this beautiful."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_0_25_0: "Of course I want to pick a fight with 'em."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_18: "This world is rough. You gotta' be tough or die."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_2: "Yes, a sane man would run, but I ain't the running kind!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_30: "This is just a victory waiting to happen!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_5: "This desert sky's gonna' open up with a rain of heavenly bloodshed and glorious violence!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_0: "I am the brutal instrument of my own destiny!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_27: "Ain't nobody gonna' give you nothing. Gotta' take it yourself."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_29: "I didn't become a Rear Forward Brigadier Admiral from running!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_13: "I don't need that lizard! Kled's got his own ideas."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_10: "I don't need nothing but this axe... and this gun... and this hat."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_23: "Why's all these intruders so far away?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_15: "I know that lizard ain't talking, but I still hear him. Shut up, lizard. Shut up!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_4: "Hey, what was that? Of course I don't need Skaarl... but he helps."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_31: "What was that? Run straight into the tower?"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_12: "I don't need a team to start a teamfight!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_24: "Sure! I'll kill all of them myself!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_17: "I said I wasn't not backing off, no how!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_25: "Even if I lose, I win! Just means I get to come back and kill you later!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_3: "I know you're listening, brain weasels! I ain't falling for it!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_32: "I am Sir Admiral Major Kled, and I smell a victory potpourri!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_26: "First thing you learn as a Lieutenant Sergeant Commodore: rely only on yourself."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_7: "I didn't not earn the rank of Sergeant double Admiral by not running!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_16: "Oh, she'll see, she'll see! She'll come strolling back when I turn them interlopers into a purée."
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_8: "Ain't nobody tough as Kled! I've got gravel in my guts and a fire in my head!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_9: "I came here to... well, I don't know what I came here for, but I'm gonna' defend it!"
Movement.Kled_Original_Move_1_11: "Lord Colonel Major Centurion Kled don't run, no he don't!"

Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_6: "Don't worry, them voices ain't telling me to kill you no more...! Yeah, of course we still gonna' kill 'im."
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_7: "You do realise... you're on my property?"
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_4: "I figure I'll help you kill 'em... before I kill you."
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_0: "Usually I find conversation boring and useless. You remind me I'm right."
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_3: "You feel like arguing about something? It'll make what happens later easier for you."
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_5: "So... when exactly you planning on getting the hell outta' here?"
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_1: "Woo, no sir, I ain't gonna' kill you and feed you to my lizard! Them's just... malicious rumours!"
Taunt.Kled_Original_Taunt_2: "Oh, before I forget, what, uh... rank are you, exactly?"
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntNoxus_4: "You may be from Noxus, but you ain't Noxian."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntNoxus_0: "You know, I like you, brother. As much as I can like a lily-livered jungle-sniffer."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntNoxus_2: "You sure you're Noxian? You look a little Ionian to me."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntNoxus_1: "Watch your stepping! That's my land you're gallivanting on!"
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntAatrox_0: "Drinking from battle? What kind of dumb crap is that?"
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntAatrox_1: "Telling people you're a god? Hell, you're barely a paring knife."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntAatrox_2: "Something caught in your throat? 'cause you sound desperate!"
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntResponse_2: "Thems fighting words! See, Skaarl? That's why I don't like people."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntResponse_0: "Shut your mouth hole! Them badgers are listening."
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntResponse_4: "I'm just a Yordle standing in front of you, asking you to shut the hell up!"
Taunt.Kled_Original_TauntResponse_3: "Of course you realize, this means war."

Joke.Kled_Original_JokeResponse_1: "So, that's what considered funny in the city, huh?"
Joke.Kled_Original_JokeResponse_0: "I got a joke too! It's called me kicking your teeth in!"
Joke.Kled_Original_JokeResponse_4: "That it? That was your joke, huh?"
Joke.Kled_Original_JokeResponse_3: "Was you making fun of my Skaarl?"
Joke.Kled_Original_JokeResponse_2: "Real funny! Knew a funny guy in the Drekan Campaign - took a javelin in the spine, couldn't walk after that. Used him as a coat rack."

Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_16: "Slow down so I can kill something!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_20: "Step on my land again, you're done!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_12: "How about a long axe in your guts?"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_38: "You should run! Skaarl likes his food lively!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_28: "Don't interrupt me! I'm trying to start a fight!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_27: "I'm Kled, and this here's Skaarl. Prepare to die."
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_30: "This is how it's gonna work: I kill you, then I take your stuff."
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_14: "You see my welcome sign back there? No? It was your friend's skull!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_0: "You will salute when you address me!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_8: "Why ain't they saluting me? They should be saluting me! Salute me now!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_1: "You get my invitation to visit? No? 'cause there ain't one!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_23: "I got your welcoming present right here!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_6: "Only coffin's gonna' be this lizard's belly!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_2: "I might have to jump off this lizard and put my boot in your watoosie!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_35: "My brain is on fire, my soul is strong, and my lizard is hungry!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_29: "He looked at me funny! Get him."
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_31: "You looking at me? 'cause I'm gonna' kill you!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_11: "You just justified a preemptive retaliatory strike!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_32: "They came looking for a fight? Let's oblige 'em."
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_0_21: "I am justified, and I am armed!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_10: "I'll say something witty after I kill you!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_11: "I'm gonna' cut you open and use your spine for a back scratcher, because it is itchy! Very itchy!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_25: "I can only express myself through violence!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_32: "You thought I was done? Kled ain't never done!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_33: "You see, Skaarl? I'm doing it alone!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_22: "You're a cockroach, and it's half-past stomping time!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_15: "I'm gonna reach down your throat, and turn your lungs into mittens!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_19: "I'm gonna make you wish you were a hallucination!"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_6: "You think I don't hear you laughing?"
Attack.Kled_Original_Attack_1_26: "There's fixing to be two sounds: me hitting you, and---"

Ability Casting.Kled_Original_AnimalThreshold_0: "Dang nabbit, you're gonna' get us killed!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_AnimalThreshold_8: "Don't you run off on me! Skaarl!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_DisMount_21: "I ain't never forgiving you, you flea-bitten-!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_DisMount_7: "Go home, get! I never needed you no how!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_DisMount_13: "No, no! The other way! Get back here!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_DisMount_8: "I will--- I ain't backing down! I don't back down! Never!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_DisMount_20: "Where you going? We got 'em right where we want 'em!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_ReMount_15: "If you does that one more time I'll skewer you and roast you myself!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_ReMount_3: "Boy am I glad to see you!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_ReMount_7: "Yeehaw! I knew you couldn't quit me, Skaarl!"
Ability Casting.Kled_Original_Q_champ_hit_5: "Come back, I gotta' put an axe in your brain!"

Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_2: "This is Noxus, son! Winner takes all!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_6: "Thought you could take my land, huh? How'd that work out for you?"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_23: "Don't worry, Skaarl! We'll come back so you can eat 'em later."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_4: "Whoops! Looks like I accidentally stabbed you with my long axe - until you were dead!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_3: "You were a visitor, now you're mulch!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_10: "Skaarl, that was what we call a predictable scenario."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_9: "I told 'em what was gonna' happen if they came onto my land!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_1: "Next time you visit, bring more stuff I can take!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_12: "I might be a deranged lizard-riding bandito, but I whooped you real good!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_20: "Now, I might have overreacted to you unlawfully entering my property - but I don't think so!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_17: "Ahahahaha! I warned him! I did warn him!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_18: "It's funny, 'cause he died right on the border of my land, and more of my land!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_22: "Don't let the door hit you on your way to hell!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_13: "We didn't come here to teach lessons in humanity!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_19: "Nothing like a river of blood to send a message."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_Kill_7: "Y'know, a long time ago, being crazy meant something."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillYordle_2: "Just 'cause we was kin don't mean I ain't feeding you to Skaarl!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillYordle_0: "Hey cous', glad you came to visit!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillYordle_7: "Afraid I had to cut your visit short."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillYordle_5: "Aw, you are so cute... 'fore I ripped your fuzzy head off!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillYordle_3: "I could feel bad about killing you, or we could stomp on your corpse!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillAatrox_2: "He died as dumb as he sounded."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillAatrox_0: "And he ain't even had the indignity to call himself a demon."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillAatrox_1: "Never had much to say, but I'm sure glad we shut him up."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillCassiopeia_1_1: "I mean, before we killed her. Snake for legs? Crazy!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillCassiopeia_2: "Was that lady half-snake, or that snake half-human? She is... confusing. Dead, but confusing."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillDarius_0: "Hey, lizard food! What exactly was you general of?"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillDarius_3: "He wanted to unify Noxus. Guess that makes me a secessionist."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillIllaoi_2: "Skaarl? You eatin' good tonight! That girl's got some meat on her!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillIllaoi_1: "I gotta' stop the mushroom juice... I swear that girl had some tentacles or something!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillJhin_0: "Hey, fancy pants! Got your cloak dirty!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillJhin_1: "I don't know what he was. I just needed him to shut up."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillJhin_3: "I can respect crazy, but what kind of fool reloads in the middle of a fight?"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillKatarina_2: "A sinister blade? Heck, girl, Skaarl's got farts more sinister than you was."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillKatarina_3: "No, obviously she didn't have any! That's the darn point!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillLeBlanc_0_1: "She had one crazy getup! Them city-folk clothes is getting ridiculous."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillLeBlanc_1: "All your little city-girl dreams just got stomped."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillReksai_2: "Damn varmint left holes all over the yard."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillReksai_0: "Queen of what? Darn thing made Skaarl look smart!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillRiven_2: "Pure Noxian girl. Almost liked her. Almost."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillRiven_0: "Seems to have lost your bounce, girl."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillRiven_1: "All that hippy hop! Getting on my nerves!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSion_0_2: "How many times do I gotta' kill him?"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSion_3: "Too stupid to live, too dumb to die."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSion_1_2: "I don't think you can eat that one."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSion_2: "Huh. I liked him better when he was alive."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSwain_1: "Master Tactician? He can keep that title."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillSwain_2_1: "I figure he gonna' taste like chicken."

Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillTalon_2: "I've seem some dumb outfits, Skaarl, but a cape made out of knives? Woo, ha! That took the cake!"
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillTalon_1: "Another dead city boy, thinking he could sneaky-sneak on my land."
Kills and Objectives.Kled_Original_KillTalon_0: "Let that be a lesson for all them sneaky-sneaks!"

Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_1: "I keep my eyes open - all the time."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_0: "I ain't paranoid - I'm ready. Real ready."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_9: "They's always trying to sneak up on us. Trying, that is."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_7: "Them sneaky-sneaks ain't gonna' sneak on us, no sir!"
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_6: "It's mine, and I got my eye on it!"
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_8: "Yeah, any of them varmints sneak up on us, we'll know."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_2: "It ain't paranoia if everyone is out to get you."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_10: "There's no such thing as paranoia; your worst fears can come true at any moment."
Other Gameplay.Kled_Original_UseItem3340_11: "Paranoia is just another word for ignorance."

Shopping.Ekko.itemGuardianAngel02: "Yep. Put an angel on the job. I could use a break."
Shopping.Ekko.itemGuardianAngel03: "I'm sure I won't be needing this… but I'll take it anyhow."
Shopping.Ekko.itemGuardianAngel04: "A second chance? I thought I was on my fifth!"

Shopping.Ekko.itemLudensEcho01: "It's like it was made for me."
Shopping.Ekko.itemRabadonsDeathcap01: "Not much of a hat guy… but this thing is awesome!"

Champion Select.Qiyana_Ban: "You are right to fear my greatness."

Movement.Qiyana_161: "Congratulations, you have Qiyana. The other side, they have no Qiyana."
Movement.Qiyana_162: "I would say 'watch and learn,' but unfortunately you cannot learn this."
Movement.Qiyana_163: "Oh, good, servants. Carry my panoply to the battle, would you?"
Movement.Qiyana_165: "I don't mean to sound arrogant, but I'm extremely good, at everything."
Movement.Qiyana_159: "Is that all they brought to face us? My omele could defeat them, and she is 85."
Movement.Qiyana_160: "Cover the ground behind me. None may tread where I have stepped."
Movement.Qiyana_158: "I can tell by your expressions you've never met a superior being."
Movement.Qiyana_080: "My enemies try their best. That is what is so sad."
Movement.Qiyana_098: "It's not a ring blade, it's an ohmlatl! Idiots."
Movement.Qiyana_073: "No more hiding in the wilderness. I demand to be seen!"
Movement.Qiyana_058: "If they want to worship me... hmph, I will not stop them."
Movement.Qiyana_015: "Some wait their turn, and some take what they deserve."
Movement.Qiyana_062: "In Ixtal we call them cao-mul: soon to be mud."
Movement.Qiyana_002: "If talent were an element, perhaps I could throw some at them."
Movement.Qiyana_140: "I wish there was someone else as perfect as me."
Movement.Qiyana_151: "'Empress Qiyana...' I do like the sound of that."
Movement.Qiyana_012: "Line them up. I will bend their knees."
Movement.Qiyana_145: "I do not lack empathy. Other people just need to be better."
Movement.Qiyana_024: "My feet cannot step where lesser beings have tread."
Movement.Qiyana_030: "You know what's hard about being a princess? Nothing."
Movement.Qiyana_031: "I cannot wait to be empress. If only my entire family were not in the way."
Movement.Qiyana_077: "Hard work is for those who possess no talent."
Movement.Qiyana_129: "Those who find Ixtal do not live to speak of it."
Movement.Qiyana_081: "I will grant this place the privilege of being conquered by me."
Movement.Qiyana_069: "Ugh, this place could use some reshaping."
Movement.Qiyana_134: "I'm getting hot. Where is my royal fanner?!"
Movement.Qiyana_052: "My parents rule with fairness and compassion. So boring."
Movement.Qiyana_053: "There will always be someone who is better, and that person is me."
Movement.Qiyana_107: "Things do what I tell them to. Right, rocks?"
Movement.Qiyana_103: "The secrets of my enemies carry far on the wind."
Movement.Qiyana_105: "Of course I've mastered fire... I just don't like to show off."
Movement.Qiyana_150: "It is a travesty to not be carried by servants."
Movement.Qiyana_117: "Ee-shao-can! They will all learn to say it."
Movement.Qiyana_064: "Being young means living to see all your enemies die first."
Movement.Qiyana_097: "One throne, nine sisters. Nine tragic accidents waiting to happen."
Movement.Qiyana_094: "This place will be a lovely addition to my empire."
Movement.Qiyana_072: ""Let's see, what can someone do for me."
Movement.Qiyana_089: "I hate it when they dare look me in the eye."
Movement.Qiyana_036: "The perfect place to dispose of my enemies."
Movement.Qiyana_041: "If I command the rivers to flow backward, they shall."
Movement.Qiyana_128: "I know what they are thinking: "There goes Qiyana! She is so much better than all nine of her sisters; I can't believe she's not our queen."
Movement.Qiyana_122: "We should throw a feast for me, but we'll need something to celebrate. I know! Let us crush the enemy!"
Movement.Qiyana_135: "Someday, all this will be Ixaocan. A glorious empire, with an empress to fit."

First Encounter.Qiyana_006: "How proud you are of your abilities, like an ape who just found a stick."
First Encounter.Qiyana_111: "There are levels to this competition. Better stay on yours."
First Encounter.Qiyana_156: "I am the shaper of lands, and who are you? A nobody."
First Encounter.Qiyana_148: "Why are you in my space? I cannot be seen with the likes of you."
First Encounter.Qiyana_152: "The rocks don't like you, the plants don't like you, and I'm pretty sure I don't like you."
First Encounter.Qiyana_019: "You dare raise a hand against your rightful ruler? Estem qa'eve!"
First Encounter.Qiyana_095: "You Pilt-ovans are like flying squirrels pretending to soar like the eagles."
First Encounter.Qiyana_032: "Magic from machines? How cheap and distasteful."
First Encounter.Qiyana_059: "I have a message for you to spread to everyone in your... Pil-tover."
First Encounter.Qiyana_048: "We have the great city of Ixaocan. What does your Shurima have?  Sand and ghosts."
First Encounter.Qiyana_090: "I have great plans for Shurima, starting with you."
First Encounter.Qiyana_045: "Commanding just one element must be quite dull. Then again, it's so you!"
First Encounter.Qiyana_096: "You only know one element? How quaint."
First Encounter.Qiyana_120: "First time seeing real magic? I'll go slowly so you may follow along."
First Encounter.Qiyana_042: "Your magic is so primitive. Just like your sense of style."
First Encounter.Qiyana_121: "Impressive magic. Did you buy that at a discount?"
First Encounter.Qiyana_109: "Why yes, I believe I will throw another rock."
First Encounter.Qiyana_068: "The jungle obeys me, Zyra. In time, you will do the same."

Taunt.Qiyana_137: "I can see your weakness; it is just, well, all of you."
Taunt.Qiyana_075: "I have humiliated my own sisters. What do you think I'll do to you?"
Taunt.Qiyana_057: "I see you have mastered the element of wind."

Joke.Qiyana_084: "I claim-" Qiyana hiccups. "Claim this land for Ixao-" Qiyana hiccups again. "I will claim this land for Ixaocan!"

Attack.Qiyana_004: "Look around, so many ways to kill you."
Attack.Qiyana_008: "You're going to die looking like that?"

Ability Casting.Qiyana_005: "Oh rock, smash these idiots, won't you?"
Ability Casting.Qiyana_029: "Rock is so common. Just like them."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_039: "Let us throw rocks at them and laugh."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_037: "See? The land knows it is mine."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_102: "This will grow on the graves of my enemies."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_035: "They'll never see me coming. What a shame."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_060: "As green as the envy of my sisters."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_067: "Oh grass, please hide me from these imbeciles."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_142: "That chill in the air? It's me."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_023: "Drown them, freeze them, watch them sink."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_088: "The best thing about water? My reflection."
Ability Casting.Qiyana_119: "Wet, like the tears of my enemies."

Kills and Objectives.Qiyana_138: "If you bleed on me, I'll kill you again!"
Kills and Objectives.Qiyana_130: "Rejoice! You are now part of the legend of Qiyana!"
Kills and Objectives.Qiyana_055: "That's where you belong. In the dirt."
Kills and Objectives.Qiyana_113: "Not my fault. They should have bowed."
Kills and Objectives.Qiyana_112: "It is exhausting to crush you so much."

Recall.Qiyana_017: "Grass? Oh grass? Take me away from this tiresome battle. And can you also fan me?"
Recall.Qiyana_027: "Everyone, your future empress is leaving the fight. ...Okay, carry on."
Recall.Qiyana_065: "Excuse me! ...Uh, excuse me?! Ugh. When I return, this place better have a statue of me."
Recall.Qiyana_164: "Servants, my palanquin. Servants? Ugh, must I do everything myself?"

Death.Qiyana_054: "See? Even death is no match for Qiyana."
Death.Qiyana_110: "I suppose they will make me do this the hard way."
Death.Qiyana_028: "I say give them a win. They're so cute when they think they have a chance."
Death.Qiyana_086: "Did anyone see that?  Well, I'll just have to kill them."
Death.Qiyana_143: "That was no crushing; that was merely a squeeze."
Death.Qiyana_126: "Can't keep me in the ground. The ground obeys me."

Champion Select.Vi_Ban: "If I want your opinion, I'll beat it out of you."

Movement.Vi_Original_Move_0: "Here I come to save the day... or wreck it."
Movement.Vi_Original_Move_9: "If you hit a wall, hit it hard!"
Movement.Vi_Original_Move_2: "I let my hands do the talking."

Taunt.Vi_Original_Taunt_1: "I've got five reasons for you to shut up."
Taunt.Vi_Original_Taunt_2: "If I want your opinion, I'll beat it out of you."
Taunt.Vi_Original_Taunt_0: "I like you as far as I can throw you... not even."
Taunt.Vi_Original_TauntCaitlyn_1: "Care for a spot of tea? Or maybe a spot of punch in the face."
Taunt.Vi_Original_TauntCaitlyn_0: "Oh, look at me... I'm on the case."

Joke.Vi_Original_Joke_0: "We can either do this the hard way or... oh wait, no, there's just the hard way."
Joke.Vi_Original_Joke_1: "Hmm, I like your smile. Gives me something to aim at."
Joke.Vi_Original_Joke_2: "I like your smile. Makes a nice target."
Joke.Vi_Original_Joke_4: "Why can't I get a straight answer? It's always just 'Oh no! Stop hitting me! Ow, my face!'"
Joke.Vi_Original_Joke_3: "Welcome to the party. Try the punch."

Other Gameplay.Vi_Original_SurviveCaitlynR_2: "Aww, was that supposed to hurt, Cait?"

Movement.Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_0: "Pantheon, I see you! Like a lamprey you attach yourself to a host! I will carve you from this mortal's form, and eviscerate you both!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_2: "Pantheon! I will crush your godhood, I will eviscerate your ideals, even your memory... I will trample!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_FirstMovePantheon_1: "Targon sends an aspect against me? Prepare yourself, Pantheon, I will end all that you hope to be!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_10: "They think me defeated, enchained. But I am unbowed... Noble is this carnage."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_26: "Am I the abyss? Or did I gaze into it?"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_1: "The only peace I seek... is death!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_14: "I am oblivion, I am destruction... I am doom."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_0: "The true sound of my blade can only be heard when they loathe re-incarnation."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_22: "This cursed form... This crude decaying flesh! I loathe it!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_21: "I stood against the void. Now... I would welcome it."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_33: "I cannot die... until all life ends."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_11: "Primitives worship me, hoping for mercy. I shall give them death."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_25: "They will call me a god killer!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_20: "As long as this form lives, I will punish them."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_16: "My suffering... I will make it bloom."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_30: "My darkness was not born, it was forged by my prison."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_28: "I am not a king, I am not a god, I am... worse..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_32: "Those who call me enemy, I welcome them."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_13: "I will snuff out the light, I shall make darkness eternal!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_4: "There is a darkness in my heart deeper than any shadow!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_15: "I march to death... Though I wish it was my own..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_12: "I will drown them in oceans of blood!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_6: "Patience, Aatrox! Patience! Your freedom will come!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_19: "Gods and mortals, they deserve only death!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_27: "Kneel mortals! So I may split your shoulders from your spine!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_5: "March toward vengeance... Drown this world in blood!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_18: "I will render these mortals' forms into my own!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_7: "Their screams will be like the soothing hum of insects at dusk."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_2: "They will call me villain... Come, let me earn their hatred, again and forever."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_Move_29: "We had another name once... Now, we are Darkin."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_9: "I am ready to be the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_7: "I am Aatrox, I am the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_0: "Carnage, hate, yes! I am the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_13: "Take everything from them! Become the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_4: "I bring silence! I am the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveUltReady_8: "There is no escape from the World-Ender!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_14: "Tricked into this existence... False slave entrapped by endless life! I shall become a beast feeding on their destruction, and making them lament my unholy birth!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_10: "I have no goodness left, it was taken from me, stolen! I... am the nemesis of life."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_9: "They sing of love, hope and gods, all that makes them want to live! So, I will quiet that first!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_20: "I shall take their limbs. I will reap their beloved! I will tear from their consciousness, the will to live. Yes, this is my purpose."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_6: "Cleave through them, Aatrox! Crush their skulls! Shatter their ribs! Disembowl their very souls!" *Heavy breathing* "Our vengeance is at hand!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_8: "Every dream is a candle I must snuff out... I... am the darkness..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_2: "The heavens, the endless skies folding into each other. Where are they now?"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_0: "How far I have fallen! A god... reduced to a prisoner!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_15: "Once in noble battle, I screamed against the silence. I stood as light against the darkness. Now, I serve a new master... oblivion..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_1: "See what beasts they have reduced us to... Creatures of flesh sustained only by this filth's blood and form!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_11: "From entire villages and towns, I will rend the flesh... Until I stand... as an unholy god."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_12: "March flesh, march toward them! We have horrors to sow! Lives to reap! Let me make them regret... being free."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_7: "Dark deeds I will do this day... Though I will carry myself as my former pride dictates!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_19: "Where I was excellence, I am deformed... Recast poorly with these crude materials. But this abomination of flesh well serves my murderous intent."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_23: "I shall not kiss the ground, nor let myself be wielded as a tool! I am damned, but I will remake this world in my dark image!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_18: "Let me tear their flesh from them. Let me break their souls... And murder their dreams."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_21: "I am but an unholy copy of life... A mockery of its freedom... And born in the cruel betrayal of the noble ideals I would've served."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_13: "I touched the stars, and saw the glorious light of a thousand suns! Now, blinded by this elegance, how could my purpose be anything... but dark..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_5: "I beg, let some challenge me today... So that I may tear out their hearts! Pray! Let me watch them die, eyes knowing they served... my dark purpose..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_17: "No beast so fierce, but knows some touch of pity... But I know none... and therefore am no beast."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_16: "To war, Aatrox! They shall not rob us of our nobility! We shall stand, and spit venom at our tormentors for eternity!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_24: "I do not obey! I cannot lay down! I will be the ender of all things!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_4: "We march to battle... Let me carve flesh, let me cloak myself in the slaughter! Hide me in their carnage... Hide me from this suffering..."
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_22: "I shall regard their cries as braying steeds, waiting to be whipped, broken, and bridled!"
Movement.Aatrox_Original_MoveLong_3: "I am in a cage within a prison... But this foul shape reminds me of my purpose!"

First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounter_4: "Do you see my edge?! Your death awaits!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounter_5: "Come closer! I will show you... darkness!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterAkali: "Tricks, Akali? They will not hide you from me, face your doom."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterAnivia: "Another foolish god, even the phoenix shall end."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterCamille: "Scissors for legs... Okay, I thought I had seen stupid designs before... Alright, let's go."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterDarius: "Look at your noble courage, Darius! Now learn... despair."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMundo: "You are unloved, Mundo! Now, face judgement!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterFiora: "I know your name, Fiora. This is not a duel you shall win."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterGalio: "A statue? Rock shatters as easily as bone! Come!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterGangplank: "Guns and oranges? Are you a cliché or a joke? Come! Fight! Die!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterGaren: "Scream 'Demacia', Garen! Scream its name before I crush you, and it!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterIllaoi: "I kill gods, priestess. Let us continue this fight... until all things stop!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterKaisa: "You would rush towards me, Kai'Sa? What fool would build a strategy on that idea? Come, let us begin."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterKayle: "Let me show you your error, Kayle! You are not worthy of ascension! You, are not worthy of the worms!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterKayn_0: "I did not think my fellows weak, Rhaast! Already you disappoint me!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterKennen: "A lightning squirrel?" *Laughs* "Thank you! Your death will amuse me!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterKled: "Are you a joke, you loud, horrible thing? I shall kill you and your steed!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite: "Where is your head, rock thing? Where is the neck I shall sever?"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMaokai: "Am I challenged by a tree?! Fine, let me build a pyre from you!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterMorgana: "You would bind yourself to this realm. Morgana? Fine, let me show you the ground!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterNasus: "Nasus, is your wisdom enough to know your fate? I am your death!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterNautilus: "Your noble purpose amuses me, Nautilus! Fight me, see true death!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterOrnn: "Hail father Ornn, god of fire and forge!" *Laughs* "I am Aatrox, and I am the god killer!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterPantheon_1: "Hail Pantheon! Let me hear you cry of friendship! Let me hear you scream of brotherhood!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterPantheon_2: "Hail Pantheon! See the weapon I have become! Watch as you are destroyed!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterPantheon_0: "Hail Pantheon! How noble and proud he carries himself! Come betrayer! Come fiend!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterQuinn: "A bird? You would challenge me with a bird?!" *Laughs* "Come!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterRenekton: "Renekton! In your madness, you know my suffering! Though I shall end yours."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterRiven: "Riven, dance, child! That broken blade is no match for me!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterRumble: "You would challenge me in a machine? You are a strange spirit, Rumble."
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterShen: "A spirit blade, master Shen? Test it agaist me, let me shatter your illusions!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterSion: "Yes Sion! I kill even that which will not die! I end all things!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterTaric: "Hail the protector! Hail Taric, aspect of- get a haircut!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterTeemo: "Cowardly spirit, how annoying you are! I will savour killing you, Teemo!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterTrundle: "A troll king?! Come! Defend your throne, king of trolls!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterTryndamere: "Yes, Tryndamere! I am the cause of your suffering! See if you can cut justice from me!"
"I wait for you, Tryndamere! Come, take your vengeance!"
"Remember the screams of your kinsmen as you fall to me, Tryndamere!"
"Rage? You are just flesh, Tryndamere, ready for harvesting!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterVarus: "You would end worlds? As a bow?!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterYorick: "I will not send you to death, Yorick! I bring oblivion!"
First Encounter.Aatrox_Original_FirstEncounterZoe: "I know it was you, trickster! You gave them the tools to trap me! Come, let me kill you! A thousand times isn't enough!"

Taunt.Aatrox_Original_Taunt_1: "I am Darkin! I do not die!"
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntKayn_1: "A scythe? A scythe?! Are you planning on murdering fields of wheat?!"
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntKayn_0: "I chose a sword, the noblest weapon, Rhaast. You- seriously I don't understand... Were you trapped in the gardening section?"
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntVarus_1: "We all agreed on the double 'A' thing, Varus. The double 'A' thing!"
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntVarus_0: "Varus, 'V' 'A' 'R' 'U' 'S', your name should have an 'A' and then another 'A', Varus. There was a memo, Varus, there was a memo!"
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntTargon: "I will find a way to tear down the heavens and reveal you as fiends! Not today obviously..."
Taunt.Aatrox_Original_TauntVoid: "Do I resemble you, abomination? Your form isn't my destiny... is it? You don't know how to talk, do you? Shit..."

Joke.Aatrox_Original_Joke_0: "I am like a demon, but more edgy, right? You know, cause I'm a sword. Hmm..."
Joke.Aatrox_Original_Joke_1: "So uh, I'm Aatrox. I'm a transcendental being trapped inside cutlery... What's your deal?"
Joke.Aatrox_Original_Joke_2: "Uh, nice world you have here. I intend to destroy it, you know, FYI."

Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_7: "I will hack and chop and cleave, and sunder the filth of your forms!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_13: "I am not your enemy, I am the enemy!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_6: "I am Darkin! Your gods fear me!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_15: "I will sever your limbs! I will carve your souls!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_20: "I can smile, and murder while I smile."
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_12: "Sorrow... I shall deliver it to you."
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_8: "I begged for death, now I am its bringer!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_Attack_10: "You would fight me?! Come, let me show you hell!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_AttackPantheon_1: "The power of an aspect, wasted on a fool!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_AttackTryndamere_1: "I killed your tribe. Now, join them!"
Attack.Aatrox_Original_AttackZoe_0: "I will gut you, and tear you from existence, trickster!"

Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_Kill_9: "To the end of times, I shall kill you again and again."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_Kill_4: "I brought you the one true gift, I brought you... death!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_Kill_8: "Your broken form speaks only of failure."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_Kill_3: "Resurrect! Return! So I may kill you again..."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillAnivia: "Resurrection, an endless cycle of life... A dead bird."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillCamille: "What foolish plan bore a woman such as you, Camille? You were a folly, crafted by an idiot."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillDarius: "The axe suited you, Darius, the weapon of a simpleton!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillFiora: "I expected you to be nimble, Fiora. Too easily, my blade crushed your spine."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillGaren: "Demacia!" *Laughs* "Whatever 'Demacia' is, I will slay it next!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillIllaoi: "In time I will learn how to kill even your god, Illaoi!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillKaisa: "I cannot know if I was corrupted by the void, but at least my choices were not asinine."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillKayle: "Die, Kayle, knowing your potential will never be reached."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillKled: "What is property? Why did this dead hamster want me off of it?"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillMalphite: "I kill mountains, Malphite! Dumb piles of rocks!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillMaokai: "Hear me, tree spirit. Your form is but kindling, and your forests I will burn!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillMorgana: "You disgust me, Morgana. Die in the filth of your bound flesh!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillNasus: "Yes, Shurima was meant to fall, Nasus, as were you!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillPantheon: "Pantheon, you crawl forward like a worm! Ready to be squashed again?"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillRiven: "Now your body matches your blade, Riven: broken and worthless!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillShen: "Die, Shen, knowing the Eye of the Twilight is blinded and plucked."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillSion: "You fought to live, Sion, yet it is I who am still alive. This at least amuses."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillTaric: "Lord of starlight, lord of hair! I trample on your corpse, Taric! I spit on your aspect's purpose!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillTeemo: "A spirit for cowards, I laugh at your tricks and mushrooms!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillTryndamere: "I thought you my next vessel, Tryndamere. Pity, you failed even to become a slave."
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillVarus_1: "Return again to your prison, Varus. Think upon your worthlessness!"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillVarus_0: "Honestly, a bow and two boys? What was your plan, Varus?"
Kills and Objectives.Aatrox_Original_KillZoe: "How I loathe your freedom, trickster! I will take this vengeance upon you, until the end of times!"

Other Gameplay.Aatrox_Original_MasteryBadgeStartedNearb: "Mastery? I must congratulate you, obviously your parents never had reason to."
"Yes, your mastery is the master of masters! I am fighting... an imbecile..."
"Mastery, how I idolise your greatness! Though I suspect your weapon lacks... impact."
"Ah, mastery, well done! Now master your insignificance."
Other Gameplay.Aatrox_Original_R_Revive_3: "Insects, you think you can kill me? Behold my curse!"
Other Gameplay.Aatrox_Original_R_Revive_13: "Did you think you could kill me?!"
Other Gameplay.Aatrox_Original_R_Revive_11: "As long as life exists, as long as time has meaning, I am not done!"

Movement.Yuumi_030: "Alright! Which one of you's got great aim, and is good at chin scritches?"
Movement.Yuumi_069: "Cats make great companions! Just ask my master... who disappeared under mysterious circumstances."
Movement.Yuumi_172: "Who's ready to risk our lives, defeat our foes, and maybe knock over some cups?"
Movement.Yuumi_087: "Tell me the game plan again. Wait. Fish! Someone has fish! Where is it?"
Movement.Yuumi_171: "So, who wants to be my best friend? ...Book, I know you're already my best friend!"
Movement.Yuumi_025: "Keep an eye out for red dot, Book! It's gotta be here somewhere."
Movement.Yuumi_077: "Where's my fishy fishy fish for my dishy dishy dish?"
Movement.Yuumi_083: "Where's my fishy fish fish dish? Meow!"
Movement.Yuumi_114: "I won't lose you, Book! Not after losing Master."
Movement.Yuumi_046: "Don't tell anyone but... I love hugs."
Movement.Yuumi_023: "Do not drop me! Do not drop me!"
Movement.Yuumi_048: "This way! No THIS way! Woah-kay, that way it is."
Movement.Yuumi_157: "They aren't ready for the ferocious team of... US!"
Movement.Yuumi_158: "You can pet me on my chin and back! Nowhere else. Mrow."
Movement.Yuumi_153: "Do you have snacks in your pocket? How 'bout now? ...How 'bout now?!"
Movement.Yuumi_106: "Is it time to save our friends again?"
Movement.Yuumi_122: "Ooh, you smell good! Did you recently fish?"
Movement.Yuumi_019: "I could tell you wanted a brave and powerful warrior by your side."
Movement.Yuumi_088: "Do you ever get so sleepy you fall asleep sitting up? Just me?"
Movement.Yuumi_055: "Okay, it's time to prowl! You do know how to prowl, right?"
Movement.Yuumi_146: "Rubbing my head on you means you're mine!"
Movement.Yuumi_105: "If we find a rat, I call dibs! Or a bug. Or a FISH!"
Movement.Yuumi_095: "Wherever you go, I go! Just... don't go somewhere bad."
Movement.Yuumi_128: "Naps make my magic stronger! It's true! Look!" Yuumi snores and pretends to sleeptalk. "I'm so strong, mmh, so strong!"
Movement.Yuumi_138: "Hey Book, do you ever take a nap? ...You can't?! What do you do all day?!"
Movement.Yuumi_142: "Book, sometimes I pretend you're just a nice comfy box! ...What? That's a compliment!"
Movement.Yuumi_078: "The Book-keeper is a great role for someone as responsible as me! ...What?"
Movement.Yuumi_080: "I save my friends? No one notices. I open a teensy portal to the spirit realm? Everyone is up in my fur!"
Movement.Yuumi_150: "If I didn't have to protect Book, I'd just be a normal magical cat floating around Bandle City! Okay, napping around Bandle City."
Movement.Yuumi_014: "I've read all of Book. Well, most of Book. I like the pictures of fish... of which there are none, Book!"
Movement.Yuumi_143: "Ah, I miss the way my yordle scratched between my ears. ...Being read from cover to cover sounds nice too."
Movement.Yuumi_168: "Hmm, today should I follow my head? Or my nose, or.. OH! Sunbeam ahead! Let's chase that!"
Movement.Yuumi_165: "Someone scratched out the page that led here! That's right, Book. Someone! We'll never know who."
Movement.Yuumi_097: "If I ever lost you, Book, the fabric of the spirit realm would get all torn up! And I'd lose my best friend."
Movement.Yuumi_164: "I'm descended from lions! And you're descended from trees! We're in our element, Book!"
Movement.Yuumi_139: "The only thing standing between us and lunch is... our enemies."
Movement.Yuumi_018: "I am the brains, you are the brawn, Book... is Book!"
Movement.Yuumi_113: "In case you're wondering what that smell is, it's Book. Smells like old trees."
Movement.Yuumi_124: "Don't worry, I'll be here through thick or thin! Unless I smell fish. Gasp- Do you have fish?!"
Movement.Yuumi_008: "Hey, new friend? Uh, warn me if you're going to do something crazy, okay?"
Movement.Yuumi_012: "Don't get too attached, Book! This one looks reckless..."
Movement.Yuumi_050: "Hey. Hey. Hey. HEY! ...Huh? Oh no, I don't need anything!"
Movement.Yuumi_038: "You hungry? I stuck a leftover rat on page 237! Mew!"
Movement.Yuumi_159: "Do you know what "vexatious" means? Book called me that and I think it might be mean."
Movement.Yuumi_115: "If someone told you to jump in a lake, would you do it? Just 'cause... I go where you go."
Movement.Yuumi_015: "I bet we'll be friends forever! Well, unless you wander into the brush with your face."

Movement.Samira_Original_MoveFirst_3: "Name's Samira. Try not to slow me down."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveFirst_2: "If you can't keep up don't step up. I don't have time for fools."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveFirst_1: "Listen up, you sorry lot! Only one rule for this mission: take no prisoners."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveFirst_0: "I've got two rules for every fight. Don't ask for permission, don't ask for forgiveness."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_9: "Virtues? I've got a few. Vices? Heh, a few more."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_4: "Some choose steel. Others, bullets. Why not both?"
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_2: "In every girl, there is a queen."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_5: "I am the beauty and the beast."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_16: "Only need one eye to hit my mark."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_17: "Well-behaved women don't make it in Noxus."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_8: "I'm not built to win. I'm built to conquer."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_22: "Oh, how great it would feel to shoot my past in the face."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_20: "Last person I loved thought I was too reckless. Their loss."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_14: "Hope I get some blood on these boots. The color's a bit dull."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_13: "The empire values strength. I value style. We're good partners."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_0: "I'm the rose that survived the desert."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_7: "'Refugee.' That label is where I draw my strength."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_10: "Money buys a gun or two. Thrill buys a reputation."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_21: "Why be average when I can be savage?"
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_15: "I feel most alive when I'm walking the line."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_11: "Guns and swords go together like rice and saffron."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_19: "The ascended think they own my people. They are wrong."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_18: "Life's simple. Take the shot or lose the chance."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_6: "My folks keep telling me to settle down. Not my style."
Movement.Samira_Original_Move_23: "Thrilling! Ha! Maybe I'll get a tattoo to celebrate the occasion."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_8: "If they think I kill for fame and fortune, ha! They're idiots, just like all the others."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_9: "I chose this life. And sure, someday it might get me killed... but 'til then, I'm unstoppable."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_5: "Those who followed the ascended burned away my home. So don't expect me to follow anyone."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_6: "Indari was a great captain. She taught me how to shoot. I taught myself how to kill."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_2: "I care most about my warband or my family. Order changes depending on who gets on my nerves."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_3: "Born in Shurima, raised by Noxus. Maybe I'll die in Demacia to make things interesting, huh?"
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_0: "People always ask about my weapons. Right hand, Blaze. Left hand, Thorn. Vanquish on the back, eh! Simple as that."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_4: "Sometimes, I'm the hero. Other times, I'm the villain. It's all a matter of perspective."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_1: "Growing up, my mamman taught me one lesson. Death isn't the scariest thing. It's a mother's rage."
Movement.Samira_Original_MoveLong_7: "Darius, Swain, pft! Those names mean little to me. I answer to myself."

First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterAmumu: "The sad mummy! My mamman used to tell stories about you when I was a girl. How I loved them."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterDraven: "I know your type, Draven. The kind of man who's compensating for something."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterEzreal: "That gauntlet would be better off without you, kid."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterLeblanc: "You seem kinda pale, LeBlanc. Sure you're getting enough sun?"
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterMissFortun: "Sarah, is it? I've killed many captains. Let's see how you measure up."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterRammus: "A talking turtle? Okay, maybe I did have one too many."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterSivir: "Sivir. You say you'll do anything for the right price, but what's the price of one's destiny?"
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterSwain: "Hey, old man. How long you got before that demon takes over?"
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterThresh: "Honestly, lantern man? Not sure you can handle my soul."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterVladimir: "If it looks like a blood sucker and it sounds like a blood sucker... Maybe I ought to kill it."
First Encounter.Samira_Original_FirstEncounterXerath: "Xerath. Your people ended my home. I will end your existence."

Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_0_0: "Come children of hopes and dreams. Let me show you what life cannot."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_0_1: "My collection is my family, and its spirits, my beloved children."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_0_2: "Lost spirits everywhere. I must guide them home."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_0_3: "Tiny twinkles of life, struggling ever so intensely. I will light their path."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveFirst_0_4: "Ah... Life. So simple, so naive, like a flower yet to bloom."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_21: "Torment is such a harsh word. I prefer, nurture."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_22: "Cruelty is a gift I learn from the living."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_19: "Spirits, alone and forsaken. I grant them all purpose."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_6: "To the living, I am a demon. To the dead, I am a savior."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_8: "Poor lost souls. I must save them all from themselves."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_2: "Why must they fear me? I do not bite, I merely collect."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_20: "Every spirit is useful. That, is why I must collect them all."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_4: "They think me a god? No. Nothing that simple."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_1: "What is the worth of a spirit?"
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_15: "No need to rush. Death will bless us all!"
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_11: "I am not the end. I am the final awakening"
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_14: "I do not discriminate. All must find comfort inside my lantern."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_10: "Life is pain, I am sweet release."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_7: "Blessed are those who need my guidance."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_0: "Screams of agony echo my favorite melodies."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveStandard_0_9: "To live is to suffer. To survive, is to find beauty in the suffering."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_9: "The dead passing to spirits. The spirits passing to my collection. That, is how it must be."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_3: "In life, you are heroes and villains. In death, you are all my children."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_1: "Do not fear me. I am but a servant of the natural order that guides us all."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_10: "That little fox and I once guided spirits together, but now, I must save them from her errant ways."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_11: "Without me, the dead would be lost. I am what drives them to greatness."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_6: "I am friends with all spirits, until they decide to question me."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_0: "Poor lost spirits beckoning to bloom. I've been waiting for you."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_2: "Do not worry my dear spirits, you will all be safe in my collection."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_4: "My children, my collection, blossom with potential."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_7: "The living say, 'look death in the eye.' I do love an intimate connection."
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_5: "No one understands the intricacies of my collection, that is why I must never stop!"
Movement.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_MoveLong_0_8: "Those privy to my secrets? They are safe with me now."

First Encounter.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_FirstEncounter_0: "Deny me your spirit. I do enjoy a good chase."

First Encounter.Thresh_SpiritBlossom_FirstEncounterSenna: "Senna, my dear girl. I do hope you enjoyed your taste of freedom, but now, you must come home."

Champion Select.Illaoi_Select: "I'm not big on sermons - broken bones teach better lessons."

Movement.Illaoi_Original_FirstMove_0: "It is my burden to carry an eye of god. It is my privilege to see the truth."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_FirstMove_2: "We cannot comprehend the design. A raindrop cannot comprehend a river valley."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_FirstMove_1: "To die is to drown - so I will swim well, till I can swim no more."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_6: "If I hate something, I destroy it. If I want something, I take it."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_14: "We are born knowing what to do. We must only act."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_5: "It is terrible to be satisfied. The world needs us to chase dreams."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_17: "This ends one of two ways - they run, or I break them."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_3: "I don't scare, I don't tire, and I don't stop."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_28: "Good? Evil? Why should we care for such things?"
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_18: "Life is the sweetness of fruit, and the joy of battle!"
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_32: "There is joy in food... and fighting."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_23: "Ah, everyone has a plan, until they get punched in the face."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_11: "Men live, men die. Change is good."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_12: "They will learn or they will die."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_29: "There are kind and gentle gods. Mine isn't one of those."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_34: "The ocean is calm. It is our desires that stir it."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_7: "Even if I die, I die in motion."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_20: "The waves will drag you down, unless you fight to shore."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_0: "How could I love only one man? They break too easily."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_1: "Wisdom is frequently a kick in the head."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_4: "We are not one soul. We are many."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_2: "Many gods ask for worship. They are weak gods."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_13: "My god is not love - it is a kick in the pants."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_24: "Without change, something sleeps inside us, and seldom awakens."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_35: "Many die. Worthy souls find new forms."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_21: "Bearded Lady, Nagakabouros, names don't matter! Action does."
Movement.Illaoi_Original_Move_26: "It is the storm that is life."

Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_1: "Live your life, chase what you desire, what else matters?"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_2: "A fool and his spirit are easily parted."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_4: "Watch your mouth, or I'll slap the soul out of you."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_5: "Fight me, if you have the spirit."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_0: "I want you to hit me as hard as you can."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_Taunt_3: "Smile, child, or I'll shove your jaw into your brain."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShurima_Ascended_3: "You wanted to be a god! Instead, you are a useless antique!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShurima_Ascended_2: "Foul creature, you would stop time when all things must move!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShurima_Ascended_1: "You soul is a fetid, stagnant pool, untouched by the tide!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShurima_Ascended_4: "You are not free from death! You are dead."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShurima_Ascended_6: "Your powers are stolen from the flow. You have damned your homeland."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDemacia_3: "What is truly noble and good would never ask you to serve another!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDemacia_1: "Duty, honor, nations? These are stagnant falsehoods!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDemacia_2: "You are slaves enchained by lies when we were born to chase our desires!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDemacia_0: "Laws, rules, these are falsehoods! Truth is chaos!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntFreljord_1: "Your people pretend to be strong. I think they are afraid."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntFreljord_0: "Your people seek a worthy death. Mine, a worthy life."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShadowIsles_6: "You are a cycle without purpose. I will end you!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShadowIsles_0: "You are a cloud of broken souls, you are an abomination."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShadowIsles_4: "You will trouble this land no more."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShadowIsles_1: "I am your enemy because you offend my god - because you cannot change."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntShadowIsles_3: "You will challenge me? Ha ha ha ha... even death fears my god."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntYordles_2: "Why would I need a spirit's help? I am guided by Nagakabouros."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntYordles_0: "Little one, I don't need empathy. Seek those who do."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntYordles_1: "Go back to where men are weak, and need your inspiration."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntAatrox: "We know your true name. We do not fear you."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntAkali: "Life is not balance. It is motion!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntBraum_2: "Northman. There are motions I would like to show you."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntBraum_0: "I know you are strong. I wonder if you have stamina."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDarius_0: "You move well. Now, you must only find joy in the motion."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntDiana: "Your god was forgotten. Mine cannot be ignored."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntElise: "False prophet! You don't even serve a true god!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntFiora: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGangplank_5: "I broke men's hearts. I broke men's spines. You're the first who's going to get both."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGangplank_3: "You paid your tithe to the mother. Now show me what she taught you."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGangplank_0: "You have learned your lesson, now fight! Kill! Conquer!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGangplank_4: "I do not want excuses. The failure was yours."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGangplank_1: "Did she not show you the way forward? Go!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGaren: "Honor? Duty? Ha! What your heart demands is all that matters."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntGragas_1: "You have followed our ways as if born to them."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntJanna: "The tempest is Nagakabouros. You serve, but are blind."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntJax: "I do not challenge you, I bring you the test!"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntKarma: "Trust the motion. All spirits are Nagakabouros'."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntKatarina: "No love is impossible, my god demands you follow your desires."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntLeona_1: "You worship the sun - it is my god that drives it through the sky."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntLeona_0: "Your faith asks for obedience - it is weak."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntMissfortune_1: "It is you who have shown Gangplank his path. For that, I thank you."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntMissfortune_0: "Gangplank was drowning. Your actions reminded him to swim."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntReksai_0: "You are in motion - but only as a parasite on a host."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntReksai_2: "Ugly thing. You weren't designed by god, you were made by fools."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntReksai_3: "You are a foul creation - born from ignorance."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntReksai_4: "What kind of stupid god made you?"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntTahmKench_1: "You move only from hunger that consumes itself."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntTahmKench_0: "Creature, why would I listen to lies when I can see the truth?"
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntTahmKench_2: "Your fine words don't disguise your foul design."
Taunt.Illaoi_Original_TauntTwistedFate_1: "Aw, child, you are cute, but I doubt you will be for long."

Attack.Illaoi_Original_Attack_12: "Ha ha ha, you think you can beat me?"
Attack.Illaoi_Original_Attack_3: "They need wisdom. They don't need teeth."
Attack.Illaoi_Original_AttackBaron_0: "I slayed greater serpents as a child."
Attack.Illaoi_Original_AttackBaron_1: "Here they call you a monster. In Buhru, we would call you dinner."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_Hit_1_4: "This is the motion. All is Nagakabouros."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_Hit_1_1: "You cannot hide from god. You cannot hide from the test."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_6: "Live your journey - or die in mine."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_24: "You speak of having a soul. It was never yours. None of them were."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_22: "You are drowning - I want you to swim."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_17: "Each of your lives has served the vortex."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_0: "This will be a good day - if you live."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_5: "The battle is lost only when you surrender. Fight for your soul."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_29: "You are the tinest sliver of energy held briefly in shape. Where this energy flows is your destiny."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_27: "This moment is waiting to be seized."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_2: "Every day is waiting to be taken."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_12: "I don't want you to worship. I want you to learn."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_33: "I will break you if that's what it takes."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_9: "Give up, and your life is nothing."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_DebuffVO_3: "Each lifetime is a spirit. Each lifetime is a chance. Take it."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_tentaclekill_1: "Do not tire, do not slow, push onward."

Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_tentaclekill_5: "Keep going, keep striving. This is our way."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_tentaclekill_3: "Your souls wait for you. Take them back if you can."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_tentaclekill_10: "This is the way of Nagakabouros - motion!"
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_tentaclekill_4: "To challenge, to fight... this pleases Nagakabouros."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_recoversoul_5: "Pray I don't have to teach you again."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_recoversoul_8: "Learn well, or you will be tested again."
Ability Casting.Illaoi_Original_E_recoversoul_1: "You have been tested. You have done well."

Attack.Rakan.attack08: "It ain't a party without a fight!"
Attack.Rakan.attack13: "I got one more thing for you!"
Attack.Rakan.attack23: "You will see the dance of death."
Attack.Rakan.attack32: "Hey! I got a joke for you!"
Attack.Rakan.attack36: "Oh! I need to get in there!"
Attack.Rakan.attack37: "Hey, what did the five fingers say to the face?"
Attack.Rakan.attack53: "I like parties with a little violence!"
Attack.Rakan.attack56: "I have killed for her! I will kill for her again."
Attack.Rakan.attack62: "Count it down! One, two, they dead!"
Attack.Rakan.attack63: "I'm here! We can get it started!"

Attack.Rakan.attackMelee16.1: "I can't hear you over all the fun I'm having!"

Attack.Rakan.attackXayah13: "You love it when I slap fools?"
Attack.Rakan.attackXayah15: "What do you want to do later?"
Attack.Rakan.attackXayah20: "Do we need any of these fools?"

Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward01: "I need to see if people can see how awesome I am!"
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward02: "When you open your eyes, you see everything is limitless."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward03: "I need to know when the action's coming."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward04: "Well I don't want to miss the start of the party."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward06: "The world's a big place. Don't want to miss any of it."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward07: "I'm pretty sure I'm supposed to scout around. Pretty, pretty sure."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward08: "I'll just put that there. That's a good place. I hope. Yeah... "
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward10: "Yep, if I'm going to see the human world I need to start."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward11: "I'm going to show people some of the strange."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward13: "I am not blind to any possibility."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward14: "I know people are watching. How could they not be?"
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward15: "If you look at things the right way, it's awesome."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward16: "The world isn't about collecting stuff, it's about seeing stuff."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward19: "Mankind is blind. I want them to see."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward20: "Vision is the first step towards understanding."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward21: "Aw, crap, I hate having to have a plan."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward23: "I think Xayah told me to improvise. At least, that's the only part of the plan I remember."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward24: "Let's see what these animals can do."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward26: "Our kind will see the truth soon enough."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward27: "I want to feel everything. That's the only way to live."
Other Gameplay.Rakan.ward31: "I should totally get paid for this."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan03.1: "Couldn't have done it without you, mieli."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan04: "Every time you do that, it drives me crazy."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan04.1: "Well. I'll have to do it more often, then."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan05.1: "Probably, but there are two of us."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan10.1: "Isn't a Vastayan farewell when you say, "ouulavaash?"
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan10.2: "I was trying to have a moment, Rakan."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.killRakan11: "Did you see that? Haha! That was amazing!"

Shopping.Xayah.item01: "This is overpriced - but I must have it."
Shopping.Xayah.item02: "I want to buy all the things!"
Shopping.Xayah.item05: "I know I'm being price gouged, but I'll splurge."
Shopping.Xayah.item06: "Where did you get all these wonderful things?"
Shopping.Xayah.item08: "Hook me up with that magical creature discount?"

Other Gameplay.Xayah.ward02: "Sometimes, I have to watch my own back."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.ward07: "I never walk into a trap unprepared."
Other Gameplay.Xayah.ward08: "I hate surprises - unless I'm doing the surprising."
