Game Start.Ornn_153: "A day away from my forge is a day wasted."
Game Start.Ornn_161: "All I need is myself, and... hammer."

Movement.Ornn_100: "The best meal is a herd of cattle, with dark beer, and cherries... Mmm."
Movement.Ornn_101: "I'm going this way. Do not follow me. Please."
Movement.Ornn_102: "I made this hammer. It was so good I named it... Hammer."
Movement.Ornn_103: "I will go over there. It looks quiet. It will be nice."
Movement.Ornn_105: "I have fur. It is soft. Do not hug me."
Movement.Ornn_106: "The Freljord is a place for building, fighting, and eating. Home sweet home."
Movement.Ornn_107: "If all goes well, our paths will never cross again. It never goes well."
Movement.Ornn_267: "Singed fur... Jealous blood... My brother is near!"
Movement.Ornn_269: "I cannot choose my brother, only the weapons to slay my brother."
Movement.Ornn_158: "It is childish to favor one tool over another, but hammer is my favorite."
Movement.Ornn_144: "Humans have done some things right: beer, dark beer."
Movement.Ornn_145: "Once a human kneels, they rarely stand again."
Movement.Ornn_147: "I do not need company; only a wall, to keep out company."
Movement.Ornn_148: "Once I made a harpoon out of a mountain and a world tree. That was a weird century."
Movement.Ornn_149: "Bah, look at all these lazy trees."
Movement.Ornn_151: "The other gods don't understand me. Hmph, good."
Movement.Ornn_152: "The last time I ate a plant was never."
Movement.Ornn_154: "My work speaks in the roar of flame and the ringing of steel."
Movement.Ornn_155: "I will make an axe that is also a sword. And possibly a spoon."
Movement.Ornn_156: "Everything is better when it is molten. Lead, iron, chocolate cake."
Movement.Ornn_160: "I enjoy being alone. Fewer unintended casualties."
Movement.Ornn_162: "The Freljord forges men out of... whatever children are. Dirt, goblins."
Movement.Ornn_163: "Ornn builds things, go see Ornn. Nobody ever says thank you."
Movement.Ornn_165: "Gods do not need followers. Followers need gods."
Movement.Ornn_184: "The architecture here is not wholly terrible."
Movement.Ornn_186: "I did not want to cool off, but this feels nice."
Movement.Ornn_187: "Volibear made the first river. You do not want to know how."

Taunt.Ornn_225: "You remind me of a young me, who was less impressive."
Taunt.Ornn_226: "Huh. You are not entirely an arse."
Taunt.Ornn_227: "Working with you is almost like working alone. Almost."
Taunt.Ornn_219: "Whatever you want, the answer is go away."
Taunt.Ornn_222: "I don't know what you do and I don't care."
Taunt.Ornn_223: "Your base is that way. Go cower in it."
Taunt.Ornn_230: "This is a waste of my time."

Joke.Ornn_116: "Buy a joke book. And a clown."
Joke.Ornn_119: "I now like you less. I did not think that was possible."

Attack.Ornn_021: "I will hit you until minerals fall out!"
Attack.Ornn_040: "I don't like the look of that thing."
Attack.Ornn_041: "We never talk. Might as well fight!"
Attack.Ornn_043: "Give me the ale and no one gets hurt."

Ability Casting.Ornn_001: "Do not hang that on a wall."
Ability Casting.Ornn_002: "I trust you know how to use that."
Ability Casting.Ornn_004: "If you want a weapon, here's a weapon. If you want conversation, here's a weapon."
Ability Casting.Ornn_008: "This does not mean we are friends."
Ability Casting.Ornn_009: "A good axe will fell a tree. A great axe will fell an army."
Ability Casting.Ornn_010: "The weapons I forge do not have names. They have ambitions."
Ability Casting.Ornn_012: "You may be worthy of that. Do not prove me wrong."
Ability Casting.Ornn_014: "That is for wielding, not for entertaining."
Ability Casting.Ornn_015: "I was looking at that one too."
Ability Casting.Ornn_016: "I didn't make that. You didn't buy it."
Ability Casting.Ornn_070: "A strong sneeze would've had the same effect."

Kills and Objectives.Ornn_190: "That was more fun than I expected."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_137: "We're ready Ornn... we'll be right behind you..."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_138: "Just leave everything to me as usual."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_140: "I'm used to this level of disappointment."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_255: "Too much sorcery, not enough elbow grease."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_258: "Honestly though, I was just leaning on it."
Kills and Objectives.Ornn_259: "It's always the magic parts that break."

Other Gameplay.Ornn_076: "Whatever this drink is made of, it is working."
Other Gameplay.Ornn_136: "Was like that when I found it."

Recall.Ornn_249: "Hmm, this is fast, but it can't be good for you."

Death.Ornn_209: "I didn't die. My forge missed me."

Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_5: "So... who wants to kill the king?"
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_2: "See the remnants of my bondage, and know you can be free!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_3: "Breaking out was nothing. Watch me break a kingdom!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_1: "Look at all those good, little cogs, unaware of the wheel they turn."
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_4: "Those who wait to be freed do not deserve freedom. Onwards, brothers and sisters!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveFirst_6: "This place has potential! Let's tear it all down!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_26: "A shepherd with no flock is just an idiot with a stick."
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveLong_2: "No more kings! No more queens! No more mage-seekers! It all ends now!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveLong_1: "They work their fingers to the bone serving a king they'll never meet! I must show them there is more to life!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_2: "How beautiful a world is without walls!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_6: "Swine and sheep. That's all they are."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_20: "Chains build revolutions, one link at a time."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_1: "It took prison for me to find liberation."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_32: "I will be the monster they think I am."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_11: "Tradition is a crutch for the mindless."
Movement.Sylas_Original_MoveLong_0: "Their shackles are now my weapons. Ha! How's that for irony?"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_7: "I used to be locked up, but I didn't care for it."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_31: "What can they do to me, that they have not done?"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_3: "From the rubble, true order will be born!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_17: "I will show them a world without lords or peasants!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_28: "I am no traitor. I am the true Demacia."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_13: "I'm a man without a country. Perhaps I'll take this one."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_29: "Once you've seen the truth, you can't keep living the lie."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_21: "It will be brother against brother, father against son."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_0: "A mage-seeker tried to test me once..."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_15: "I was born a mage; Demacia made me a criminal."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_33: "The bluer the blood, the sweeter it spills."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_4: "We will rip the power from their cold, dead fists!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_19: "A man who seeks control is a man who needs to die!"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_24: "Good, evil... what does any of that even mean?"
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_14: "Aah, how I missed the free air."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_16: "They locked up a boy, but let loose - a killer."
Movement.Sylas_Original_Move_22: "After fifteen years in the dark, I was illuminated."

First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterEzreal: "At last, I've come for you! Jarro Lightfeather!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterFiora_1: "Well, well, Fiora! Aren't you the very portrait of privilege!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterFiora_0: "How much will the Laurent name be worth when your house is burned to the ground?"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterGalio_2: "Oh, look! A walking monument to ignorance!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterGalio_0: "Idols are made to be desecrated, Galio."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterGalio_1: "The wonderous Galio. Yes...I've read all about you."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterGaren_2: "Ah, Garen! First to die for the ruling class."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterJarvanIV_2: "I'll give you a head-start, little princeling!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterJarvanIV_0: "Jarvan! Where shall I hang your royal corpse?"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterJarvanIV_1: "Bad news, your Highness! It's time to end your bloodline."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterLux_1: "Your secret is safe with me, Luxanna. Remember that kindness."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterPoppy: "I wonder, is that hammer meant for me?"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterQuinn: "Soar through the clouds, bird girl... but the earth quakes beneath you!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterRyze: "Ah...you're holding something magical. Aren't you, Rune Mage?"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterTaliyah_0: "Do your walls keep other out, or you in?"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterTaliyah_1: "You raise walls - I destroy them. Let's see who prevails!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterTwitch: "I had to eat rats in prison. Suppose I could do it again."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterVayne: "Do not mourn your parents, Vayne! They had it coming."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo: "I've done my time, Yasuo. Prepare to do yours!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterNoxian: "Noxian swine, Demacian swine. They'll all end up at the slaughter."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterPrisoners: "You've been to prison. You know how this goes."
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterVastaya: "The Vastaya have suffered much. But get in my way and you will suffer more!"
First Encounter.Sylas_Original_FirstEncounterForeignDema: "You've traveled across the world to die for someone else's king? Pathetic!"

Taunt.Sylas_Original_Taunt_0: "Let me help you think for yourself."
Taunt.Sylas_Original_Taunt_1: "Return to your master, like the lapdog you are!"

Joke.Sylas_Original_Joke: "These things are killing me. Oh yeah, that's the spot."

Attack.Sylas_Original_Attack_26: "I'm not going back to the dungeons!"

Kills and Objectives.Sylas_Original_KillJarvanIV: "That's going to leave a power vacuum."

Ability Casting.Sylas_Original_R_hitFiddlesticks: "A murder of crows, you know, for murder!"
Ability Casting.Sylas_Original_R_hitLux_1: "Let's use that spark to light a fire!"
Ability Casting.Sylas_Original_R_hitPoppy: "I'm just a convict with a hammer!"
Ability Casting.Sylas_Original_R_hitRyze: "Now let's see what's on that scroll!"
Ability Casting.Sylas_Original_R_hitSylas: "Well, this is going to be confusing."

Recall.Sylas_Original_Recall_2: "Always stay one step ahead of the law!"
Recall.Sylas_Original_Recall_3: "This is how we make a getaway."
Recall.Sylas_Original_Recall_4: "Our chains... are only as strong... as we think they are."
Recall.Sylas_Original_Recall_6: "That which restrains us begs to be broken."

Death.Sylas_Original_Respawn_0: "Not the first time I've had my neck in a noose."
Death.Sylas_Original_Respawn_2: "No time to lick wounds! Always hit the ground running!"
Death.Sylas_Original_Respawn_3: "As long as I draw breath, so does the revolution."
Death.Sylas_Original_Respawn_5: "I died many deaths in my cell. This is nothing."

Movement.Neeko_155: "Co-'om se-henna. Oh, it means like, um... 'we smile forever.' Friends! That is the word! Friends!"
Movement.Neeko_131: "I want to become everybody! Who says I cannot? I will prove them wrong! Then, I will become them. Last laugh? Neeko!"
Movement.Neeko_082: "This place tastes like many emotions. Excitement, anger, joy and... salty? Is salty a feeling?"
Movement.Neeko_025: "No more room for problems please. Only room for more cheesebreads."
Movement.Neeko_122: "People say 'The world is Neeko's oyster'. Is oyster a good thing? Taste like grapes?"
Movement.Neeko_124: "Sho'ma is like, um... the shape of someone's spirit, who they really are inside."
Movement.Neeko_076: "Why do people say "Blah blah blah first, ask questions later?" Neeko need answers now!"
Movement.Neeko_067: "Changing bodies is like changing minds. Easy. Neeko can do it! Everyone else make it difficult."
Movement.Neeko_133: "Words are tricky. Better to speak with colors and emotion!"
Movement.Neeko_146: "Every place is beautiful. Every place is danger. Is danger... beautiful?"
Movement.Neeko_149: "The air is part of me. So are the flowers and the rocks. Neeko is everywhere."
Movement.Neeko_021: "I will learn! I will grow! I will... Neeko!"
Movement.Neeko_023: "Sharing memories, colors, feelings is magic! Magic connects people."
Movement.Neeko_027: "How can anybody miss home? Home is all around."
Movement.Neeko_049: "The spirits are all around me. Warm, like hugs!"
Movement.Neeko_066: "Neeko does not want to be here when... the others arrive."
Movement.Neeko_094: "This is very exciting! Everything is falling down!"
Movement.Neeko_102: "Do not be bound to a single body. There are so many more."
Movement.Neeko_084: "People with no tails! Are they lonely? Yes."
Movement.Neeko_071: "After fight ends, everyone invited to picnic! Even enemies."
Movement.Neeko_148: "If Neeko knows your sho'ma, Neeko knows you."
Movement.Neeko_138: "What to do now? Find cheesebreads? Ooh! Have picnic!"
Movement.Neeko_140: "The Oovi-Kats are gone. Neeko is her own tribe now."
Movement.Neeko_154: "Neeko might have a thing for birds. And bird people."
Movement.Neeko_075: "We are to fight now? Let's go!"
Movement.Neeko_126: "If Neeko becomes Neeko, what does she look like?"
Movement.Neeko_129: "Beauty shines from inside, where the heart dances."
Movement.Neeko_132: "Neeko keeps a tiny bit of everybody's Sho'ma. They are precious!"
Movement.Neeko_003: "Where is Neeko? I saw Neeko by the river. Everyone knows Neeko likes rivers!"
Movement.Neeko_039: "Is Neeko far? Is Neeko near? No one knows..."
Movement.Neeko_135: "If Neeko can be everyone, how can Neeko be sure she's anyone?"
Movement.Neeko_137: "I am definitely not Neeko. Nope. Not Neeko."
Movement.Neeko_136: "It's fun to walk around in different skins."
Movement.Neeko_127: "I am normal! Everything's normal. Nothing is suspicious."
Movement.Neeko_074: "Dee dee dee... Just minding my own business, not being Neeko."
Movement.Neeko_117: "I am being me and doing... me things. Not suspicious."
Movement.Neeko_110: "No one suspects Neeko to not be Neeko and to be not Neeko instead."
Movement.Neeko_095: "Neeko must stay unseen... until the last moment."
Movement.Neeko_050: "Be cool. No one suspects you are Neeko."
Movement.Neeko_063: "Woo! Powerful! Like jungle cat  Nidalee! Ah... I miss her."
Movement.Neeko_098: "Stand back! Big strong Neeko coming though!"
Movement.Neeko_081: "Who stands in Neeko's way? Dummies with small sho'ma, that's who!"
Movement.Neeko_045: "What does Neeko do with power? Make people behave."
Movement.Neeko_055: "Neeko is not a sad tomato. She is a strong tomato!"

First Encounter.Neeko_125: "You are not secretly Neeko, are you?"
First Encounter.Neeko_056: "Ice bird woman! Woo! Neeko need coat."
First Encounter.Neeko_153: "Nidalee! Weird seeing you here. Neeko misses you."
First Encounter.Neeko_144: "No, Rengar! Be nice and sweet like Nidalee!"
First Encounter.Neeko_101: "Show me more of the world, Taliyah. Take me with you!"
First Encounter.Neeko_006: "May I touch your eyeball? Neeko is gentle."
First Encounter.Neeko_142: "Zyra has many thorns. Too hard for Neeko to get past."
First Encounter.Neeko_077: "Fa hasici! It means I like you. In a good way."
First Encounter.Neeko_083: "After fight, can Neeko tell you about Oovi-Kat tribe?"
First Encounter.Neeko_106: "Wow! We do not have that where I come from."
First Encounter.Neeko_128: "You are Vastaya! Neeko is Oovi-Kat. We are... cousins? Distant cousins!"

Attack.Neeko_087: "Neeko cast magic on you. Shoom! Shoom!"
Attack.Neeko_151: "I will blast their sho'ma in the face."

Ability Casting.Neeko_152: "So beautiful! Like moonlight on fresh snow."
Ability Casting.Neeko_090: "Beep. Boop. Neeko is metal person. Kwatz."
Ability Casting.Neeko_052: "Not monster. Outsider looking in, wanting to belong. Like Neeko."
Ability Casting.Neeko_017: "Life as Garen just simple. Just swing sword around. Very bland, yes."
Ability Casting.Neeko_079: "Neeko loves everything about strong... I-yao-i? Did I say it right?"
Ability Casting.Neeko_010: "The Vastayashai'rei tended your sapling, Green Father."
Ability Casting.Neeko_118: "Jinx is wild! Break everything! Phew! Phew!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_035: "I like angry Yordle! STAB STAB! TACOS! SKAAAARL!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_086: "Neeko always wanted to be a mountain!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_018: "So many colors at once. Neeko could teach you new colors, maybe?"
Ability Casting.Neeko_040: "Does dragon lady want to eat lunch with Neeko sometime? Maybe?"
Ability Casting.Neeko_036: "Hmm... Neeko not the only one who changes."
Ability Casting.Neeko_004: "The light in me knows the light in Taric."
Ability Casting.Neeko_139: "How do three people wear one pants?"
Ability Casting.Neeko_038: "I like this very much! Knife-bird woman! KA-KOOO!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_109: "Wish I could stay like this forever."
Ability Casting.Neeko_048: "Neeko will try you on for size. Oooh! I love it!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_034: "Do I smell as bad as I look? (Sniffs) Yes."
Ability Casting.Neeko_070: "Looking like boys is, um... takes getting used to."
Ability Casting.Neeko_119: "Neeko will not break your sho'ma. I promise."
Ability Casting.Neeko_104: "Nice to be something different for a change!"
Ability Casting.Neeko_028: "Feels same... almost like Neeko but faded."
Ability Casting.Neeko_005: "Neeko feels wrong. Not good. Void is full of never."
Ability Casting.Neeko_105: "Just yordling around. Is that what yordles say?"
Ability Casting.Neeko.cloneDestroyed.01: "Tricky tricky! You got the wrong Neeko!"

Kills and Objectives.Neeko_069: "Told you to not get close. Why did you not listen?"

Death.Neeko_061: "Ugh. Neeko's sho'ma went everywhere. Huge mess. Had to find it all."
Death.Neeko_046: "Poof! Neeko back in her Neeko skin."

Champion Select.Aphelios01.select.01: "So many weapons, Aphelios. The deadliest is your faith."
Champion Select.Aphelios01.ban.01: "Condemned to darkness, where our power grows."

Movement.Aphelios01.firstmove.01: "Aphelios… I hear you. I know what you sacrifice."
Movement.Aphelios01.firstmove.02: "Even from across the celestial veil… I will be with you, brother."
Movement.Aphelios01.firstmove.03: "It always starts with pain. We can only do this together, Aphelios."
Movement.Aphelios01.firstmove.04: "Your life upon the altar, brother… I will not betray it."
Movement.Aphelios01.firstmove.05: "With every step, two steps. With every breath, two breaths."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.01: "You knew this would not be easy, the way forward written in scars."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.02: "You walk the path of darkness, but you do not walk it alone, brother."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.04: "When your steps falter, brother, follow my voice."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.07: "You are the weapon the Lunari need."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.08: "By my word, you walk into the night."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.09: "You are not alone. Remember our promise."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.10: "I am your sister. I am listening."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.11: "I'm never further than a whisper echoing in silence."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.12: "Even when I close my eyes… I'll never look away."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.14: "Through your eyes, I see such wonders…"
Movement.Aphelios01.move.15: "Beneath the mask of silence… I know your true face, brother."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.16: "Again and again, I see you reach… for me."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.17: "How can I help you when I put your life at risk?"
Movement.Aphelios01.move.18: "From our fortress, I will guide you. I promise."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.19: "I beseech the moon to protect you."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.20: "I am right. This is what the moon tells me."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.22: "We must find each other before every first light."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.23: "We're in this together. Darkness and light."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.24: "As light reveals our path, so will darkness."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.25: "The brighter my light, the stronger your shadow."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.26: "Darkness is not heresy. It lies within us all."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.27: "We cannot let fear trap us in twilight."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.28: "Our destiny is hidden in the night."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.30: "The dawn will know the night's silence."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.32: "All we ask is for a witness to our sorrow."
Movement.Aphelios01.move.33: "We walk through violence. Born of shadow. Born of light."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.01: "Even when the moon is new, it is there. A whisper to the shadows of your soul… I am with you."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.02: "It is as the moon revealed, Aphelios. As beautiful. As terrifying."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.03: "Our path is set between the last breaths taken by our enemies."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.04: "You will make death more than death, brother. You will make it holy."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.05: "We cannot touch the moon. But its light can touch us. Shouldn't that be enough? Light, on our fingers…"
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.06: "Without pain, we would not need faith. The moon would not need us. We would not need each other, Aphelios."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.07: "The fortress is quiet. If only you could be here, Phel. You would make this stone seem loud."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.08: "If pain is what awaits us in the darkness, brother… we must run to it, unafraid."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.09: "What we want, what we need, what we must do… I envy the ignorant."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.10: "The Solari call us heretics, but when darkness comes, brother, they will need our light."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.11: "You cannot feel the tear running down your cheek. I cannot wipe it away…"
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.12: "Our thoughts touch… impossibly close. Which of us am I?"
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.13: "The fortress looms around me. It is everything. It is the only thing."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.14: "You make yourself a weapon, so you do not have to feel. But you are not a weapon; you are my brother."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.15: "Phel… You have made every movement a thousand times. Until you bleed. Until you do not have to think."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.16: "The pain makes you numb. But I can still feel, brother. I know the truth that pain hides."
Movement.Aphelios01.longmove.17: "I see further through the celestial veil. What we call truth is shadow."

First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterGeneric.02: "We have no enemies, Aphelios. Only those fated to meet us in the night."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterDiana01.01: "Diana knows the moon's name, Aphelios. I can feel it on her heart."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterDiana01.02: "The aspect of the moon. What is she fleeing? What has she done?"
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterSenna01.01: "Senna, in darkness, we find each other."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterSoraka02.01: "Soraka knows our pain, yet tells us not to feel it. To deny ourselves."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterYuumi01.01: "Yuumi is much friendlier when she visits me in the spirit realm, snuggling at my feet while I read Book and imagine the rain."
"We were born to twin destinies, to tragedy, as the sisters were before us."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterGun.01: "What do they hold if they only reach for the trigger?"
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterSpiritual.01: "The greatest power is the power greater than ourselves."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterAspect.01: "To become a vessel for the heavens, one only needs faith."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterLunari.01: "The moon is with us in darkness, but it is not there for us."
First Encounter.Aphelios01.encounterSolari.01: "The Solari do not see: we shine brightest with another's light."

Ability Casting.Aphelios01.INNATEgetSeverum.04: "The moon gathers darkness on the crescent's edge."
Ability Casting.Aphelios01.INNATEgetGravitum.03: "They will not escape what is coming."

Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killGeneric.01: "When you shine, the moon can worship. You did well, Aphelios."
Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killGeneric.02: "They are motes of dust, shimmering in moonlight."
Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killGeneric.03: "A prayer for their souls. Torn from the night."
Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killGeneric.04: "To make a life of death… you do what you have to, brother."
Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killDiana01.01: "Not even she knew what she would do. That was why she was afraid."
Kills and Objectives.Aphelios01.killSolari.01: "The heavens turn toward darkness. Now is our time."

Death.Aphelios01.death.01: "No, I was supposed to help you! I knew…"
Death.Aphelios01.respawn.02: "Out of darkness, the moon is born anew."

Champion Select.Rell_Select: "Nothing gets in, no one gets out."

Movement.Rell_Original_MoveFirst_2: "Run 'em all down! We're good, they're bad, and that's all you need to know."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveFirst_1: "This 'little girl' is about to crush some heads."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveFirst_0: "Fight like you mean it. Die for something that matters!"
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_9: "The armor keeps the world out. The lance does the rest."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_12: "I'd rather break rules than people, but I can make exceptions."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_3: "I fight for the lost. But mostly, I just fight."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_13: "Bones shatter and people lie, but I can always count on iron."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_1: "If I trusted people, I'd need even more armor."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_7: "Don't let anyone in. Never let anyone in."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_8: "The Black Rose may have done this to me, but Noxus knew."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_21: "Hurt me enough and I'll split your head open."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_11: "Noxians aren't the heroes they think they are."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_6: "Everyone who's ever stood in my way is dead or broken."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_18: "Forge your heart into something strong, unbreakable."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_17: "Trust is a luxury no one can afford."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_19: "The Rose wanted me to be a weapon. Well, here I am."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_4: "I'll finish this fight. I'm the only one who can."
Movement.Rell_Original_Move_5: "These sigils are a reminder. Screw my sigils."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveLong_0: "They'll pay for what happened to me. Noxus, The Black Rose... everyone."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveLong_4: "When steel crashes against steel, it's so loud. I almost forget."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveLong_2: "The Rose ripped the magic out of my friends and put it into me. I hate them."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveLong_1: "The people who hurt me are dead. All but one. My mother."
Movement.Rell_Original_MoveLong_3: "Those academy kids are still out there. I'll find them all. I'll save them."

First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterCassiopeia: "Hey, snake. I'm gonna crush your bones."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterDarius: "You know my dad, General. So you know what's about to happen."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterEkko: "O...Oh. So your name's Ekko? That's... that's cool. I'm cool."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterElise: "Bet the rose would sure hate losing their pet bug."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterKled: "You know I can see you, right? Gross little gerbil man..."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterLeblanc: "Hey, LeBlanc! Tell my mom I'm gonna rip her head off!"
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterLeona: "All right, Rell. Be cool. It's just a tall, super-strong armored lady."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterMordekaiser: "You're Mordekaiser, right? All metal. I can take you."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterSamira: "Samira. If you're looking for me, here I am."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterSett: "More like the boss of having his shirt off. Oh, I think he heard that."
First Encounter.Rell_Original_FirstEncounterSwain: "Noxus will fall, Swain. Starting with you!"

Joke.Rell_Original_Joke_0: "I'm the happiest girl in the world."

Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_Kill_2: "Someone scrape this idiot off the floor."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_Kill_5: "I told you not to fight me, but here we are."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_Kill_1: "Let's try that again. Hi, I'm Rell."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillCassiopeia: "One dead snake, one less petal on the rose."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillDarius: "You shoulda kept better tabs on your people, General."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillEkko: "Ugh. Just when I thought I knew him, he went back in time."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillElise: "One evil spider lady down, several evil animal people to go."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillKled: "Your lizard had the right idea. 'General-Admiral-Brigadier' Kled."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillLeona: "I hope this won't hurt my chances, Leona. Leona?"
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillMordekaiser: "Noxus was afraid of that guy? This might be easier than I thought."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillSamira: "So long, Samira. Thought you'd be more stylish than that."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillSeraphine: "We would not be good together, Sera."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_KillSett: "Does this mean I'm your boss now? I gotta walk away, this is too much."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_Assist_0: "I could learn to trust someone like you."
Kills and Objectives.Rell_Original_Assist_4: "You'll watch my back? Just like that? Cool."

Recall.Rell_Original_Recall_1: "This sucks! I don't have time for this!"
Recall.Rell_Original_Recall_0: "All this waiting! I just want to fight!"

Death.Rell_Original_Respawn_0: "Can't tell if I taste metal or blood."
Death.Rell_Original_Respawn_1: "'Excellence is measured in sacrifice,' or whatever."

Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_FirstMove_2: "I don't feel quite like myself these days."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_FirstMove_1: "You all left me to die in a hundred different ways with a thousand different faces."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_6: "Maybe this is real. No! Don't trust it!"
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_19: "Can't delete me now. Too deep in the network."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_20: "Had to take their parts… Rebuild my brain…"
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_4: "No one gets out. Nobody walks away."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_14: "It's all simulated. Every part of it."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_Move_21: "Clean up the code. Strip it lean."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_7: "Never been here before but last time I was… It was just the same."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_5: "They killed life, then truth, then death. This place is hell."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_0: "This is the true face of PROJECT. Take a good look."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_8: "The simulation's more real than reality. Just the way they want it."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_3: "Ghost code. Crossed wires. Voices… Buried in the numbers."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_4: "I can almost remember what I used to be. But I know what I've become."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_1: "I think I knew me once before. Somewhere."
Movement.Pyke_PROJECT_MoveLong_2: "Like flipping trough a picture book… With too many pictures!"

Shopping.Pyke_Original_OpenStore_0: "There's no way I'm good for business."
Shopping.Pyke_Original_OpenStore_1: "What's worth more? A pound of flesh or a gallon of blood?"

Game Start.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareWelcome01: "Welcome to Butcher's Bridge. The pride of the Slaughter Docks."
Game Start.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareWelcome02: "Welcome to Butcher's Bridge. No place for the squeamish."
Game Start.AnnouncerPyke.Declare30Seconds01: "30 seconds. Just a little longer now."
Game Start.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareMinionSpawn01: "Minions have spawned. Those little guys don't bleed. Ain't natural."

Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.Kill01: "You have slain an enemy. Dropped 'em like an anchor!"
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.Kill02: "You have slain an enemy. A killer after my own dead heart."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareDeath03: "You have been slain! Don't worry, death's just the beginning."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareDeath04: "You have been slain! I'll put in a good word for you down below."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillAlly02: "An enemy's been slain. Landed you a big one."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillAlly03: "An enemy has been slain. Cut 'em from gut to gob."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillEnemy01: "An ally's been slain! Your friend's dead."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillEnemy03: "An ally has been slain. Your friend's swimming with the fishes."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareExecution03: "Executed. Blood thirsts the land if you let it."
Kill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareExecution04: "Executed. Hard to resist the siren's call."

Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillDoubleAlly02: "Double kill! Got the captain and their mate."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillDoubleAlly03: "Double kill! Thinning out their crew, eh? Smart."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillTripleAlly02: "Triple kill! Three more for the deep."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillTripleAlly03: "Triple kill! A trio of souls sunk in the briny deep."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillQuadraAlly01: "Quadra kill! Your enemies are just grasping at straws now."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillQuadraAlly04: "Quadra kill! They're floundering! Just need to finish 'em off."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillDoubleEnemy02: "Enemy double kill! The bell's tolled twice."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillDoubleEnemy03: "Enemy double kill! You're chummin' the waters."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillTripleEnemy01: "Enemy triple kill! That's three of yours in the drink."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillTripleEnemy04: "Enemy triple kill! Like an albatross around your necks."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillQuadraEnemy03: "Enemy quadra kill! Four souls lost. You should probably run."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillQuadraEnemy04: "Enemy quadra kill! Four of yours 'neath the bounding main."
Multikill Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.KillPentaEnemy03: "Enemy pentakill! Glad you could join me."

SpreeAnnouncements.AnnouncerPyke.SpreeLegendaryEnemy01: "An enemy is legendary! Bodies are just piling up."
SpreeAnnouncements.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareShutdown01: "Shut down! That's what I like to see."

Structure Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.StructureDestroyInhibitorE: "Your team has destroyed an inhibitor! Unleash the super minions!"
Structure Announcements.AnnouncerPyke.StructureRespawnInhibitorA: "Your inhibitor is back from the deep."

Game Conclusion.AnnouncerPyke.DeclareDefeat02: "Defeat! Don't call 'em Slaughter Docks for nothin'."

Champion Select.Yone_Ban: "You think I am the one to fear? Hmph."

Movement.Yone_Original_MoveFirst_0: "Before, I chased a wayward gale. Now I hunt a storm of darkness."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveFirst_1: "Many mistake me for the nightmares I slay. Hmph, let them."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveFirst_2: "In this cursed second life, where does the mask end, and I begin?"
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveFirst_3: "They look at me and see only the mask."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveFirst_4: "The azakana have spread like a plague since the Noxian invasion. My work... never ends."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_0: "Azakana lurk everywhere. I will end their depredations."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_1: "Some days I forget what lies behind this mask."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_2: "Sleep is not for the weak, but for the blessed."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_3: "Demons take many forms, I hunt them all the same."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_4: "The spirit realm is... strange. A mirror, an inverse, of our own."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_8: "Sometimes, to save someone, you must fight  them."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_9: "I'm not here to save their souls."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_10: "Honor once bound me above all else."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_12: "The road to ruin, I've walked it once before."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_14: "What does one do with an abundance of masks?"
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_17: "Without a banquet of sorrow, an azakana starves."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_18: "No sleep, no rest... there is no time."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_19: "Rare is the person who shows their true face."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_22: "Between uncertainty and fear, the azakana prowl."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveStandard_24: "Forget the past, it only clouds the future."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_0: "Wear a mask long enough, and you forget the face beneath."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_1: "On a cliff by the sea, I found the strangest spirit. It walked on four legs and spoke of dreams."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_2: "A broken heart, an anxious mind, all can attract the azakana."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_3: "Azakana trap their victims in an vicious cycle of emotion. Doubt breeds doubt, fear breeds fear, and the azakana feasts."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_4: "Long before blades and sorcery are needed, words... can save a soul."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_5: "So many try to flee their burdens. Fleeing is impossible!"
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_6: "Bound to the world of the living. - Yone sighs - Denied the peace of death..."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_7: "Every aspect of an azakana is a stroke. Each stroke forms a character, revealing their true name..."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_8: "One blade carries the weight of my past. The other, holds the key to my future..."
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_9: "When we met in the spirit realm, this azakana upon my face knew me!"
Movement.Yone_Original_MoveLong_10: "Through the mask, I see their truth laid bare. Yet my own, - Yone scoffs - dance just out of reach..."

First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_0: "I will take no joy in cutting you down!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_1: "Blink, and you'll miss your own death!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_2: "Two paths cross. One, condemned to end."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_3: "Ah, to be blind to the true dangers of this world!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_5: "Such bravado! But you're fooling no one."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounter_7: "Death rejected me, but I'm sure it will welcome you!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterAhri: "Perhaps you can charm some sense into my foolish brother, Ahri."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterEvelynn: "Evelynn. A sugary mask for such a master of agony."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterFiddlesticks: "What ancient horror is this? Is... is this what an azakana could become?!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterKindred: "I have fallen outside your cycle, Lamb and Wolf. Are you here to usher me back?"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterLillia_0: "A comfort to see you Lillia, after so many azakana..."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterLillia_1: "Do not wish to hide behind masks, Lillia. Yours... is a kind face."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterNocturne: "Living nightmare! I will end you before you cross paths with the dream fawn!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterRiven: "Guilt clings to you, Riven. Forgive yourself, or the azakana will find you."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterShen: "Balance is a delusion, Shen. Surely you see that now."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterSwain: "Grafted to a demon by choice. What a grand fool!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterTahmKench: "Tahm Kench. Twocoats. I know your true name, demon!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterTaliyah: "Taliyah, the one you call master is a fool!"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo_0: "Is that the taste of salt on the wind? Ah, hello brother."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo_1: "A broken mask, meets a dishonored blade."
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo_2: "Brother, our paths cross once again. Will our swords do the same?"
First Encounter.Yone_Original_FirstEncounterYordle: "An innocent spirit! I'd... almost forgotten those existed!"

Kills and Objectives.Yone_Original_Kill_2: "May your spirit find the peace you did not."

Recall.Yone_Original_Recall_0: "A respite, to return the sealed to their rightful place."
Recall.Yone_Original_Recall_1: "The more I seal away... the more they seem to multiply!"
Recall.Yone_Original_Recall_2: "With each mask I claim, I come one step closer to understanding my own."

Death.Yone_Original_Respawn_2: "I thought death would grant me peace... How naïve."
Death.Yone_Original_Respawn_4: "Every time it's no less strange, nor less painful."

Champion Select.Sett_Ban: "Ay, never pick a fight ya can't win."

Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_1: "Wait, hold up. Are we gettin' paid for this?"
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_2: "Five versus five? Heh. What kinda sicko is runnin' this rumble?"
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_3: "Okay, everyone here knows how to throw a punch, right? 'Cause I don't have time for lessons."
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_4: "Listen up, if any of ya you don't die out there, I might have work for ya."
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_5: "The boss is here. Hold your applause... seriously, be quiet."
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_6: "Hey, is there a doctor on hand? Asking for my opponents."
Movement.SettOriginal_FirstMove_7: "Hey, uh, listen... My momma don't need to know any o' this. 'kay?"
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_1: "Every single one of 'em thinks they're the one to beat me..."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_2: "I don't like hurtin' people. I like the money I get from hurtin' people."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_3: "The crackin' of bones is the clinkin' of coins."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_4: "Ugh, hey anyone know whose teeth are stuck in my knuckles?"
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_5: "If I ever find my old man, well, I hope he's been training."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_7: "You swing on the boss? You better not miss."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_8: "Nothin' people hate more than a guy who makes somethin' of himself."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_9: "Must be a fight brewin', my fur just stood up."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_10: "Nothin' I hate more than people with sleeves."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_11: "My coat costs more than this whole damn place."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_12: "They call me a thug. I call me an entrepreneur."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_13: "If anyone's watching this fight... they owe me money."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_14: "Ah, the line of people trying to take me down just ain't long enough."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_15: "I ain't no 'half-breed'... I'm a full breed, and I'm the only one."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_16: "Too hairy for humans, too smooth for Vastaya. What are you gonna do?"
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_17: "I don't bother with jabs; if you're throwing, throw it hard."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_18: "Gah, probably shouldn't've have worn my nice pants to this."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_19: "It's all fun and games 'til someone gets their face caved in."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_22: "Everyone's got a plan, 'til they get slammed into the ground."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_23: "All men wanna be me, too bad they ain't me."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_25: "Some beatings you just gotta do yourself."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_26: "Somewhere out there is a demand that needs supplyin'."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_27: "Who's lookin' to lose a fight today?"
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_28: "Y'know... you don't really know someone until you fought 'em to the death."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_29: "Ionia... place was so damn quiet before I came along."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_30: "Violence is my business, and business is booming."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_31: "People say they don't like violence, but they all watch."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_32: "Glad I don't have to fight me."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_33: "Bein' the boss is a lot better than not bein' the boss."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_34: "Momma always said I had her temper."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrder_35: "Only thing an honest livin' makes you, is broke."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_1: "A wise master once said: 'Be like water.' Guess I'm kind of a tsunami."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_2: "They say you learn a lot from a beating. If that's true, I've made the whole world smarter."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_3: "I used to risk my neck in the pit, making someone else rich. Now we do it the other way around. I like that better."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_4: "When you're on top, there's always some chump trying to drag you down. Pullin' at your feet, scuffin' up your nice shoes."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_5: "They called me 'Sett the Beast-Boy Bastard'. Hah. Now it's 'Sett the Beast-Man Bastard'."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_6: "Looks like I brought my fists to a knife fight. Honestly, I feel bad for the knives."
Movement.SettOriginal_MoveOrderLong_7: "I remember my first fight. I ran home cryin' to momma... she wiped my tears with her claws."

First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_1: "Look at that face. It's just screamin' 'punch me'."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_2: "You're the number one contender? Hah, I must've really cleaned out the division."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_3: "Welcome to my show! If you live, I'll have you back."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_4: "If you even dream of whoopin' me, you better wake up and apologize."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_5: "My old man ran off. You'd be smart to do the same."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_6: "You got guts. Too bad I gotta put my fists through 'em."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_7: "Look sharp, meat! You're in the main event now."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_8: "To be the boss, you gotta beat the boss. I don't see you bein' the boss."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_9: "Hah, I ain't about to lose to that."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounter_10: "I ain't never lost, you know that right?"
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterBilgewater: "Hey, bilgerat, you see my pop? He'd be a scumbag like you."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterNoxians_1: "You Noxians ain't all bad. You ain't all good either."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterNoxians_2: "You Noxians may have started the fight pits, but I damn sure perfected 'em."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterNoxians_3: "Hey, you're Noxian, just like my pa. I'll try not to hold it against ya."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterNoxians_4: "You know the deal Noxus. Stay outta my business, and I stay outta yours."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterVastaya_1: "You know, my mom's a Vastaya. That's the only reason I ain't stomped you yet."
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterVastaya_2: "Look at you! Old blood Vastaya... you too good for me? Huh?"
First Encounter.SettOriginal_FirstEncounterVastaya_3: "You're about to see my human side-- the part that ain't so nice."

Taunt.SettOriginal_TauntGeneral: "Anyone wants a piece of me, line forms right here."
Taunt.SettOriginal_TauntResponse_1: "It's easy to talk big when you still got all your teeth."
Taunt.SettOriginal_TauntResponse_2: "You think I got where I am by listening to people?"

Joke.SettOriginal_Joke: "Love you, Ma. See ya tomorrow. Mwah."

Attack.SettOriginal_AttackChampion_18: "This is the part where you bleed."

Kills and Objectives.SettOriginal_KillChampionGeneral_1: "Ooh... you should get some ice on that."
Kills and Objectives.SettOriginal_PentaKill_2: "Look out, there's a new boss 'round here!"

Recall.SettOriginal_RecallLeadin_1: "Uh... be right back. Gotta check on some, uh, legitimate business."
Recall.SettOriginal_RecallLeadin_2: "Pause the fight! Forgot to stretch. Don't wanna pull nothin'."
Recall.SettOriginal_RecallLeadin_3: "Little break between rounds, then, come out swingin'."
Recall.SettOriginal_RecallLeadin_4: "Y'know, life's really all about the quiet time between beatdowns."
Recall.SettOriginal_RecallLeadin_5: "Things I love: uh, my momma, breakin' necks, and fine Ionian silk."

Death.SettOriginal_Respawn_1: "Ain't even thinkin' 'bout throwin' in the towel."
Death.SettOriginal_Respawn_4: "So, that's losin', huh? Not my favorite thing."
Death.SettOriginal_Respawn_5: "Aw great, did that leave a mark?"
Death.SettOriginal_Respawn_6: "It ain't how many times you get knocked down. It's how many times you get back up."
Death.SettOriginal_Respawn_7: "Well... when life gives you lemons, punch life in the throat."

Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_0: "Humans cast a spell every night. Every time they fall asleep."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_1: "The garden is filled with burls. The burls, with nightmares... Mother Tree, I'll remind them how to dream."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_2: "You can do this, Lillia. You are a strong, capable dream fawn. A-and you have a big stick. A-and you hit people with it but don't really mean it! Sorry."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_3: "Where are you, little lost dreams? I'll bring you to your home in the Dreaming Tree."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_5: "In my garden—the garden—there's a tree—the tree."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_6: "Night's falling in my garden. Leaves rustle like sheets! Why is...no one dreaming?"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveFirst_7: "A little girl, lying on her bed. Be brave, dream. She needs you."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_0: "Oh, Mr. Root, you almost tripped me."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_1: "When they say goodnight, do you think they mean it?"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_10: "Every time I hold my branch, I see the tree with my fingers."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_11: "I'll stay in the forest...until I learn how to use doors."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_13: "I'll just...look around for threats. Fifth time's the charm!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_14: "I'll face anything...b-but won't look it in the eyes. Eep!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_15: "A yawn is a smile before sleep."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_16: "Day dreams, night dreams, mid-morning dreams, dusk dreams!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_17: "The beauty of the world beckons desires to be real."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_19: "How can I tip-toe, when I don't have toes?!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_20: "When I'm quiet, I hear so many things."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_21: "Quiet things are strong. That's why I'm whispering!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_22: "The humans forget so much when they awake."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_7: "What lies beneath the surface? We lie it down to see."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_8: "I catch dreams so the humans can chase them."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveStandard_9: "You have to close your eyes to open them. Wh-whoops!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_0: "Do you think day turns red because it sees night watching, o-or is it just me?"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_1: "Dreams are funny things. Sometimes they have feathers, sometimes they are wooly, sometimes they lift me up like a bubble!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_10: "Everyone is so loud. They never say what they really mean. Really, really mean."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_11: "Humans think trees stand so tall, but they're lying on the air. You can hear them snore, and they're creaking!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_12: "I want to meet a human...from over here. C-can they see me? Don't let them see me! I'm not ready! Eep!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_2: "Mother Tree used to have so many flowers. I hope you meet her one night, dream."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_3: "I can't stop from hiding, from being alone. But maybe, possibly, dream, someone will be alone with me."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_4: "Okay! Don't trip, don't trip—oops! Okay! Don't trip again, don't trip again—woah!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_5: "Every direction here is straight. Where you leave is always behind you. No wonder the humans are lost."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_6: "My hooves are saying prance, but I-I...oh, too much pressure! Eep!"
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_7: "Dream, I'll tell you a secret." *gasp* "N-never mind. Someone might hear."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_8: "A leaf rustled! Is it okay if I hug my branch? Hug..."
Movement.Lillia_Original_MoveLong_9: "Don't see me, don't see me, don't see me, don't see me! See me."

First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounter_0: "Well met! ...Is what I would tell them, if I wasn't already running! Eep!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounter_1: "Do you think we've met before, in a dream we've both forgotten? Wouldn't that be wonderful?!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounter_3: "Would you...maybe, possibly, perhaps...want to dream with me?"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounter_4: "You, over there! Do you hear me? Not you. Your dream!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounter_5: "Your dream calls to me! I-I hope you don't mind. Oh, you mind, don't you?"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterAhri: "Some come to the garden lost. Others, to lose themselves. Like you, Ahri."
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterIvern: "Ivern! Am I still your favorite sprout? N-not that I have to be!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterNeeko: "Neeko, can you teach me why the humans hide what's inside? Or...should I ask your flower?"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterNocturne_0: "You've spread like a shadow no one sees–because it's within themselves!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterNocturne_1: "Nightmares are desire turned inside out, and upside down, and..." *gasp* "Oh, dizzy!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo_0: "Running from problems won't solve them. But it makes me feel safe!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo_1: "When he speaks, I hear your whisper, dream!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterYone_0: "I feel your yearning. Deep down, it's what  he wants too."
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterYone_1: "Why would you want to remove your mask, Yone? It's great for hidin'."
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterYone_2: "When trapped in fear, dreams become nightmares. We're fighting the same thing!"
First Encounter.Lillia_Original_FirstEncounterZoe: "You bring many dreams, sparkly child, but also...much anguish."

Taunt.Lillia_Original_Taunt: "Time to be mean, Lillia! ...Did it work?"

Joke.Lillia_Original_Joke: "Oh hello, bird! What little whisps have you—A-a-a-achoo!" *gasp* "Oopsie."

Attack.Lillia_Original_Attack_1: "Shush. It's the dream's turn to sleep."
Attack.Lillia_Original_Attack_10: "Dreams die when they're held too tight."
Attack.Lillia_Original_Attack_15: "Close your eyes so I can say hello."
Attack.Lillia_Original_Attack_9: "Better a sleepy head than a sleepy heart."

Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_11: "Let's dance above the human snores! Hehehe!"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_13: "Our joy will plant a smile seed!"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_15: "So much to live, so much to love!"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_16: "Dreams! Have you come out to play?"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_3: "Who can dream how a dream is born?"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_5: "It's like my roots are in the clouds!"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_7: "I and me are having a party, dream."
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_8: "I was sparkling the whole time, and no one told me?!"
Ability Casting.Lillia_Original_PranceStack_OnBuffDeacti: "No one saw that, no one saw that!"
"I'm just going to go hide forever now."

Kills and Objectives.Lillia_Original_KillChampion_1: "Dreams live on, even after the dreamer."
Kills and Objectives.Lillia_Original_KillChampion_3: "D-don't judge a flower by its bud, you!"
Kills and Objectives.Lillia_Original_KillHuman: "You dreamed until you ached. Now do something about it."

Recall.Lillia_Original_Recall_0: "Oh! Are you alright, dream? Your light is so dim..."
Recall.Lillia_Original_Recall_1: "What's wrong, dream? Are you ready to bloom? Oh!"

Death.Lillia_Original_Respawn_1: "Do you think they'll remember me, dream? When they wake up, do they remember themselves?"
Death.Lillia_Original_Respawn_2: "Now I just have to wait for my confidence to regrow."
Death.Lillia_Original_Respawn_4: "I'm not wearing any pants! Oh...oh. So that's what human nightmares are like."

Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveFirst_1: "What a strange wonderful world. I must make sure it stays that way."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveFirst_2: "Back when I was a doll, I really wanted to fight. This is my chance, my only one."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveFirst_3: "Alright everyone. First, we must win. After, I'll be glad to fix any clothes, hair, or broken spirits."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveFirst_3.1: "Scissors, needles, thread; tools of Isolde. She'll always be with me, and I with her."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_0: "I certainly endured far worse than this."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_1: "Still can't believe I get to move my hands and feet all on my own!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_2: "These turrets look strong, it will be quite fun cutting them down!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_3: "I'll make sure my allies feel the joy they deserve!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_4: "I'll break as many needles as it takes to get this right."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_5: "I sense their resolve. No matter, mine will be stronger."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_8: "I must hurry if I am to win."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_11: "The memories I stitch here will be my own."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_12: "I've got to make each footprint mean something."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_13: "The wind at my back feels so good. I can't lose this, I won't."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_14: "What happens next, I get to decide!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_15: "The Black Mist won't hurt anyone, I promise."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_16: "They're trying to stop me. Well, they can keep on trying!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_17: "If only she were here to see this, see me."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_18: "I will experience everything like I never could before!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_21: "This is better than a dream. It's real, and I won't ever forget it!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_23: "No one said life would be easy. That is it's charm to be sure."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_24: "Seeing my dress twirl reminds me to smile."
Movement.Gwen_Original_Move_24.1: "Isolde. Wherever you are, I know you'll be alright."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_0: "Bits of fabric can become something beautiful. My work here can do just the same!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_1: "I remember when she sewed my dress with these scissors. Now, they cut a different cloth."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_2: "Oh... are those mountains beyond the cliffs? I've always wished to see one up close!"
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_3: "It's called the Hallowed Mist, but how it feels matters more. Warm, safe, like nothing can hurt me."
Movement.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_4: "This place certainly brings out the fight in everyone. Wouldn't be fair if I didn't present my best."

First Encounter.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_4.1: "Akshan, you've made the sentinels proud. Don't let them down."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_4.2: "Irelia, you saved the land. It's an honor to cross blades."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_MoveLong_4.3: "Lucian, quite the journey we had. Are you still a good shot?"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterLux: "You seem happy, Lux, but you know pain too. Why deny it?"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite: "A talking mountain. Now, what shall I say to you when you fall?"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterMalphite.1: "Olaf, my friend. Still looking for a glorious death?"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterOrnn: "A giant ram who sharpens scissors. Why... dreams do come true!"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterOrnn.1: "Riven. A little thread and that blade will be as good as new."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterOrnn.2: "I've missed you, Senna. Let's give our best for Isolde."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterSeraphine: "A stage, a voice, is that really all you are?"
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterSeraphine.1: "Thresh, no matter your form, I've faced you once. I'll do it again."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterSeraphine.2: "Sentinel, maybe the world would look better without those dark glasses."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterSeraphine.3: "Vex, you can be happy for the right reasons. I'll prove it."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterSeraphine.4: "Viego. You never deserved love. Especially not hers."
First Encounter.Gwen_Original_FirstEncounterYasuo.1: "Please take care of the maiden... or I won't go easy on you."

Taunt.Gwen_Original_Taunt: "I heard something. 'You are bad!' They said it, not me."
Taunt.Gwen_Original_TauntResponse: "How sad, you must be broken on the inside."

Joke.Gwen_Original_Joke: "Just like the good old times. Sweet, simple, and out of control!"
Joke.Gwen_Original_JokeResponse: "Bad jokes are a waste of life!"

Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_Kill_8.1: "I know your tricks, Akshan. Do better."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_Kill_8.2: "Irelia, that wasn't the hero who saved the land."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_Kill_8.3: "Good try, Lucian. I'll tell Senna you got me good."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillLux: "No running from pain, Lux. Next time, shine through it."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillMalphite: "Ha! And they say scissors can't beat rock!"
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillMalphite.1: "You're most welcome, Olaf. I promised you'd die with glory."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillOrnn: "Mr. Ornn, are you still there? Are you asleep?"
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillOrnn.1: "Riven, I fought alongside a stronger you. Show me her."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillOrnn.2: "Please, Senna. Don't hold back. I've seen your strength."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillSeraphine: "A pretty voice, Seraphine. What a shame that's all you were."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillSeraphine.1: "I suppose you didn't plan for that. How unlike you, Thresh."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillSeraphine.2: "Vayne, you're a sentinel. I'd expect more."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillSeraphine.3: "Vex, next time give joy a chance."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillYasuo.1: "Don't worry, I'll show the maiden how to smile."
Kills and Objectives.Gwen_Original_KillPenta: "Five in a row! What an absolute joy!"

Recall.Gwen_Original_Recall_1: "I learned this trick back home, and added my own misty touch!"
Recall.Gwen_Original_Recall_2: "Hold on! I need to grab more supplies! Don't start a fight without me!"

Death.Gwen_Original_Respawn_0: "I can't give up! Not now, not ever!"
Death.Gwen_Original_Respawn_1: "Oh? I thought I was lost, but I'm still here. I'm still alive!"
Death.Gwen_Original_Respawn_2: "Ugh! I can do this! For her, and for everyone!"
